NK013(pa)014:0: b+ha ga w+aam gu h+ya ga r+b+ha sh+aa n+ta ma
NK013(pa)014:1: d+h+yam s+ya sa d+ha n+aa d+hi sh+tha n+aam gu n+d+ai
NK013(pa)014:2: n+aa ma bi ha ra ti sma //
NK013(pa)014:4: / bcom ldan 'das gsang ba snying po zhi ba 'bring
NK013(pa)014:5: po'i sgrub thabs byin rlabs kyi snye ma zhes bya
NK013(pa)014:6: ba bzhugs so // bcom ldan 'das gsang ba snying
NK013(pa)014:7: po zhi ba 'bring po'i sgrub thabs byin rlabs kyi
NK013(pa)014:9: thugs rje'i mnga' bdag rje btsun bla ma dkyil 'khor
NK013(pa)014:10: gyi dbang phyug la gus pa chen pos phyag 'tshal
NK013(pa)014:11: lo // rgyal ba kun gyi rdo rje gsum bsdus ye shes sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dngos //
NK013(pa)014:12: dbyings phyug dga' mar rnam rol mchog bde'i sprin phung chos dbyings kun khyab las //
NK013(pa)014:13: mtha' dag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis lha yi gar spro in+d+ra n+ai la'i ri //
NK013(pa)014:14: rab sgeg ltar mdzes bla ma mi bskyod rdo rjes snying la bde chen byin //
NK013(pa)014:15: gang de'i dngos gyur pad+ma gnyag gnubs zur pa'i srol //
NK013(pa)014:16: chos kyi spyan mnga' dam pa yab sras kyis bkral ba //
NK013(pa)014:17: dus mthar spyod pa'i skal mnyam don du 'dir bsdebs te //
NK013(pa)014:18: rnyog med bkod la dpa' bo mkha' 'gros brtse bar mdzod //
NK013(pa)014:19: ye shes 'ja' lus sgyu ma'i sku can rnams //
NK013(pa)014:20: gshegs shul zab don rgyud sde'i grong khyer du //
NK013(pa)014:21: rim gnyis sgo chen 'byed la brtson pa rnams //
NK013(pa)014:22: skal bzang 'dod pa sbyin pa'i lde'u mig longs //
NK013(pa)014:23: de la 'dir chos thams cad kyi brjod bya bden
NK013(pa)014:24: gnyis dbyer med 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid blo yi
NK013(pa)014:26: rjod byed stong phrag brgya pa sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las phyungs shing /
NK013(pa)014:27: gnyis su med pa'i rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po
NK013(pa)014:28: theg pa thams cad kyi gzhi dang rtsa bar nges
NK013(pa)014:29: pa dpal gsang ba snying po'i don thams cad dril
NK013(pa)014:30: na chos barje kahthoga pa'i bzhed kyis lngar mdzad de
NK013(pa)014:31: / shes bya gzhi sku gsum gyi dkyil 'khor du gnas tshul /
NK013(pa)014:32: de ma rtogs pas gzhi sems can /
NK013(pa)014:34: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi snang ba so sor 'char ba'i 'khrul 'khor snang tshul /
NK013(pa)014:35: de yang dag pa 'dul byed sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs rjes mkhyen cing gzigs pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:36: gzigs nas rtog pa med pa'i thugs rje nyi ma'i 'od dang /
NK013(pa)014:37: chu bo'i rgyun ltar rtag khyab lhun grub tu 'char zhing /
NK013(pa)014:38: khyad par 'khrul pa sbyong byed thabs lam rkyen yi
NK013(pa)014:39: ge'i rgyud kyis don mdzad tshul rnams su bsdu bar
NK013(pa)014:40: mdzad la / de las lam rgyud kyi rim pa /
NK013(pa)014:41: srid pa sdug bsngal du ma mthong ba'i blos //
NK013(pa)014:43: rang gcig pu ma yin par mkha' khyab kyi sems
NK013(pa)014:44: can thams cad sgrol 'dod kyi byang chub la 'jug
NK013(pa)014:45: pa brtan pos / rdo rje'i slob dpon dngos grub thams cad kyi rtsa ba mnyes par byas te /
NK013(pa)014:46: rdo rje theg pa'i lam gyi gzhi smin byed kyi dbang thams cad bskur ba thob pas /
NK013(pa)014:47: rgyud smin pa'i rgyal sar chud pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:48: rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig mtha' dag mig
NK013(pa)014:49: 'bras ltar ma nyams la yongs su rdzogs par srung
NK013(pa)014:50: ba'i rten gyi gang zag shes rab mchog dang /
NK013(pa)014:51: brtson 'grus kyi go cha bgos pa zhig gis sku
NK013(pa)014:52: gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor lam rim pa
NK013(pa)014:54: de'ang in+t+ra b+hu tis mdzad pa'i rim gnyis las /
NK013(pa)014:55: sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos bstan pa //
NK013(pa)014:56: rim pa gnyis la yang dag gnas //
NK013(pa)014:57: bskyed pa yi ni rim pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:58: rdzogs pa yi ni rim pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:60: ting 'dzin de la legs gnas nas //
NK013(pa)014:61: rdzogs pa'i rim pa 'dod pa yis //
NK013(pa)014:62: skad gcig nyid la lha rnams gsal //
NK013(pa)014:63: rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i bskyed rim ste //
NK013(pa)014:64: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i rdzogs pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:65: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar rdzogs rim gyi rtogs pas skye ba'i nus pa smin //
NK013(pa)014:66: lus ngag yid gsum tha mal du 'dzin pa bzlog cing /
NK013(pa)014:67: rgyud sbyong ba'i phyir lam lnga'i rnal 'byor rgyud don
NK013(pa)014:68: slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang bas lam gyi
NK013(pa)014:69: rim par bkral pa las ji skad 'byung ba ltar
NK013(pa)014:70: stong chen dang snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor la
NK013(pa)014:71: goms pas phyag rgya gcig pa'i phra ba yi ge'i
NK013(pa)014:72: spro bsdu dang / rags pa zhal gcig phyag gnyis dang /
NK013(pa)014:73: goms nas zhal gsum phyag drug gi rjes spros pa'i
NK013(pa)014:74: rnal 'byor bskyed pa'i rim pa la nan tan du
NK013(pa)014:75: bya ba las / le'u bco lnga pa yan gyi
NK013(pa)014:76: rtsa rgyud kyi ma bsgyur rnal ma zhi ba la'ang
NK013(pa)014:77: lha dang tshom bu spro bsdu mtha' yas pas 'dir
NK013(pa)014:78: ni gleng gzhi las gsungs pa lha so drug dang
NK013(pa)014:79: bya ba las / / gsum pa las thub drug
NK013(pa)014:80: bcas dngos bstan zhe gnyis zhi ba 'bring po'i phyag
NK013(pa)014:81: rgya spro ba dang tshogs bsgrub kyi mos bsgom mtha'
NK013(pa)014:82: dag la sbyar du rung ba'i mngon rtogs yan lag
NK013(pa)014:85: sgrub byed cho ga'i rim pa grub pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK013(pa)014:86: dang po la gsum sbyor dngos rjes so //
NK013(pa)014:87: dang po la sngon 'gro'i sbyor ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:95: dbang rnams thob par byas pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:96: ston pa mchod brtson rtogs pa gsal //
NK013(pa)014:97: dam tshig sngags dang phyag rgya rnams //
NK013(pa)014:98: ma nyams shes shing yo byad ldan //
NK013(pa)014:99: zhes pa'i mtshan nyid mnga' bas //
NK013(pa)014:100: gnyis pa yang de nyid las //
NK013(pa)014:101: khe grags 'dod g.yengs kun spangs te //
NK013(pa)014:103: tshad med thugs rjes 'gro sgrol zhes //
NK013(pa)014:104: dam bca' brtan te mi ldog par //
NK013(pa)014:105: zhes pa ltar sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i 'dod bya la dran pa nye bar bzhag pas /
NK013(pa)014:109: ri bo dben pa'i gnas mchog ni //
NK013(pa)014:110: me tog shing dang bkra shis bya //
NK013(pa)014:111: snyan pa'i sgra ldan bar chad med //
NK013(pa)014:112: ces sogs 'byung ba bzhin bdag dbang bar chad med pa'i gnas bsam gtan dang mthun par /
NK013(pa)014:114: sku gsung thugs ldan gzugs kyang dgod //
NK013(pa)014:115: ces pa dam tshig gi bris sku dang /
NK013(pa)014:116: rten gsum la mchod pa'i bye brag phyi nang dang /
NK013(pa)014:117: stegs dma' bar sngon gtor chu dang nyer spyod /
NK013(pa)014:118: sgrub po'i mdun du rdor dril dang nang mchod sogs mkho ba'i yo byad rnams tshogs par bya'o //
NK013(pa)014:120: phyag dang gsol gdab rgyun bshags dang //
NK013(pa)014:121: sgrib sbyong tshogs bsags bsang chu brlab //
NK013(pa)014:122: bgegs bsal mtshams bcad bshags sdoms bzung //
NK013(pa)014:123: byin rlabs sngon 'gro'i rim pa bcu //
NK013(pa)014:125: bla ma dkyil 'khor srung ma la phyag dgu sprugs su 'tshal ba tshul phyag dang /
NK013(pa)014:126: slob dpon la slob ma rnams nas phyag dang /
NK013(pa)014:127: phan tshun thams cad nas phyag bsnol ba'i gral phrag gis bde ba'i stan la 'khod pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:128: gnyis pa 'dus pa tshom bu'i sgrub pa'i skabs /
NK013(pa)014:129: las kyi rdo rjes phyag gsum 'tshal nas /
NK013(pa)014:130: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen pos dbu mdzad /
NK013(pa)014:131: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir 'dus pa thams cad thugs dam la mnyam par bzhag par zhu /
NK013(pa)014:133: thams cad kyi gnas gsum du bdud rtsi'i thig le
NK013(pa)014:134: re byas la sku gsung thugs su byin gyis rlabs
NK013(pa)014:135: rdo rje slob dpon nas bzung ste thams cad kyi
NK013(pa)014:136: dbu la me tog gi phreng ba gdags so //
NK013(pa)014:137: gsum pa la gnyis yan lag bdun pa dang skyabs sems so //
NK013(pa)014:139: rang nyid dpal rdo rje sems dpar gsal ba'i thugs
NK013(pa)014:140: kar nyi zla'i ga'u kha sbyor gyi dbus h'u gi
NK013(pa)014:141: 'od zer srog dag pa'i lam nas zhugs /
NK013(pa)014:142: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad chos kyi sku las
NK013(pa)014:143: gzugs kyi skur bzhengs pa bcom ldan 'das thugs sgyu
NK013(pa)014:144: 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lha tshogs rdo rje slob dpon la
NK013(pa)014:145: brgyud pa'i bla mas bskor ba dang bcas pa mdun
NK013(pa)014:146: gyi nam mkhar badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes se gol
NK013(pa)014:148: yid las sprul pa'i lha mo rnams kyis mchod par bsam ste /
NK013(pa)014:149: badz+ra sa t+wa sa pa ri wa ra badz+ra ar+g+ham pa tits+tsha h'u /
NK013(pa)014:151: thal mo snying gar bkod de /
NK013(pa)014:152: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK013(pa)014:153: sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK013(pa)014:154: yid bzhin rin chen lta bu'i sku //
NK013(pa)014:155: bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:156: bla ma bshes gnyen dam pa khyod //
NK013(pa)014:157: bdag cag rnams kyi pha lags so //
NK013(pa)014:158: bdag cag rnams kyi ma lags so //
NK013(pa)014:159: bdag cag rnams kyi mgon lags so //
NK013(pa)014:160: bdag cag rnams kyi ston pa lags //
NK013(pa)014:161: bdag cag rnams kyi 'dren pa lags //
NK013(pa)014:162: mun pa sel ba'i sgron ma lags //
NK013(pa)014:163: dug gsum nad sel sman pa lags /
NK013(pa)014:165: / 'gro ba sgrol ba'i gru lags so //
NK013(pa)014:172: des bskyed dus gsum sangs rgyas dang //
NK013(pa)014:173: dam chos rgyu 'bras ma lus dang //
NK013(pa)014:174: rig 'dzin byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK013(pa)014:176: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi bdag /
NK013(pa)014:177: ye shes rgya mtsho rab zab thugs //
NK013(pa)014:179: nor bu rin chen yon tan mdzod //
NK013(pa)014:180: rdo rje yid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:181: mnyam nyid dbyings su bdud bzhi ngang gis bcom //
NK013(pa)014:182: phyag rgya'i rang bzhin gnyis med rdzogs par ldan //
NK013(pa)014:183: yod med mtha' 'das bdag gzhan yongs kyi dpal //
NK013(pa)014:184: kun bzang lha yi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:185: dpal ldan gnyis med sgrib pa spangs pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:186: ye shes rang rig gsal ba'i mkha' dkyil nas //
NK013(pa)014:187: dkyil 'khor spro ba 'gro don sprul pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:188: ma lus thugs su chud la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:189: kun bzang 'khor lo bzhi dbus dga' bzhi'i gzugs //
NK013(pa)014:190: bde chen sprin dpung rdo rje'i lha mo rnams //
NK013(pa)014:191: tshad med bzhi dang 'dod lnga'i dpal thogs pas //
NK013(pa)014:192: ye shes lnga dang rdo rje bzhi ru mchod //
NK013(pa)014:193: bdag gis tshe rabs thog ma med pa nas //
NK013(pa)014:194: da lta yan chod mi dge sdig spyod dang /
NK013(pa)014:196: / 'dul sdom bshig dang phyi nang dam nyams dang //
NK013(pa)014:197: khyad par nyon mongs bag med le lo yis //
NK013(pa)014:198: rtsa ba yan lag la sogs bsrung bya rnams //
NK013(pa)014:199: zhig ral nyams dang khyad bsad yal bar dor //
NK013(pa)014:200: gzhung du ma bsnyag gzhung 'gal che chung rnams //
NK013(pa)014:201: nyams dang tshor dang ma tshor nyams so 'tshal //
NK013(pa)014:202: rtsa ba yan lag zla zhar kun tu nyams //
NK013(pa)014:203: shin tu 'gyod cing gdung bas bshags par bya //
NK013(pa)014:204: gnong ngo 'gyod do tshangs par stsal du gsol //
NK013(pa)014:205: rdzogs sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK013(pa)014:207: / 'phags pa rnams dang so so'i skye bo yis //
NK013(pa)014:208: dge ba'i rtsa ba bsags pa ma lus la //
NK013(pa)014:209: rtag tu bdag ni rjes su yi rang ngo /
NK013(pa)014:211: / 'bras bu mngon gyur ring po ma len par //
NK013(pa)014:212: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten khams na bzhugs so 'tshal /
NK013(pa)014:214: / 'gro rnams myur du sangs rgyas thob slad du //
NK013(pa)014:215: bla med chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul //
NK013(pa)014:216: gdul bya'i bya ba tshar ba'i thub pa rnams //
NK013(pa)014:217: chos kyi dbyings su 'dar bar bzhed pa la //
NK013(pa)014:218: ji srid 'khor ba stong par ma gyur bar //
NK013(pa)014:219: bzhugs nas mya ngan mi 'da' gsol ba 'debs //
NK013(pa)014:220: bdag gis tshe rabs thog ma med pa nas //
NK013(pa)014:221: da lta yan chod dge ba ci spyad dang //
NK013(pa)014:222: khyad par deng 'dir dge ba ci bsags pa //
NK013(pa)014:223: bdag gzhan don phyir byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK013(pa)014:224: gnyis pa sgrub thabs me long lta bu las /
NK013(pa)014:225: byams dang snying rje dga' ba dang //
NK013(pa)014:226: btang snyoms pa yang yongs bsgoms nas //
NK013(pa)014:227: zhes pa ltar skyes bu mchog gi bsam pas drangs pa'i blos /
NK013(pa)014:228: bdag gzhan nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad /
NK013(pa)014:229: ji srid byang chub bar du /
NK013(pa)014:230: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo
NK013(pa)014:231: bo dam pa'i chos theg pa rim pa dgu'i 'byung
NK013(pa)014:232: gnas / dge 'dun 'phags pa rnams kyi mnga' bdag
NK013(pa)014:233: rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i dpal ldan bla
NK013(pa)014:234: ma rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK013(pa)014:235: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK013(pa)014:236: legs par gsungs pa'i chos la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK013(pa)014:238: bcom ldan 'das rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la
NK013(pa)014:239: sogs pa yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams
NK013(pa)014:240: la sh+r+ai ma h+aa ka la /
NK013(pa)014:241: dpal lha mo nag mo la sogs te chos skyongs
NK013(pa)014:242: pa'i srung ma ye shes kyi spyan dang rdzu 'phrul
NK013(pa)014:243: gyi zhabs dang ldan pa rnams la lan gsum /
NK013(pa)014:244: sems can thams cad dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i go 'phang la 'god par bya /
NK013(pa)014:245: de yi ched du sku gsung thugs kyi rnal 'byor la 'jug par bya'o //
NK013(pa)014:246: sems can thams cad bde ba dang sogs tshad med bzhi bsgom /
NK013(pa)014:247: bzhi pa zhi khro bshags chung gi don bsdu na thun mong min pa'i rdor sems bsgom bzlas te /
NK013(pa)014:248: rang gi spyi gtsug tu sna tshogs pad+ma 'dab brgyad
NK013(pa)014:249: kyi lte bar che mchog yon tan la snying gar
NK013(pa)014:250: zhi ba dang spyi bor khro bo'i lus dkyil rdzogs
NK013(pa)014:251: pa'i dbu thog tu pad+ma dang zla ba'i gdan la
NK013(pa)014:252: / h'u las byung ba'i bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo
NK013(pa)014:253: rje sems dpa' bla ma dang gnyis su med pa
NK013(pa)014:254: sku mdog dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis rdo rje
NK013(pa)014:255: dang dril bu thugs kar bsnol bas yum snyems ma
NK013(pa)014:256: dkar mo g.yon dril bu thogs pa la 'khyud pa
NK013(pa)014:257: / / zhabs phyed skyil mthe bong g.yas rang gi spyi gtsug tu reg pa /
NK013(pa)014:258: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i rgyan can /
NK013(pa)014:260: mgrin par +aah thugs kar h'u dang rdo rje zla ba sngags phreng g.yas 'khor dang bcas pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:261: de las 'od zer 'phros sgrub sde brgyad kyi lha
NK013(pa)014:262: lus dkyil dang bcas pa dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK013(pa)014:263: dkyil 'khor gyi rnam par badz+ra sa m+aa dzas spyan
NK013(pa)014:264: drangs te / bcom ldan 'das zhi khro rab 'byams kyi tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:266: phyogs bcu dus bzhi kun gyi bdag nyid che //
NK013(pa)014:267: bla ma rgyal ba zhi khro yongs rdzogs dgongs /
NK013(pa)014:269: / 'dir gshegs nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK013(pa)014:270: nyams chag na rag sbyong phyir phyag mchod bzhes //
NK013(pa)014:271: yon tan phun tshogs bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:272: dmigs med spros bral chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:273: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la 'gro mgon
NK013(pa)014:274: cir yang sprul pa'i sku la gnas lugs mi 'gyur
NK013(pa)014:275: rdo rje'i sku yang dag mngon par byang chub sku
NK013(pa)014:276: la nyon mongs zhi mdzad zhi ba'i lha la log
NK013(pa)014:277: lta tshar gcod khro bo'i sku la thabs mgon tshe
NK013(pa)014:278: bdag 'jam dpal skyon bral sgra sgrog pad+ma'i gsung la
NK013(pa)014:279: // yang dag don ldan badz+ra thugs la dug lnga
NK013(pa)014:280: nad sel bdud rtsi sman la dregs pa 'jam mdzad
NK013(pa)014:281: phur pa'i lha 'byung ba'i mnga' bdag ma mo'i tshogs
NK013(pa)014:282: la sa dang lam rdzogs rig 'dzin rnams la bstan
NK013(pa)014:283: pa bsrung mdzad dam can rnams dgra bgegs 'dul mdzad
NK013(pa)014:284: sngags bdag rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:285: gang gi rgyal ba zhi khro yi //
NK013(pa)014:287: nyams chag ma lus kun byang nas //
NK013(pa)014:288: mtshams med lnga la smos ci dgos //
NK013(pa)014:289: na rag gnas kyang dong dkrugs te //
NK013(pa)014:290: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK013(pa)014:291: rdo rje sems dpa'i gsang sngags dngos //
NK013(pa)014:292: las sgrib nyams sgrib dag byed pa'i /
NK013(pa)014:294: / 'khor ba dong dkrugs yong snying bzlas //
NK013(pa)014:295: bcom ldan 'das bdag gi sdig sgrib nyes ltung thams cad byang zhing dag par mdzad du gsol //
NK013(pa)014:296: zhes gsol ba btab pas gnas gsum 'bru gsum las 'od kyi lus ngag yid gsum la phog /
NK013(pa)014:298: slar yang sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang sems ye shes bdud rtsis lus thams cad gang /
NK013(pa)014:299: dam tshig nyams chag thams cad byang zhing dag par gyur par mos la /
NK013(pa)014:300: badz+ra sa t+wa sa ma y+aa /
NK013(pa)014:301: sogs yi ge brgya pa lan nyer gcig bzlas mthar /
NK013(pa)014:302: hoh bde gshegs yongs rdzogs dgongs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:303: rgyal ba'i bka' dang bla ma'i lung //
NK013(pa)014:304: ji bzhin ma spyad slob dpon smad //
NK013(pa)014:305: rdo rje mched dang lcam dral la //
NK013(pa)014:306: lta log ngan sems ngag tu smras //
NK013(pa)014:307: brdeg btsog gnod pa dngos su spyad //
NK013(pa)014:308: lha dang dkyil 'khor nyams ma gsal //
NK013(pa)014:309: dzab bzlas ma dag zur chag nyams //
NK013(pa)014:310: gsang bar 'os dang gnyer gtad smras //
NK013(pa)014:311: gsang bcu bsgrag cing bla ma bslus //
NK013(pa)014:312: rtsa ba'i dam nyams mthol zhing bshags //
NK013(pa)014:313: spyad par bya ba'i dam tshig lnga //
NK013(pa)014:314: shes bya lnga dang bsgrub bya lnga //
NK013(pa)014:315: mi spang lnga dang dang len lnga //
NK013(pa)014:316: yan lag dam nyams mthol zhing bshags //
NK013(pa)014:317: bsnyen bsgrub ting 'dzin mi gsal zhing //
NK013(pa)014:318: nya stong dus drug mchod pa chag /
NK013(pa)014:319: le lo bsog 'jog tshogs spyang gis //
NK013(pa)014:320: phud lhag nyams shing kha tshar shor //
NK013(pa)014:321: tshor dang ma tshor rkyen dbang gis //
NK013(pa)014:322: sgo gsum bag med dam nyams bshags //
NK013(pa)014:323: bla ma rdo rje sems dpas rigs kyi bu khyod
NK013(pa)014:324: kyi sdig ltung thams cad dag pa yin no zhes
NK013(pa)014:325: gnang ba byin par bsam nas /
NK013(pa)014:326: chos thams cad ye nas gnas pa'i gnas lugs yid la byas te /
NK013(pa)014:327: yid kyi dam nyams lta bas bshags //
NK013(pa)014:328: de yang kun gzhi byang chub sems //
NK013(pa)014:329: yin pa med pa'i lta ba rtogs //
NK013(pa)014:330: min pa med pa'i spyad pa rtogs //
NK013(pa)014:331: yin pa med pa'i dgongs nyams lon //
NK013(pa)014:332: yin min med pa'i spyod pa rtogs //
NK013(pa)014:333: re dogs med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK013(pa)014:334: rtsa ba yan lag thams cad kyi //
NK013(pa)014:335: chag nyams ma byung ma skyes pas //
NK013(pa)014:336: bshags bya bshags byed gnyis med grol //
NK013(pa)014:338: sku gsum gyi man+dala 'bul ba las longs sku dag pa zhing gi man+dala ni /
NK013(pa)014:340: h'u +amo s+w+aa +aam h+aah snang srid phyogs bcu rnam
NK013(pa)014:341: dag zhing khams bde chen 'og min stug po bkod
NK013(pa)014:343: 'dod lnga'i sprin gyi char chen rtsi shing skar ma ltar bkram 'dod dgu'i dkyil 'khor kun 'byung bas /
NK013(pa)014:344: kun khyab chos dbyings rdul snyed mchod pas kun tu 'gengs pa'i kun bzang nam mkha'i mdzod chen 'di /
NK013(pa)014:345: dpal ldan rdor sems rgyal ba rgyal sras rgya mtsho mnyes pa'i dpal stug rgya mtshos mdzes gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:346: phyogs bcu'i brtan g.yo rdul snyed kyis //
NK013(pa)014:347: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK013(pa)014:348: bla ma rnams dang dkon mchog gsum //
NK013(pa)014:350: sprul sku snang srid rnam dag gi man+dala la /
NK013(pa)014:353: gling bzhi'i dkyil 'khor rin chen ldan //
NK013(pa)014:354: dpag bsam shing dang rdzing bu mdzes //
NK013(pa)014:355: las bzhi'i byin brlab khyad par las //
NK013(pa)014:356: lha dang lha mo longs spyod ldan //
NK013(pa)014:357: lhag pa'i ting 'dzin mchod par bzhes //
NK013(pa)014:358: chos rnams thams cad 'bras bu yongs rdzogs shing //
NK013(pa)014:359: sangs rgyas rnams la man+dala 'di 'bul bas /
NK013(pa)014:361: / 'bras bu 'phags pa'i nor bdun lhun grub ste //
NK013(pa)014:362: ting 'dzin 'bum phrag rnams la dbang bsgyur shog /
NK013(pa)014:363: mos gus gsol ba gdab pa chos sku'i man+dala ni /
NK013(pa)014:364: na mo de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang /
NK013(pa)014:369: zhing khams zag pa med pa /
NK013(pa)014:370: zad mi shes pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:374: brgyud pa'i bla ma rje btsun rin po che rnams kyi byin rlabs kyis //
NK013(pa)014:375: bdag rig pa 'dzin pa rdo rje zhes bgyi ba la /
NK013(pa)014:376: sems can thams cad kyi don du rdzogs pa chen po shin tu rnal 'byor /
NK013(pa)014:377: don rang byung gi ye shes de kho na nyid don gyis gang ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:384: shin tu grol ba rgya chen po mdzad du gsol /
NK013(pa)014:385: bdag gis dge ba'i las 'di bgyis pa yis /
NK013(pa)014:387: / 'jig rten ring por mi thog sangs rgyas nas /
NK013(pa)014:388: de kun 'gro la phan phyir dam chos kyis //
NK013(pa)014:389: sdug bsngal mang gdung sems can sgrol gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:390: ces brjod pas lhan skyes kyi ye shes 'char bar 'gyur ro //
NK013(pa)014:392: tshogs zhing rnams rang la thim par gyur pa'i ngang la bzhag go //
NK013(pa)014:393: drug pa la rang nga rgyal bzung ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:397: skad cig gis stong pa'i ngang las /
NK013(pa)014:398: rang nyid dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i sku mdog sngo nag g.yas rdo rje /
NK013(pa)014:400: zhal 'dzum yang mche ba yud tsam gtsigs pa /
NK013(pa)014:401: spyan gsum zhi ba yin kyang yud tsam sdang mig tu gzigs pa /
NK013(pa)014:402: sku 'od dpung gi nang na bzhugs kyang 'od kyi rtse mo la me ri 'phro ba /
NK013(pa)014:403: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la yum dbyings phyug ma dang snyoms par 'jug pa /
NK013(pa)014:405: g.yon pas dril bu yab kyi snyan rtsar 'khrol pa /
NK013(pa)014:406: de yi thugs kar zla ba'i gdan la rang 'dra'i ye shes sems dpa' /
NK013(pa)014:407: de yi thugs kar rdo rje'i lte bar h'u la /
NK013(pa)014:408: h'u badz+ra d+h+rika gis bskor ba /
NK013(pa)014:409: yum gyi thugs kar dril bu la /
NK013(pa)014:410: mum d+h+aa du shwa ris bskor ba'i bdag nyid can du gyur /
NK013(pa)014:411: de dang dus mnyam du phyogs bcu'i 'gro ba thams cad kyang rdo rje sems dpa'i skur gyur te /
NK013(pa)014:412: spyi mgrin snying ga nas 'od zer dkar dmar sngon po byung nas rang la thims par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:414: b+han+d+ha'i nang du a mri ta btab pa bkod /
NK013(pa)014:416: b+h+r+aum las b+han+d+ha'i nang du a las zla ba'i steng du /
NK013(pa)014:417: m+aum las yum kro d+hi shwa ri ma sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK013(pa)014:418: rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams pa /
NK013(pa)014:419: dpal gyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa'i thugs kar zla ba'i steng du /
NK013(pa)014:420: b+han+d+ha m+aum gyis mtshan par gsal bar gyur /
NK013(pa)014:421: badz+ra d+h+aa du kro ti shwa ri de bi shwa d+ha na ta na dz+ny+aa na h'u h'u h'u /
NK013(pa)014:423: dbyings phyug khro mo 'od du zhu ba'i chu yi
NK013(pa)014:424: rdul phra rab tu bsam nas bdag gnas yo byad
NK013(pa)014:426: kro d+hi shwa ri h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:428: dkar phyogs drod nyul gyi bgegs bsal ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:429: nag phyogs glag lta'i bgegs bsal ba'o //
NK013(pa)014:433: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+rum las byung ba'i snod yangs
NK013(pa)014:434: shing rgya che bar tram las bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho
NK013(pa)014:435: zad mi shes pa'i gtor ma 'dod pa'i yon tan
NK013(pa)014:438: rang gi snying ga'i h'u gi 'od zer gyis dkyil
NK013(pa)014:439: 'khor gyi 'khor yug tu gnas pa mkha' 'gro'i tshogs
NK013(pa)014:440: dang / phyogs skyong zhing skyong srid gsum 'byung po'i
NK013(pa)014:441: tshogs thams cad a kar+sha ya dzah sa spyan drangs
NK013(pa)014:442: la spro na sngags drug phyag spel /
NK013(pa)014:443: d+aak+ki ni lo ka p+aa la k+she tra p+aa la
NK013(pa)014:444: sa p+aa ri wa ra i dam b+aa lin+ta kha
NK013(pa)014:445: kha kha hi gsum dbul la /
NK013(pa)014:446: ting 'dzin mthu ldan rnam rol gzi byin can //
NK013(pa)014:447: shes rig grags pa'i tshul khrims 'khor gyis bskor //
NK013(pa)014:448: mya ngan 'das pa bdud rtsi'i ro yi bcud //
NK013(pa)014:449: mkha' 'gro zhing skyong mnyam nyid ngang du bsngo //
NK013(pa)014:450: phyogs skyong rgyal chen so so'i 'khor bzlog cing //
NK013(pa)014:451: phyogs dang phyogs mtshams thams cad bsrung ba dang //
NK013(pa)014:452: dam bcas zhal bzhes khas blangs lha dag bzhin //
NK013(pa)014:453: bstan pa brjod la tshul bzhin srung du gsol //
NK013(pa)014:454: zhes rol mo'i sgra bcas dkar gtor sgrub khang gi ngos su dor /
NK013(pa)014:456: sarba big+h+nana ba lin+ta g+h+ri h+na kha hi /
NK013(pa)014:459: gsang ba'i dam can so so nas /
NK013(pa)014:461: / 'du ba la ni ma gtogs shing //
NK013(pa)014:462: nyan pa la ni mi dbang ba //
NK013(pa)014:463: kun kyang re ba bskang lags kyis //
NK013(pa)014:464: da lta nyid du so sor dengs //
NK013(pa)014:466: ci ste bka' las 'das gyur na //
NK013(pa)014:467: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal khros nas ni //
NK013(pa)014:468: rdo rje mtshon chen 'bar ba yis //
NK013(pa)014:469: thal ba bzhin du brlag par byed //
NK013(pa)014:472: h'u bzhi ba'i sngags rol mo'i sgra drag po dang bcas pa'i tsham rngams bya /
NK013(pa)014:473: brgyad pa kun rdzob kyi mtshams dang /
NK013(pa)014:476: rang gi mig g.yas ma las nyi ma /
NK013(pa)014:477: g.yon pa a las zla ba /
NK013(pa)014:478: g.yas kyis mes bgegs dang log 'dren thams cad bsreg /
NK013(pa)014:481: man+t+ra su ma b+h+aa ni h'u /
NK013(pa)014:487: zhes gsungs pa tsam gyis lha tshogs rnams kyi thugs ka nas rdo rje'i char /
NK013(pa)014:492: sku thams cad las brag ri'i char byung bas bgegs rnams brgyal zhing gtor /
NK013(pa)014:493: g.yon gyi zla ba bdud rtsis chus thal ba yang ma lus par bkrus /
NK013(pa)014:495: phyi rol du mtshon cha rnams rim pa drug gi
NK013(pa)014:496: gur khang du gyur pa'i phyi rdo rje rgya gram
NK013(pa)014:497: sna tshogs pa'i rwa can du brtan /
NK013(pa)014:498: slar yang spyan dbus ma'i byang chub sems kyi 'od
NK013(pa)014:499: kyis bgegs brgyal ba rnams slar bslang ste gnyis su
NK013(pa)014:500: med pa'i ye shes kyi rang bzhin du byas shing
NK013(pa)014:501: 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan du skyes par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:503: badz+ra sa t+wa ra dz+aa dza h'u /
NK013(pa)014:504: nga yi dkyil 'khor brtan bya'i phyir //
NK013(pa)014:505: khro rgyal byin rlabs las byung ba //
NK013(pa)014:506: mtshon cha rnam pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK013(pa)014:507: dkyil 'khor rim pa tshul bzhin srungs //
NK013(pa)014:509: steng yang rdo rje'i bla bre la //
NK013(pa)014:510: rdo rje'i tho thog ser chen 'bebs /
NK013(pa)014:512: / 'og kyang rdo rje'i sa gzhi la //
NK013(pa)014:513: rdo rje'i tsh+wa tsh+wa skar ltar 'khrug /
NK013(pa)014:514: phyogs mtshams rdo rje 'bar bas gtams //
NK013(pa)014:515: rlung yang 'gyu ba'i skabs med na //
NK013(pa)014:516: bgegs kyi tshogs lta ga la srid //
NK013(pa)014:517: badz+ra dz+wa l+aa na lang+ka kro d+ha h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:519: steng yang 'khor lo'i 'khor lo'i 'og kyang 'khor lo'i
NK013(pa)014:520: phyogs mtshams 'khor lo rlung yang bgegs kyi tshogs lta
NK013(pa)014:522: steng yang ral gri'i ral gri'i 'og kyang ral gri'i
NK013(pa)014:523: tsha phyogs mtshams rlung yang bgegs kyi p+r+aa dz+ny+aa dz+wa
NK013(pa)014:524: l+aa h'u / steng yang tho ba'i tho ba'i tho
NK013(pa)014:525: thog 'og kyang tho ba'i phyogs mtshams rlung yang 'gyu
NK013(pa)014:526: bgegs kyi mu sti dz+wa la h'u /
NK013(pa)014:527: steng yang rgya gram rgya gram tho thog 'og kyang
NK013(pa)014:528: rgya gram tsh+wa phyogs mtshams rlung yang bgegs kyi tshogs
NK013(pa)014:530: steng yang brag ri'i brag ri'i tho thog ser chen 'bebs /
NK013(pa)014:532: / 'og kyang brag ri'i sa gzhi la //
NK013(pa)014:533: brag ri'i tsh+wa tsh+wa skar ltar 'khrug /
NK013(pa)014:534: phyogs mtshams brag ri 'bar bas gtams //
NK013(pa)014:535: rlung yang 'ju ba'i skabs med na //
NK013(pa)014:536: bgegs kyi tshogs lta ga la srid /
NK013(pa)014:537: badz+ra pa ta la pany+tsa h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:539: rnam par rtog pa bgegs yin te //
NK013(pa)014:540: bgegs ni rang gi sems las byung //
NK013(pa)014:541: rang bzhin ye nas dag zhes na //
NK013(pa)014:542: bgegs zhes bya ba'i ming yang med //
NK013(pa)014:543: spyi bo sna tshogs rdo rje'i rwa ba las //
NK013(pa)014:544: rkang mthil rdo rje chen po'i sa gzhi dang //
NK013(pa)014:545: rtsib ma rdo rje'i rwa bar gnas pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:546: ltag pa rdo rje gur du phub nas ni //
NK013(pa)014:547: ba spu mda' yi d+r+wa ba chen po ste //
NK013(pa)014:548: sen mo me ri rab tu 'bar ba'o //
NK013(pa)014:549: dgu pa la dam tshig nyams pa'i bshags pa khyad par ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:553: bshags yul bla ma rgyal ba rgya mtsho nam mkha'
NK013(pa)014:554: til gyi gang bu bzhin du khyab pa gsal bar
NK013(pa)014:555: gyur / tshe rabs 'khor ba thog med nas bsags
NK013(pa)014:556: pa'i sdig ltung thams cad la gnong zhing 'gyod pas
NK013(pa)014:557: gyur / bla ma dang / khyad par du gsang sngags kyi skor zhugs nas dam tshig nyams pas /
NK013(pa)014:558: 'gyod sdoms kyi bsam pa brtan pos phyag srin lag rtse sprad de /
NK013(pa)014:560: ye shes sku mchog rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ni //
NK013(pa)014:561: zla rgyas bzhin du spros pa mi mnga' yang //
NK013(pa)014:562: thugs rje nyi gsal 'od bzhin mdzad pa /
NK013(pa)014:564: / 'dir gshegs pa dag la dgongs shing bzhugs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:565: brjod med shes rab mi g.yo chos kyi sku //
NK013(pa)014:566: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs sku rigs lnga'i gtso //
NK013(pa)014:567: thugs rje thabs mkhas rgya cher rol pa'i lha //
NK013(pa)014:568: zhi khro sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:569: dngos su 'byor dang yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:570: kun tu bzang po bla med mchod sprin gyis //
NK013(pa)014:571: mkha' dbyings rnam dag rgya cher yongs bkod de //
NK013(pa)014:572: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rgya mtshos mchod //
NK013(pa)014:573: kun tu bzang mo gsang ba'i b+ha ga la //
NK013(pa)014:574: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rab 'byams ma lus kun /
NK013(pa)014:576: / 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang du ro gcig pa //
NK013(pa)014:577: gnyis med byang chub sems kyis mnyes rgyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:578: sems kyi rang bzhin chos dbyings nam mkha' che //
NK013(pa)014:579: chos rnams rnam dag ye nas 'od gsal zhing //
NK013(pa)014:580: rnal 'byor nyid dbyings smra bsam las 'das pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:581: mnyam nyid byang chub sems la rtag tu 'dud //
NK013(pa)014:582: kun bzang rdzogs chen ye nas brdal ba la //
NK013(pa)014:583: phyi nang gsang ba bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK013(pa)014:584: snang srid rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i dbyings /
NK013(pa)014:586: / 'byung dang 'byung 'gyur yab yum lhun rdzogs rnams //
NK013(pa)014:587: gsang chen rab dgyes gzugs can bdag nyid ma //
NK013(pa)014:588: mkha' dbyings klong yongs pad+mo 'khyil pa la //
NK013(pa)014:589: gnyis med thig le chen por 'od gsal zhing //
NK013(pa)014:590: ma bcos spros med byang chub snying po'i sku //
NK013(pa)014:591: cir yang snang ba bde chen g.yung drung lha /
NK013(pa)014:594: bdag nyid chen po rigs lnga yab yum dang //
NK013(pa)014:595: byang chub lcam dral khro bo khro mo'i tshogs //
NK013(pa)014:596: rdo rje lha mo tshogs rje tshogs kyi bdag /
NK013(pa)014:597: rigs lnga dpal chen khro rgyal yab yum bcu //
NK013(pa)014:598: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya sgo ma bzhi //
NK013(pa)014:599: ye shes sprul pa'i lha tshogs mang po dang //
NK013(pa)014:600: ma ltar byams shing sring ltar gdung la sogs //
NK013(pa)014:601: legs nyes stangs 'dzin dam tshig rjes gcod ma //
NK013(pa)014:602: phyi nang mkha' 'gro rnal 'byor ma yi tshogs //
NK013(pa)014:603: dpang gyur rdo rje dam can dgongs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:605: thugs rje gdung 'tshob rig 'dzin bdag cag gis /
NK013(pa)014:607: / 'gro ba'i don du byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK013(pa)014:608: bla med go 'phang bgrod par bya ba'i phyir //
NK013(pa)014:609: bstan pa rgya mtsho so so'i 'dul khrims dang //
NK013(pa)014:610: sku gsung thugs dang mnyam sbyor sdom pa'i mchog /
NK013(pa)014:611: rdo rje 'das dka' dam tshig gtan gyi gnyer //
NK013(pa)014:612: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK013(pa)014:613: snga phyir nos shing gnyer du smras so 'tshal //
NK013(pa)014:614: yun du ma gtong 'da' bar mi bgyid cing //
NK013(pa)014:615: don las gol zhing ldog sems ma mchis kyang //
NK013(pa)014:616: gdod bya longs yod snyam pa'i le lo yis //
NK013(pa)014:617: klong du ma gyur rtsal shugs chung ba dang //
NK013(pa)014:618: shes bzhin mi ldan bag med dbang gyur te //
NK013(pa)014:619: sgom la mi brtson bsnyen sgrub g.yel la sogs //
NK013(pa)014:620: tshor dang ma tshor ma rig dbang gis na //
NK013(pa)014:621: ston pa'i bka' dang dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK013(pa)014:622: rnal 'byor gang zhig dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:623: skad gcig tsam yang phrad smra mi bya zhing //
NK013(pa)014:624: lung pa gcig gi chu la mi 'thung zhes //
NK013(pa)014:625: bka' las byung ba de ltar ma lcogs te /
NK013(pa)014:626: gsang sgo 'chol bas dbye bsal dka' ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:627: mngon shes chung bas skyon can ma rtogs te //
NK013(pa)014:628: nyams dang tshogs 'dres nyams pa bskang ba dang //
NK013(pa)014:629: nyams dang snod min rnams la chos bshad de //
NK013(pa)014:630: nyams la mi 'dzem nyams pa'i skyon la sogs //
NK013(pa)014:631: nyams dang 'grogs shing nyams pa de dag gis //
NK013(pa)014:632: nyams grib skyon gyis gos par gyur to 'tshal //
NK013(pa)014:633: tshe 'di'i rkyen dang yun gyi sgrib pa rnams //
NK013(pa)014:634: rab gnong 'gyod pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK013(pa)014:635: byams pa'i thugs brtses bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK013(pa)014:636: gnyis med mi 'gyur dbyings la bdag bkod de //
NK013(pa)014:637: mi dmigs btang snyoms ngang du bzhugs nas kyang //
NK013(pa)014:638: gnyis med don gyi tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
NK013(pa)014:639: don dam gnyis med spros las 'das pa la //
NK013(pa)014:640: rnam rtog gang yang dmigs par mi 'gyur te //
NK013(pa)014:641: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam gyi dbang gis na //
NK013(pa)014:642: nongs pa mchis na rab gnong bzod par gsol //
NK013(pa)014:643: mthol lo bshags so dam can gnyan gyi tshogs //
NK013(pa)014:646: nongs pa mchis na mi 'chab bzod par gsol //
NK013(pa)014:647: bzod par bzhes te tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
NK013(pa)014:648: yi ge brgya pa brjod de chag nyams rang bzhin med par dag par bsam /
NK013(pa)014:650: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i rgya bcas pa thugs kar 'chang bzhin du /
NK013(pa)014:651: bla ma dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:652: bla med mi spangs bla ma bkur //
NK013(pa)014:653: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad //
NK013(pa)014:654: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK013(pa)014:655: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya //
NK013(pa)014:656: gti mug chags dang zhe sdang che //
NK013(pa)014:657: nga rgyal phrag dog mi spang ngo //
NK013(pa)014:658: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen //
NK013(pa)014:659: dag pa'i snod bcud mi 'dor ro /
NK013(pa)014:661: // bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK013(pa)014:662: de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:663: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas pa /
NK013(pa)014:665: / 'gro la phan pa'i don du spyad //
NK013(pa)014:666: byang chub sems mchog dam pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:667: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK013(pa)014:668: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong na //
NK013(pa)014:669: rdo rje rgyal pos byin rlobs shig /
NK013(pa)014:671: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' bdag gis mdzad //
NK013(pa)014:672: byang chub spyod dka' bdag gis spyad //
NK013(pa)014:674: bdag cag bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:676: bcu pa la rang gi rgyud byin rlabs pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:678: dang po ni ye shes 'beb pa ste /
NK013(pa)014:680: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK013(pa)014:681: khyad par ston pa'i byin chen dbab pa'i dbang chen bskur /
NK013(pa)014:682: mthu chen mthu stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK013(pa)014:683: dbang chen dbang bskur dngos grub mchog stsol gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK013(pa)014:684: las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK013(pa)014:687: zhes spos dang byin chags pa'i rol mo'i bskul /
NK013(pa)014:690: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs sku gsung thugs kyi phyag
NK013(pa)014:691: rgya 'og min nas kha char bab pa ltar byon
NK013(pa)014:692: nas snying ga'i sgo phyes te sib kyis thim par
NK013(pa)014:693: gyur pa'i ngang la gsal stong 'dzin med du ci
NK013(pa)014:699: rang gi thugs ka nas yi ge gsum spros /
NK013(pa)014:704: ma dag pa thams cad bsreg gtor bkrus //
NK013(pa)014:706: thugs kar thim ste stong par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:707: stong pa'i ngang las rdo rje bde mchog sgyu 'phrul
NK013(pa)014:708: d+r+wa ba'i ye shes lnga yi rang gzugs dkar mthing
NK013(pa)014:709: sngo ser dmar ljang gzugs kyis mdzes pa'i /
NK013(pa)014:710: rig ma dam pa mchod yon ma sogs /
NK013(pa)014:714: dpag bsam gyi me tog sogs thogs shing /
NK013(pa)014:715: brtan g.yo'i bcud kun bsdu ba /
NK013(pa)014:716: ting nge 'dzin gyi 'gyur ba mtha' yas pa'i dpal can /
NK013(pa)014:717: spyod yul kun bzang nam mkha'i mdzod kyi sprin dpung chen po /
NK013(pa)014:718: bla ma dang bcom ldan 'das rnam par shes pa'i
NK013(pa)014:719: rgyal po la sogs pa dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lor
NK013(pa)014:720: mnyes pa rgya mtsho 'byung bar gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:723: pat+yam push+pe nas gan+d+he'i bar sbyar /
NK013(pa)014:724: lhag ma nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgyas byin gyis brlab bo //
NK013(pa)014:725: gnyis pa thun min sman rag gtor ma brlab /
NK013(pa)014:728: stong pa'i ngang las rang gi thugs ka nas b+h+aum chad /
NK013(pa)014:729: mu tig dri ma med pa dkar po lta bu'i /
NK013(pa)014:730: nang ka p+aa la yangs shing rgya che ba'i phyi
NK013(pa)014:731: rin po che sna lnga las grub pa'i gzhal med
NK013(pa)014:732: khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs dang bcas pa
NK013(pa)014:733: / thig bzhi btab pas ril cha dgu dang ldan
NK013(pa)014:734: pa'i dbus nyi ma'i steng byang sems dkar po la
NK013(pa)014:735: / h'u m+aum / shar du zla ba'i steng dri chen ser po la +amo l+aam /
NK013(pa)014:736: lhor rin chen zur brgyad steng sha chen sngon po la s+w+aa m+aam /
NK013(pa)014:737: nub tu pad+ma 'dab brgyad steng rak+ta dmar po la +aam b+aam /
NK013(pa)014:738: byang du e gru gsum steng dri chu ldang gu la h+aa t+aam /
NK013(pa)014:739: de rnams las 'od 'phros 'khor 'das kyi bcud bsdus te bstim /
NK013(pa)014:740: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK013(pa)014:742: so so'i rigs kyi dril bur gyur //
NK013(pa)014:743: spro bsdus rdo rje gsum du byas //
NK013(pa)014:744: dbus su rdor sems yab yum dkar //
NK013(pa)014:745: shar du rnam snang yab yum ser //
NK013(pa)014:746: lho ru rin 'byung yab yum sngo //
NK013(pa)014:747: nub tu snang mtha' yab yum dmar //
NK013(pa)014:748: byang du don grub yab yum ljang //
NK013(pa)014:749: rang rtags thugs bsnol yum la 'khyud //
NK013(pa)014:750: rang gi phyag g.yon pa'i mtheb srin la ma a
NK013(pa)014:751: yongs su gyur pa'i nyi zla'i dbus h+r+aihls rta mgrin
NK013(pa)014:752: dmar po lcags kyu thogs shing sdigs mdzub mdzad pa
NK013(pa)014:753: / mi pham ma dkar mo lcags kyu /
NK013(pa)014:754: khro gnyer ma ser mo zhags pa /
NK013(pa)014:755: ro lang ma dmar mo lcags sgrog /
NK013(pa)014:756: ral gcig ma ljang khu dril bu 'dzin pa bzhis mdun g.yas rgyab g.yon nas 'khril ba /
NK013(pa)014:757: rang dang rta mgrin rigs lngar bcas pa'i yab kyi rdo rje la phata /
NK013(pa)014:758: yum gyi pad+ma la yang phata kyis mtshan pa /
NK013(pa)014:762: a nu r+aa ga ya mya /
NK013(pa)014:763: dza h'u bam hmohbo d+hi tsit+ta /
NK013(pa)014:764: s+pha ra na phatah sam ha ra na h'uh zhes
NK013(pa)014:765: rang yi dam yab yum sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang
NK013(pa)014:766: chub sems kyi 'od zer rta mgrin yab yum la
NK013(pa)014:767: phog / de rol pa mdzad pa'i byang chub sems sprin rigs lnga yab yum bcu la phog ste /
NK013(pa)014:768: de dag rol par mdzad pa'i byang chub sems kyi
NK013(pa)014:769: 'od zer gyis sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs yang
NK013(pa)014:770: dag pa'i ye shes kyi bdud rtsi bkug ste dam
NK013(pa)014:771: tshig gi bdud rtsi dang ro gcig tu gyur /
NK013(pa)014:782: +aah'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aah rdo rjes dkrug ste lan nyer gcig gam bdun brjod nas /
NK013(pa)014:783: theb srin nyi zla'i skyogs kyis /
NK013(pa)014:785: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro chos skyongs mchod //
NK013(pa)014:788: rnal 'byor mched rnams sdig sgrib dag par gyur yang gtor /
NK013(pa)014:789: +aa h'u mchod rdzas dang gnas khang gi nyes skyon dag par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:790: rdo rje'i rtses 'thor zhing rdo rje gsor la /
NK013(pa)014:791: +aahmh'u gang zhig bka' rku ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:794: nyam pa la mi dbang ba snod ma yin pa'i bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu po dag la /
NK013(pa)014:795: nga yi ye shes kyi bdud rtsis chu rgyun 'di
NK013(pa)014:796: phog pa tsam gyis lus srog sgyu ma rdul du
NK013(pa)014:797: brlag nas thams cad med par byos shig /
NK013(pa)014:798: gang zhig dam tshig dang ldan pa rnams kyi thugs dam bskangs bar mdzod cig /
NK013(pa)014:799: rig can rnams kyi dam tshig ni //
NK013(pa)014:800: rig med rnams la dbab mi 'gyur //
NK013(pa)014:801: rig can rang gi dam tshig las //
NK013(pa)014:802: sangs rgyas kun kyang 'da' ba min //
NK013(pa)014:807: kha chod zla ba rdo rje lam theb srin gyi rta mgrin bzhugs par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:810: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las lcang lor bcas pa'i
NK013(pa)014:811: dung chen du ra las ngo bo ye shes la
NK013(pa)014:812: rnam pa 'jig rten rtsi bcud srog gi rten 'byung
NK013(pa)014:813: rak+ta'i rgya mtsho / dmar gyi sbu phreng lha mo'i sprin dang /
NK013(pa)014:816: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h'u h'u h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:818: rdo rjes dkrug ste gtor zhing /
NK013(pa)014:819: h'u de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud tshims /
NK013(pa)014:820: h'u chos skyongs rnams kyi thugs dam bskangs /
NK013(pa)014:821: h'u bgegs rig stong phrag brgyad cu rdul du brlag par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:822: rang gi lce la lan gsum blang ste /
NK013(pa)014:823: snying gar zla gam gyi mtshan ma btab bo //
NK013(pa)014:826: stong pa'i ngang las b+han+da rin po che'i gzhal med
NK013(pa)014:827: khang yongs su rdzogs pa ril cha dgu ldan la
NK013(pa)014:828: / dbus byang sems dkar por h'u //
NK013(pa)014:829: de'i mdun mi ro dmar skya la m+aum //
NK013(pa)014:830: shar dri chen ser po la +amo //
NK013(pa)014:831: lhor sha chen sngon po la s+w+aam //
NK013(pa)014:832: nub tu pad+ma rak+ta dmar po la +aam //
NK013(pa)014:833: byang du dri chu ljang gu la h+aa //
NK013(pa)014:834: shar lhor glang po che'i ro dkar po la l+aam /
NK013(pa)014:835: lho nub tu rta ro sngon po la m+aam /
NK013(pa)014:836: nub byang rma bya'i ro ljang ku la b+aam /
NK013(pa)014:837: byang shar khyi ro dkar po la t+aam /
NK013(pa)014:839: rang gi thugs ka nas nyi dkyil h'u gis mtshan pa spros /
NK013(pa)014:840: ma dag pa thams cad bsregs /
NK013(pa)014:842: pad+ma +aam gyis mtshan pas yig 'bru bcu po bdud rtsir gyur /
NK013(pa)014:844: zla dkyil gyi mtshan pa bdud rtsis steng du kha
NK013(pa)014:845: chod gnas pa'i dbus +amo las gzugs rdo rje ma
NK013(pa)014:847: sgra rdo rje pi wam sgreng ba sngo //
NK013(pa)014:848: dri rdo rje spos khang thogs pa ser //
NK013(pa)014:849: ro rdo rje ro brgya ba'i zhal zas thogs pa dmar //
NK013(pa)014:850: reg rdo rje na baza'i gong ba rdo rjes mtshan pa bres pa ljang //
NK013(pa)014:851: chos rdo rje e grub gsum 'dzin pa mthing mdog ste /
NK013(pa)014:852: 'dod pa'i yon tan khams drug gis mchod pa dpag
NK013(pa)014:853: tu med pas rgyal ba mchod cing ting nge 'dzin
NK013(pa)014:854: gyi mdzes sdug sgyu ma'i 'gying bas rol pa can
NK013(pa)014:855: / gtor ma kun bzang nam mkha'i gter du gyur /
NK013(pa)014:856: ba lim ta te dz+wa la lim ta /
NK013(pa)014:858: gu h+ya sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:860: rgyud kyi rgyal po las phreng las 'byung ba'i mchod
NK013(pa)014:861: sprin byin rlab dang rol mo'i byin rlabs lhag chad
NK013(pa)014:862: kha bskong yig brgya dang bcas rol mo bskul nas
NK013(pa)014:863: snang spyod dag pa bde chen du shes par bya'o
NK013(pa)014:864: // gnyis pa dngos gzhi la yang gnyis /
NK013(pa)014:865: sems bskyed pa dang rnal 'byor dngos la 'jug pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:866: dang po la'ang kun rdzob dang /
NK013(pa)014:869: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK013(pa)014:870: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK013(pa)014:871: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK013(pa)014:872: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK013(pa)014:874: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)014:875: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK013(pa)014:876: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK013(pa)014:877: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK013(pa)014:878: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK013(pa)014:879: rdzogs pa'i sangs 'gag pa med las 'gag pa nyid
NK013(pa)014:880: na e ma ho rdzogs pa'i gnas pa med las
NK013(pa)014:881: gnas pa nyid na e ma ho rdzogs pa'i dmigs
NK013(pa)014:882: pa med dmigs pa nyid e ma ho ngo mtshar
NK013(pa)014:883: rmad kyi chos // rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang /
NK013(pa)014:889: ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis khog dbub pa /
NK013(pa)014:891: cho 'phrul bzhis gzhung bsrang nas tshogs pa sku yi rnal 'byor /
NK013(pa)014:892: thugs dam bskul zhing bzlas pa gsung gi rnal 'byor /
NK013(pa)014:893: mnyam par bzhag pa'i ting 'dzin phra mo'i mjug ldang thugs kyi rnal 'byor te bzhi las /
NK013(pa)014:895: dang po de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin ni /
NK013(pa)014:896: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med par /
NK013(pa)014:897: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK013(pa)014:898: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK013(pa)014:899: de phyir dngos po dngos med pa'o /
NK013(pa)014:901: / +amo ma h+aa shu mya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa w+aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:902: phyi nang gi chos 'di ltar snang ba thams cad
NK013(pa)014:903: ye gdod ma nyid nas rang bzhin med pa'i de
NK013(pa)014:904: kho na nyid spros pa kun dang bral ba sems
NK013(pa)014:907: de bzhin nyid ni spros med kyang //
NK013(pa)014:908: rang bzhin kun tu snang ba'i dbyings //
NK013(pa)014:909: lus dang ngag sems chos thams cad //
NK013(pa)014:910: gang na'ang ni mi dmigs pa /
NK013(pa)014:911: mig yor tshul du sbyar ba yis //
NK013(pa)014:912: sems can kun la snying brtse'i phyir //
NK013(pa)014:913: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK013(pa)014:914: stong pa nyid dang dbyer med pa'i /
NK013(pa)014:916: / 'gags med snying rje sgyu ma kun khyab 'dzin med ni //
NK013(pa)014:917: ma rtogs sems can gyi yul nam mkha'i mtha' khyab pa de snyed du gsal bar gyur //
NK013(pa)014:919: dngos po med las dngos po'i sprin //
NK013(pa)014:921: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK013(pa)014:922: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK013(pa)014:923: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK013(pa)014:924: yi ge yid bzhin rin chen sprin //
NK013(pa)014:925: yi ge mchog ni bsgom par bya //
NK013(pa)014:926: ah rab tu brtan gyur a dkar las //
NK013(pa)014:927: shin tu phra ba'i a rnams spro //
NK013(pa)014:928: phyogs bcu gang bar gsal gyur nas //
NK013(pa)014:930: de las ming tshor gsal 'bar kun //
NK013(pa)014:931: spro zhing bsdu ba'ang de bzhin no /
NK013(pa)014:933: / 'di ni rdo rje dngos grub kyi //
NK013(pa)014:934: brtan 'byung ye shes rgyu yin no //
NK013(pa)014:935: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i snying rje las yi
NK013(pa)014:936: ge a yig dkar po gzhi rtsar bzhugs pa gsal
NK013(pa)014:939: de las nam mkha'i mtha' klas par spros /
NK013(pa)014:941: de thams cad kyang gzhi po'i a la thim ste
NK013(pa)014:942: 'phel 'grib med pa'i byang chub sems kyi mtshan nyid
NK013(pa)014:943: brtan par gyur / gnyis pa la /
NK013(pa)014:952: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo a dkar po las /
NK013(pa)014:953: e yam bam lam sum ram rnams chad /
NK013(pa)014:954: 'od zer spro ba dang bsdu bas 'byung lnga'i rtog
NK013(pa)014:955: pa bsal te yum lnga'i mkha' klong du dag par
NK013(pa)014:956: byas / e las chos kyi 'byung gnas zur gsum
NK013(pa)014:957: mthing ka rgya khyon nam mkha' ltar 'byams klas pa'i
NK013(pa)014:958: byas / dbus su / yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor sra zhing mkhregs pa /
NK013(pa)014:959: kha dog dud ka dbyib zla gam zur la ba dan g.yo bas mtshan pa'i steng /
NK013(pa)014:960: bam las chu yi dkyil 'khor dkar zlum bum pas brgyan pa /
NK013(pa)014:961: de yi steng lam las gser gyis dkyil gru bzhi ser po /
NK013(pa)014:962: rdo rje dang bum pas mdzes pa'i steng /
NK013(pa)014:963: sum las ri yi rgyal po ri rab rin po
NK013(pa)014:964: che sna tshogs pa bkra zhing dbyibs gru bzhi kha
NK013(pa)014:965: khyer dang rgya mnyam pa'i thog /
NK013(pa)014:966: ram las phyi rol kun tu ye shes kyi me sna lnga pa 'bar ba'i dbus /
NK013(pa)014:967: h'u mthing nag dang sna tshogs rdo rje las skyes
NK013(pa)014:968: pa'i sra brtan rdo rje'i gur khang srung ba'i 'khor
NK013(pa)014:969: lo rdo rje'i sa gzhi ra ba 'bar ba dang
NK013(pa)014:972: de yi nang du rgyu yi a las b+h+r+aum chad /
NK013(pa)014:973: 'od zer spro bsdus tha mal pa'i gnas kyi 'dzin pa bsal te dag pa'i zhing du byas /
NK013(pa)014:975: b+h+r+aum yongs su gyur pa las chos kyi dbyings rang
NK013(pa)014:976: bzhin ye shes rin po che sna tshogs 'bar ba
NK013(pa)014:977: thar pa chen po'i gzhal med khang gru bzhi sgo
NK013(pa)014:978: bzhi / rgya khyon tshad bzung du med pa'i nang
NK013(pa)014:979: nas mthing dkar ser dmar ljang ba'i rtsig pa rim
NK013(pa)014:981: shar gyi logs dkar po 'khor lo //
NK013(pa)014:982: lho ser po rin po che /
NK013(pa)014:985: steng mthing nag rdo rjes brgyan pa ste /
NK013(pa)014:986: rigs drug pa'i thugs ye shes kyi 'od zer mtha' yas pas khyab pa /
NK013(pa)014:987: de yi steng gser gyi pha gu 'phyang ba'i ngos chu na 'phyang phreng ba gcus pa'i steng /
NK013(pa)014:988: rin po che'i phra tshom can gyi mdzes gdung gis
NK013(pa)014:989: mnan pa'i ka thung nyer brgyad bar seng mgo las
NK013(pa)014:990: 'phyang 'phrul mu tig gi d+r+wa ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:994: de las zla ba dang rnga yab chen po'i bsil yab bskyod pa'i thog /
NK013(pa)014:995: bya 'dab las rin po che dkar po'i shar bu /
NK013(pa)014:996: steng na mda' yab shel gyi mchod rten dbyibs can
NK013(pa)014:997: gyis yongs su bskor ba'i pad+ma'i gdan la zur bzhir
NK013(pa)014:998: gdugs dang / ba dan dang rgyal mtshan brgyad brgyad dang /
NK013(pa)014:999: rdo rje'i 'phan lha rdzas kyis gos rnam par bkra ba lhab lhub tu g.yo bas brgyan pa /
NK013(pa)014:1000: nyi ma dang zla ba phyed pa dang rang pa'i
NK013(pa)014:1001: skar khung lding ba'i phyogs ta ra na yis bzung
NK013(pa)014:1002: ba / rtsig pa'i phyi 'gram 'dod yon gyi snam
NK013(pa)014:1003: bu dmar po gru bzhi kun du 'khor ba'i bar
NK013(pa)014:1004: snang d+r+wa ba'i gseb dang kha khyer la gzugs kyi
NK013(pa)014:1005: rdo rje sogs gzungs ma kha dog sna tshogs pas
NK013(pa)014:1006: mchod rdzas sna tshogs pa thogs te bcom ldan 'das
NK013(pa)014:1007: la mchod pa dang rol mo sna tshogs sprin ltar
NK013(pa)014:1008: ba / gtib pa / sgo bzhi'i mdun stegs bu
NK013(pa)014:1009: gru bzhi pa'i steng bum pa la gnas pa'i ka
NK013(pa)014:1010: ba bzhi bzhis btegs pa'i rta babs gsal ba'i mthong
NK013(pa)014:1011: khong rdo rje'i 'greng rwa dang bcas pa la /
NK013(pa)014:1012: rta rkang chu skyes rin chen sgrom /
NK013(pa)014:1013: ma skyes thabs kyis zar tshags /
NK013(pa)014:1015: sna tshogs khyung mgo rims par 'khrigs /
NK013(pa)014:1016: zhes pa'i snam bu rim pa brgyad ldan /
NK013(pa)014:1020: rnga yab dril bu g.yo zhing mdzes pa'i rtse mor
NK013(pa)014:1021: gdugs dang pad+ma'i bar na chos 'khor g.yas g.yon ri
NK013(pa)014:1022: dwags pho mo dang bcas pa /
NK013(pa)014:1023: glang seng ngang pa ri dwags dang /
NK013(pa)014:1024: khye'u chung klu phrug chu srin khyung /
NK013(pa)014:1025: sgo khang gi rgyan dgu dang /
NK013(pa)014:1027: g.yas g.yon gyi gzhi la mkha' 'gro so gnyis kyi
NK013(pa)014:1028: gnas ta la'i ljon shing so gnyis te phyogs rer
NK013(pa)014:1029: brgyad re la gser gyi d+r+wa ba sbrel zhing /
NK013(pa)014:1030: gser gyi tsong tsong bres ba /
NK013(pa)014:1031: de dang grangs mtshungs dpag bsam gyi shing man+d+h+aara ba'i
NK013(pa)014:1032: me tog bkra shis zhing chos sgra sgrogs pa'i sprul
NK013(pa)014:1033: pa'i bya skad snyan par sgrogs pa gnas pa /
NK013(pa)014:1035: bar na rin po che sna bdun pa'i ri dang /
NK013(pa)014:1036: sprin gseb na mchod pa'i lha mo gar rtse ba /
NK013(pa)014:1037: yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa'i bdud rtsi khrus rdzing dang /
NK013(pa)014:1039: me tog dkar po'i gling rnams na dad pa can
NK013(pa)014:1040: chos nyan pa'i gnas rin po che sna bdun dang
NK013(pa)014:1041: / bkra shis pa'i rdzas sogs 'dod yon gyi sprin gtib pa'i pho brang gi zur bzhi dang /
NK013(pa)014:1042: sgo dang sgo khyud phyi mtshams la zla phyed rdo rje nor bu 'bar ba gnas pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:1043: gzhal med khang kun du yang nang du gyur pa'i
NK013(pa)014:1044: bar khyams gru bzhi kun nas bskor ba'i gru chad
NK013(pa)014:1045: bzhi la glo bur mkhar thabs bzhi yis brgyan pa'i
NK013(pa)014:1046: dbus rdo rje'i phreng ba'i nang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi
NK013(pa)014:1047: pa ser po rtsibs mchan sngon po'i lte ba zlum
NK013(pa)014:1048: po mthing ka dang bcas pa /
NK013(pa)014:1049: bla na med pa'i rtags rim pa bzhin rdo rje'i 'greng bu res sbags shing /
NK013(pa)014:1050: rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i zlum bskor la brten pa /
NK013(pa)014:1054: byang ral gri'i brgyan pa'i ka ba gnyis gnyis brgyad
NK013(pa)014:1055: kyis btegs pa'i rdo rje'i gdung bzhis mig mang ris
NK013(pa)014:1056: su bres shing mdzes par phub pa'i ka rgyan dang
NK013(pa)014:1057: ka zhu thams cad rin po che 'bar ba las
NK013(pa)014:1058: byas pa / phyam tsa rin po che'i gdung phran nyer brgyad phyogs bzhir bzhi bzhi /
NK013(pa)014:1060: phyam rtse gdung thung nyer brgyad mthud pa /
NK013(pa)014:1061: de yang bya skyibs lnga ldan gzhal med khang gi
NK013(pa)014:1062: thog sangs rgyas kyi gtsug tor ltar zlum por 'khyil
NK013(pa)014:1063: ba'i chos kyi sku yi pho brang mchod rten bum
NK013(pa)014:1064: dbyibs bre dang chos 'khor 'phan dang zar tshags nyi
NK013(pa)014:1065: zla rdo rje rin po che'i tog gis mdzes pa'i
NK013(pa)014:1066: / 'og min gyi zhing rang snang rnam dag stug po bkod pa /
NK013(pa)014:1067: snang la rang bzhin ma grub cing /
NK013(pa)014:1068: bde la sgrib pa med par gsal ba /
NK013(pa)014:1069: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes chos kyi 'khor lo'i
NK013(pa)014:1070: gdan gyi lte ba la pho brang rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK013(pa)014:1071: rgyas kyi bkod pa khyad par 'phags pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:1072: gzhal yas dbus kyi lte ba la smon lam grub pa'i gdan mi 'jigs bzhi'i rtags seng ge /
NK013(pa)014:1073: rtsibs bzhi'i shar du stobs bcu ldan phyir glang po /
NK013(pa)014:1075: nub tu dbang bcu rma bya /
NK013(pa)014:1076: byang 'phrin las bzhi mkha' lding rnams brgyad brgyad kyis
NK013(pa)014:1077: btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri mdzod mig bdun bdun
NK013(pa)014:1078: dang ldan pa rin po che 'od 'bar ba'i ka
NK013(pa)014:1079: ba can / mu tig gi d+r+wa bas ngos g.yogs
NK013(pa)014:1080: shing mdzes pa phul du byung ba'i steng yon tan
NK013(pa)014:1081: gyis nyes tshogs bcom pa'i gdan sna tshogs pad+ma 'dab
NK013(pa)014:1082: ma stong dang ldan pa'i dbus na nyi ma dang
NK013(pa)014:1083: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor re re ste lnga brtsegs /
NK013(pa)014:1084: glo 'bur bzhi gru chad bzhi ste brgyad du rin
NK013(pa)014:1085: po che'i khri chung dang pad nyi zla ba bzhi
NK013(pa)014:1086: brtsegs / lha snam shar nub drang po gnyis su pad+ma nyi zla gsum brtsegs //
NK013(pa)014:1087: mtshams bzhi lho nub gnyis dang drug tu pad kyang re re /
NK013(pa)014:1088: sgo bzhir nyi ma la bdud bzhi dkar ser dmar ljang dang bcas pa gsal bar gyur /
NK013(pa)014:1089: slar yang gsal gdab cing dag pa dran pa'i phyir /
NK013(pa)014:1090: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags te //
NK013(pa)014:1091: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun grub ni //
NK013(pa)014:1092: rdzogs chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK013(pa)014:1096: phyogs bcur rgya yang ma chad pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:1097: yon tan khyad par 'phags pa ni //
NK013(pa)014:1098: gsang ba yum gyi ba ga la //
NK013(pa)014:1099: bcu gsum dbang phyug ldan pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:1100: rdo rje 'chang chen dpag med dang //
NK013(pa)014:1101: til 'bru'i tshul du rab tu gnas //
NK013(pa)014:1102: chos rnams kun gyi de bzhin nyid //
NK013(pa)014:1103: thog ma tha ma dbus med pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:1104: rang bzhin don gyi 'og min ni //
NK013(pa)014:1105: rgyal ba kun gyi pho brang phyir /
NK013(pa)014:1107: / 'das dang da ltar ma byon pa //
NK013(pa)014:1108: rgyal ba kun gyi rten pa'i gnas //
NK013(pa)014:1109: chos rnams sna tshogs ji snyed pa //
NK013(pa)014:1110: dngos po mtha' dag med phyir zlum //
NK013(pa)014:1111: khyab dang dpag dang tshad med dang //
NK013(pa)014:1112: ye shes bzhi phyir 'khor lo bstan //
NK013(pa)014:1114: mu khyud zlum pos kun nas bskor //
NK013(pa)014:1115: sku gsung thugs dang byin rlabs dang //
NK013(pa)014:1116: thugs rje ma khyab med pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)014:1117: yongs sangs rgyas pa'i dbyings su bstan //
NK013(pa)014:1118: rang byung ye shes mtha' bral bas //
NK013(pa)014:1120: tshad dang bral ba'i sems kyi phyir /
NK013(pa)014:1121: gzhi rtsa tshad med 'khor lor bstan //
NK013(pa)014:1122: gdod nas byin rlabs ngo bo'i phyir //
NK013(pa)014:1123: ma bsags lhun rdzogs mdzad nyid de /
NK013(pa)014:1126: rin chen 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK013(pa)014:1127: sna tshogs dngos dang dngos med pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:1128: chos kun ngo bor rang gnas te //
NK013(pa)014:1129: bdag gzhan gzung 'dzin bral ba'i phyir //
NK013(pa)014:1130: phyi dang nang bral sgrib pa med //
NK013(pa)014:1131: thun mong la brten thabs kyi 'bras //
NK013(pa)014:1132: ye shes thabs kyis 'phags pa nyid //
NK013(pa)014:1133: gdul bya'i blo la mngon snang ba //
NK013(pa)014:1134: glo 'bur bzhi ni lhag par mdzes //
NK013(pa)014:1135: thun mong thun mong ma yin pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:1136: gdul bya'i rim pa mtho dman kun //
NK013(pa)014:1138: de phyir ye shes sgo bzhir bshad //
NK013(pa)014:1139: thabs mang bsam gyis mi khyab pas //
NK013(pa)014:1140: lam brgyad rim par bgrod pa yi /
NK013(pa)014:1142: / 'bras bus yon tan kun rdzogs pas //
NK013(pa)014:1143: rta babs rgyu 'bras bcu drug bstan //
NK013(pa)014:1144: zhen dang sbang ba'i lam bral ba /
NK013(pa)014:1146: / 'dod yon ye shes lngar rol te //
NK013(pa)014:1147: bdag mchod kun mnyes las 'byung bas /
NK013(pa)014:1149: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:1150: ma chags thabs dang ldan pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:1151: che ba'i yon tan lhun rdzogs pas //
NK013(pa)014:1152: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che //
NK013(pa)014:1153: las dang thugs rje smon lam gyi //
NK013(pa)014:1154: byang chub sems dpa' mthu bo che //
NK013(pa)014:1155: smon lam dbang gis de dag tu //
NK013(pa)014:1156: thos pa rgya mtsho bsags phyir gnas //
NK013(pa)014:1157: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis kyis brgyan //
NK013(pa)014:1158: seng ge glang chen rta dang khyung //
NK013(pa)014:1159: nam mkha'i lding gi khri chen te //
NK013(pa)014:1160: rang byung dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub //
NK013(pa)014:1161: thams cad ngo bo gcig pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)014:1162: rtse mo kun tu zlum por 'khyil //
NK013(pa)014:1163: tshad med bzhi yi don brtson nas //
NK013(pa)014:1164: dgos 'dod re skong don grub phyir //
NK013(pa)014:1165: sgo bzhi g.yas g.yon ljon shing dang //
NK013(pa)014:1166: dpag bsam shing zung tsong tsong 'phel //
NK013(pa)014:1167: dril bu g.yer ga theg sgrogs pa //
NK013(pa)014:1168: bkra shis bya snyan sgra sgrogs ldan //
NK013(pa)014:1169: yid bzhin rin chen brgyad bskor bas //
NK013(pa)014:1170: rin chen phung po bzhi gnyis ldan //
NK013(pa)014:1171: thams cad la ni dbang sgyur phyir //
NK013(pa)014:1172: lha chen phyogs skyong brgyad kyis bskor //
NK013(pa)014:1173: gnyis pa lha gsal ba la gsum /
NK013(pa)014:1178: gzhi yi a dkar po las k+shahsngona po byung /
NK013(pa)014:1179: a dang k+sha'i khyad par las yi ge bzhi bcu gnyis su byung ste /
NK013(pa)014:1180: so so'i gdan la 'khod de thabs shes mtshon pa'i log drang gis bzhugs pa /
NK013(pa)014:1182: rtsibs bzhi'i shar du ta ta dkar /
NK013(pa)014:1190: gru chad shar lhor pa ya dkar /
NK013(pa)014:1191: lho nub tu pha wa ser /
NK013(pa)014:1193: byang shar du b+ha la ljang /
NK013(pa)014:1194: khyams kyi shar lho i dkar /
NK013(pa)014:1203: byang sgor o oo ta ljang /
NK013(pa)014:1204: slar yang k+sha nyi khyams kyi shar drang por bzhugs /
NK013(pa)014:1205: a las a zhig byung nub drang po bzhugs gzhi
NK013(pa)014:1206: bo'i a de yig 'bru thams cad la thim pas
NK013(pa)014:1207: gsal zhing 'bar te slar yang 'od zer grangs med
NK013(pa)014:1208: pa 'phros / mkha' khyab 'di gnyis gcig tu bsdu'ang gsum /
NK013(pa)014:1210: kyi 'phags pa'i gsung gi rgyud bskul /
NK013(pa)014:1212: 'gro ba sems can gyi tha mal ba'i ngag gi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK013(pa)014:1213: slar 'dus yig 'brur thim ste yongs su gyur pa las /
NK013(pa)014:1215: dbus su rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK013(pa)014:1216: rtsibs kyi shar 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK013(pa)014:1217: lhor rin po che dang dril bu /
NK013(pa)014:1218: nub tu pad+ma dang dril bu /
NK013(pa)014:1219: byang du ral gri dang dril bu /
NK013(pa)014:1220: glo 'bur shar rin po che'i myu gu dang me long /
NK013(pa)014:1221: lho ru ral gri dang rin po che'i phreng ba /
NK013(pa)014:1222: nub tu pad+ma dkar po dang pi wam /
NK013(pa)014:1223: byang du rdo rje dang gar gyi lag pa /
NK013(pa)014:1224: gru chad bzhi'i shar lhor klu shing dang /
NK013(pa)014:1226: lho nub tu chos kyi 'khor lo dang me tog gi phreng ba /
NK013(pa)014:1227: nub byang du rin po che'i snye ma dang mar me /
NK013(pa)014:1228: byang shar du ut+pala dang dri chab /
NK013(pa)014:1229: khyams kyi shar du rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga /
NK013(pa)014:1233: lhor mkhar bsil dang lhung bzed /
NK013(pa)014:1234: nub byang du chos kyi glegs bam /
NK013(pa)014:1235: lho nub tu rin po che'i sgrom bu /
NK013(pa)014:1237: shar sgor thod dbyug dang lcags kyu /
NK013(pa)014:1238: lho sgor rdo rje'i dbyug pa dang zhags pa /
NK013(pa)014:1239: nub sgor pad ma'i dbyug pa dang lcags sgrog /
NK013(pa)014:1240: byang sgor rgya gram gyi dbyug pa dang dril bu rnams las 'od zer grangs med pa 'phros /
NK013(pa)014:1241: mkha' khyab bde bar gshegs pa'i thugs kyi rgyud bskul /
NK013(pa)014:1243: 'gro ba sems can gyi tha mal pa'i yid kyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK013(pa)014:1244: slar phyag mtshan la thim ste yongs su gyur pa las /
NK013(pa)014:1246: rigs lnga bya byed sangs rgyas gdan //
NK013(pa)014:1247: thub drug sems dpa' sems ma'i gdan //
NK013(pa)014:1248: khro rgyal sgo ba sgo ma'i gdan //
NK013(pa)014:1249: ces pa ltar rim pa bzhin du bskyed de /
NK013(pa)014:1251: m+aum d+ha t+wi shwa ri ti /
NK013(pa)014:1252: sems nyid rdo rje dril bu la sogs pa sku
NK013(pa)014:1253: phra mor gnas 'gyur bzhin 'od zer grangs med pa
NK013(pa)014:1254: 'phros / mkha' khyab bde bar gshegs pa'i sku yi rgyud bskul /
NK013(pa)014:1256: 'gro ba sems can gyi tha mal pa'i lus kyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK013(pa)014:1257: sku phra mo grangs med pa spro ba dang bsdu ba mdzad de /
NK013(pa)014:1258: dbus kyi gdan la rang nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal
NK013(pa)014:1259: thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rdo rje sems dpa' bde
NK013(pa)014:1260: ba chen po mi bskyod pa'i skur gyur pa ni
NK013(pa)014:1261: / rnam shes kyi phung po dang zhe sdang ma
NK013(pa)014:1262: spang gnas su dag pa chos kyi dbyings kyi ye
NK013(pa)014:1263: shes las byung ba'i rtags su sku mdog mthing ka
NK013(pa)014:1264: in+t+ra ni la dang nam mkha' 'dres pa'i lta bur
NK013(pa)014:1266: zhal g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus sku dang mthun pa
NK013(pa)014:1267: dbu ra la pa'i thor tshugs nag po 'gying ba
NK013(pa)014:1268: rin po che'i rtse bran can /
NK013(pa)014:1269: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu bsnol bas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK013(pa)014:1271: tha ma na rin po che /
NK013(pa)014:1272: g.yon bar ma na pad ma /
NK013(pa)014:1273: tha ma na ral gri 'dzin pa'i phyag rgya de dag la ye shes kyi me 'bar ba /
NK013(pa)014:1274: phyi nang ni mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK013(pa)014:1275: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus spras pa /
NK013(pa)014:1276: zhabs mnyam pa'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa'i bar
NK013(pa)014:1277: du yum snang ba nam mkha' rnam par dag pa
NK013(pa)014:1278: rdo rje dbyings phyug ma mthing ka /
NK013(pa)014:1279: zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK013(pa)014:1280: g.yon pas rdo rje'i dril bu bsnams pa /
NK013(pa)014:1281: brtul zhugs skyil mo krung gis 'khril ba'o /
NK013(pa)014:1286: gzugs phung dang gti mug bcos slad med par dag
NK013(pa)014:1287: pa me long lta bu'i ye shes las byung ba'i
NK013(pa)014:1288: rtags su / de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par snang mdzad sku mdog zla ba ltar dkar ba /
NK013(pa)014:1289: dkar sngo dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang
NK013(pa)014:1290: po gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bus yum la 'khyud
NK013(pa)014:1291: pa / g.yas rdo rje rin po che /
NK013(pa)014:1293: yum sra ba sa dag pa spyan ma dkar mo
NK013(pa)014:1294: g.yas yab la 'khyud cing g.yon 'khor lo'i dril bu
NK013(pa)014:1297: lhor tshor phud dang nga rgyal gsal stong du dag
NK013(pa)014:1298: pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes las byung ba'i
NK013(pa)014:1299: rtags su / de bzhin gshegs pa rin chen 'byung ldan gser btso ma'i kha dog can /
NK013(pa)014:1300: ser sngo dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang
NK013(pa)014:1301: po gnyis rin po che dang dril bus yum la
NK013(pa)014:1303: g.yon pad ma ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)014:1304: yum mnyen pa chu khams dag pa m+aa ma k+ai
NK013(pa)014:1305: ser mo g.yas yab la 'khyud cing g.yon rin po
NK013(pa)014:1309: nub tu 'du shes kyi phung po dang 'dod chags
NK013(pa)014:1310: bde stong du dag pa so sor rtog pa'i ye
NK013(pa)014:1312: de bzhin gshegs pa snang ba mtha' yas pad+ma r+aa ga ltar dmar ba /
NK013(pa)014:1313: dmar dkar sngo ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi phyag
NK013(pa)014:1314: dang po gnyis pad+ma dang dril bus yum la 'khyud
NK013(pa)014:1316: g.yon rin chen ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)014:1317: yum dro ba me khams dag pa gos dkar mo
NK013(pa)014:1318: dmar mo g.yas yab la 'khyud cing g.yon pad+ma'i dril
NK013(pa)014:1320: tam badz+ra ra ti byang du /
NK013(pa)014:1321: 'du byed kyi phung po dang phrag dog rang grol
NK013(pa)014:1322: du dag pa bya ba grub pa'i ye shes las
NK013(pa)014:1324: de bzhin gshegs pa don yod grub pa mrgad ltar ljang ba /
NK013(pa)014:1325: ljang dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang
NK013(pa)014:1326: po gnyis ral gri dang dril bus yum la 'khyud
NK013(pa)014:1329: yum bskyod pa rlung dag pa dam tshig sgrol ma ljang gu g.yas yab la 'khyud cing /
NK013(pa)014:1330: g.yon ral gri'i dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)014:1331: bde bar gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas pa de dag thams cad kyang /
NK013(pa)014:1332: gnag snum ral pa'i thor tshugs 'gying ba rin po che'i rtse bran gyis mdzes pa /
NK013(pa)014:1333: kha sbyor sgyu ma'i bde ba'i lang tsho dar la bab cing /
NK013(pa)014:1334: mdzes pa thams cad kyi phul du gyur pa /
NK013(pa)014:1335: phyi nang gi mtshan gyi me tog la dpe byad kyi 'bras bu chags pa /
NK013(pa)014:1336: snyan gong g.yas g.yon ut+pala mdzes shing /
NK013(pa)014:1338: snyan cha phyag zhabs dpung pa'i gdu bu /
NK013(pa)014:1341: do shal te rin po che'i rgyan brgyad dang /
NK013(pa)014:1342: lha rdzas kyi dar dkar po gser gyi ngang ris can gyi stod g.yogs /
NK013(pa)014:1344: kha dog sna tshogs pa'i cod pan /
NK013(pa)014:1345: zi ldir gar gyi phu rung ste dar gyi chas gos lnga yis klubs pa /
NK013(pa)014:1346: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can /
NK013(pa)014:1347: gsal 'tsher lhun stug gzi byin ldan pa ste zhi ba'i nyams dgus rgyas pa /
NK013(pa)014:1348: yab yum de rnams ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku
NK013(pa)014:1349: ste kha dog drug ldan 'od zer bye ba phrag
NK013(pa)014:1350: drug re 'bar ba'i klong na bde stong gnyis med
NK013(pa)014:1351: kyi ye shes la yab rnams mnyam pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:1352: yum rnams brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung gis rol pa /
NK013(pa)014:1353: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med pa'i rtags yab yum zhal sbyor dang /
NK013(pa)014:1354: 'byung lnga chos dbyings su gzigs pas yab rnams yum la gzigs pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:1355: phung lnga ye shes su shar bas yum rnams yab la gzigs pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:1356: glo 'bur la nang sems bzhi ni /
NK013(pa)014:1357: 'di bi ma las rtsibs mchan la mdzad kyang slob
NK013(pa)014:1358: dpon pad+mas glo 'bur la 'god pa'i rjes su dam
NK013(pa)014:1359: pa bde bar gshegs pa bzang /
NK013(pa)014:1362: h'u l+aa s+ye sa ma s+t+wam /
NK013(pa)014:1363: shar du mthong ba mig shes rnams par dag pa byang chub chen po sa yi snying po dang /
NK013(pa)014:1364: yul gzugs dag pa yum lha mo sgegs mo ma
NK013(pa)014:1365: gnyis sku mdog dkar po yab kyi phyag g.yas na
NK013(pa)014:1366: rin po che'i myu gu dang /
NK013(pa)014:1367: g.yon dril bu dkur bstan pa /
NK013(pa)014:1368: yang na skyab sbyin mdzad gsungs /
NK013(pa)014:1370: yum gyis phyag g.yon na me long 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)014:1372: de gnyis ni rnam par snang mdzad kyi sku dang thugs las byung ba /
NK013(pa)014:1374: t+r+aam m+aa l+ye sa ma ya ho /
NK013(pa)014:1375: lhor snom pa sna shes rnam par dag pa byang chub chen po nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK013(pa)014:1376: yul dri dag pa yum rin po che'i phreng ba ma gnyis sku mdog ser po /
NK013(pa)014:1377: yab kyi phyag g.yas na ral gri /
NK013(pa)014:1379: yum gyis phyag gnyis na rin po che'i phreng ba thogs pas yab kyi dbu la thod bcing ba /
NK013(pa)014:1380: de gnyis ni rin 'byung gi sku dang thugs las skyes pa /
NK013(pa)014:1381: h+r+aim ha h'u pad+ma ba da ma /
NK013(pa)014:1383: nub tu myong ba lce shes rnam par dag pa byang chub chen po spyan ras gzigs dang /
NK013(pa)014:1384: yul ro dag pa yum lha mo dbyangs mkhan ma gnyis sku mdog dmar ba /
NK013(pa)014:1385: yab kyi phyag g.yas na pad+ma dkar po dang /
NK013(pa)014:1387: yum gyi phyag gnyis pi wam 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)014:1388: de gnyis ni snang mtha'i thugs las skyes pa /
NK013(pa)014:1389: dz+rim ku ru p+aa na h+r+aih a nirti r+aa ga y+aa mi /
NK013(pa)014:1390: byang du thos pa rna shes rnam par dag pa byang chub chen po phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK013(pa)014:1391: yul sgra dag pa yum lha mo gar mkhan ma gnyis sku mdog ljang ku /
NK013(pa)014:1392: yab kyi phyag g.yas na rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga pa /
NK013(pa)014:1394: yum gyi phyag gnyis gar gyi lag pa bsgyur nas /
NK013(pa)014:1395: zhal zas ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa yab kyi zhal du stobs pa /
NK013(pa)014:1396: de gnyis ni don yod grub pa'i thugs dang sku las skyes pa /
NK013(pa)014:1397: gru chad kyi zur bzhir phyi sems bzhi ni /
NK013(pa)014:1398: zur lugs pa bshad rgyud bzhed ltar dkar ser sogs khra bor mdzad kyang /
NK013(pa)014:1399: slob dpon pad+ma'i man ngag la dkar 'byams sogs mdzad pa kahthoga pa'i bzhed /
NK013(pa)014:1401: meem d+ha ra na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:1402: dzahd+h+au sh+pa pra we sha ya /
NK013(pa)014:1403: shar lhor mthong byed mig dbang dag pa byang chub chen po byams pa mgon po dang /
NK013(pa)014:1404: yul 'das pa dpyid kyi dus dag pa yum lha mo bdug spos ma gnyis sku mdog dkar po /
NK013(pa)014:1405: yab kyi phyag g.yas na me tog gi phang phung g.yo ba'i klu shing dang /
NK013(pa)014:1406: g.yon na gun+d+he ste ril ba spyi blugs /
NK013(pa)014:1407: yum gyi phyag gnyis bdug sprin 'thul ba'i spos khang 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)014:1408: th+l+him nis+sa ram b+h+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:1410: lho nub tu thos byed rna ba'i dbang po rnam
NK013(pa)014:1411: par dag pa byang chub chen po sgrib pa thams
NK013(pa)014:1412: cad rnam par sel ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:1413: yul da lta dbyar gyi dus dag pa yum lha
NK013(pa)014:1414: mo me tog ma gnyis sku mdog ser po yab
NK013(pa)014:1415: kyi phyag g.yas na chos kyi 'khor lo dang /
NK013(pa)014:1417: yum gyi phyag gnyis me tog gi phreng ba bsnams pa /
NK013(pa)014:1418: h'u s+w+aa r+aa dz+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:1419: bam d+ai ba su gi khi n+ai ri /
NK013(pa)014:1420: nub byang du snom byed sna dbang rnam par dag
NK013(pa)014:1421: pa byang chub chen po kun tu bzang po dang
NK013(pa)014:1422: / yul ma 'ongs pa ston gyi dus dag pa yum mar me gnyis sku mdog dmar po /
NK013(pa)014:1423: yab kyi phyag g.yas na rin po che'i snye ma dang /
NK013(pa)014:1425: yum gyi phyag g.yon mar me /
NK013(pa)014:1427: m+aum sh+r+ai a r+aa g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:1429: byang shar du myong byed lce dbang rnam par dag
NK013(pa)014:1430: pa byang chub chen po 'jam dpal gzhon nu dang
NK013(pa)014:1432: ma nges pa'i dgun dus dag pa yum lha mo
NK013(pa)014:1433: dri chab ma gnyis sku mdog ljang gu yab kyi
NK013(pa)014:1436: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyis dri chab dung phor bsnams pa /
NK013(pa)014:1437: de bzhi ni sna tshogs pa'i rigs sam rdo rje mi bskyod pa'i sku dang thugs las skyes pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:1438: sems dpa' sems ma de thams cad kyang zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK013(pa)014:1440: zhi ba'i tshul ldan cing rin po che dang dar gyi rgyan thams cad brgyan pa /
NK013(pa)014:1441: 'od zer grangs med pa'i klong na /
NK013(pa)014:1442: dbu ral pa'i thor tshugs dang bcas /
NK013(pa)014:1443: yab thams cad zhabs g.yas dang /
NK013(pa)014:1444: yum zhabs g.yon cung zad brkyang pa'i phyed dkyil gyis
NK013(pa)014:1445: yab yum zhal sbyor du gnas te thugs rjes sems
NK013(pa)014:1446: can thams cad la bu gcig pu la mas byams
NK013(pa)014:1447: pa bzhin dgongs te ye shes bde chen sgyu ma'i
NK013(pa)014:1448: ros sgegs pa / yab yum de rnams mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'o //
NK013(pa)014:1449: khyams la bya byed gnyis ni /
NK013(pa)014:1450: h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsit+ta a /
NK013(pa)014:1451: a a a badz+ri b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK013(pa)014:1452: shar drang po rtog tshogs rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du
NK013(pa)014:1453: shar bas rgyud thams cad kyi byed po yid rnam
NK013(pa)014:1454: par dag pa bcom ldan 'das yab rdo rje kun
NK013(pa)014:1455: tu bzang po sku mdog sngon po zhal gcig phyag
NK013(pa)014:1456: gnyis mnyam pa'i phyag rgya'i dkyil na rdo rje dkar
NK013(pa)014:1457: po rtse lnga pa las ye shes kyi 'od zer
NK013(pa)014:1458: 'phro ba / mkhyen pa'i ye shes shes bya'i dngos
NK013(pa)014:1459: po thams cad dbyings su gzigs pa'i rtags zhal nub
NK013(pa)014:1460: 'phro ba / tu gzigs pa / nub drang bor
NK013(pa)014:1461: chos 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas thams cad gnas
NK013(pa)014:1462: su dag pa byed pa bcom ldan 'das ma yum
NK013(pa)014:1463: kun tu bzang mo sku mdog dkar mo phyag gnyis
NK013(pa)014:1464: chos 'byung gi phyag rgya bcas te /
NK013(pa)014:1465: dbyings mkhyen pa dang ldan pa'i rtags zhal shar du gzigs pa /
NK013(pa)014:1466: gnyis ka yang mnyam pa'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK013(pa)014:1467: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan can /
NK013(pa)014:1468: yab yum de gnyis ni chos kyi sku'o //
NK013(pa)014:1469: khyams la thub pa drug ni /
NK013(pa)014:1471: shar lho rang rgyal dag pa lha yi thub pa
NK013(pa)014:1472: brgya sbyin dkar po phyag na pi wam 'dzin pa
NK013(pa)014:1473: / mu ne h'u t+r+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:1474: byang du phrag dog dag pa lha min gyi thub
NK013(pa)014:1475: pa thag bzang mthing ga go cha dang mtshon mdung
NK013(pa)014:1476: thung 'dzin pa / mu ne srum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:1477: lhor 'dod chags dag pa mi yi thub pa sh+aakya seng ge gser btso ma'i kha dog can /
NK013(pa)014:1478: bsreg shang dang par bu 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)014:1480: nub byang du gti mug dag pa byol song gi
NK013(pa)014:1481: thub pa seng ge dam brten ser nag chos kyi
NK013(pa)014:1484: lho nub tu ser sna dag pa yi dwags kyi
NK013(pa)014:1485: thub pa kha 'bar ma sngon po rin po che'i
NK013(pa)014:1488: byang shar du zhe sdang dag pa dmyal ba'i thub
NK013(pa)014:1489: pa chos kyi rgyal po sngon po phyag g.yas me
NK013(pa)014:1490: bsnams nas grang ba'i sdug bsngal bsil ba /
NK013(pa)014:1491: g.yon chu thogs nas tsha ba'i sdug bsngal bsil bar mdzad pa /
NK013(pa)014:1492: sku mdog sogs 'di dag sgyu 'phrul bla ma ste bshad rgyud kyis rtsa rgyud 'brel ba'i lugs yin /
NK013(pa)014:1494: kun kyang dbu gtsug tor dang ldan cing tshangs par spyod pa'i cha lugs can /
NK013(pa)014:1495: 'gro ba'i don la bsnyel ba mi mnga' bar gzhan bde ba'i don mdzad pa'i rtags su /
NK013(pa)014:1496: gdan la bzhengs stabs kyis rgyud drug gis 'gro ba sgrol ba /
NK013(pa)014:1497: thub pa de dag ni sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK013(pa)014:1499: h'u ya m+aan+ta kri tra phata /
NK013(pa)014:1501: ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa li ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:1502: shar sgor reg pa lus shes dag pa 'joms pa chen po gshin rje'i gshed dang /
NK013(pa)014:1503: rtag par ma yin pa'i yum mi pham ma gnyis sku mdog mthing nag /
NK013(pa)014:1504: yab kyi phyag g.yas na thod dbyug /
NK013(pa)014:1505: yum gyi g.yas na lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK013(pa)014:1506: phung po'i bdud kyi gdan la rol ba'o //
NK013(pa)014:1508: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa ri dz+wa li ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:1509: lho sgor reg byed lus dbang dag pa 'joms pa chen po stobs po che dang /
NK013(pa)014:1510: chad par ma yin pa'i yum khro gnyer ma gnyis
NK013(pa)014:1511: sku mdog ser nag yab kyi phyag g.yas na rdo
NK013(pa)014:1512: rje'i dbyug pa / yum gyi g.yas na zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK013(pa)014:1513: 'chi bdag gi bdud kyi gdan la rol pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:1516: ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa li ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:1517: nub sgor reg bya dbang yul dag pa 'joms pa chen po rta mgrin dang /
NK013(pa)014:1518: bdag tu ma yin pa'i yum ro lang ma gnyis sku mdog dmar nag /
NK013(pa)014:1519: yab kyi phyag g.yas na pad+ma'i dbyug pa sbrul gyis dkris pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:1520: yum gyi phyag g.yas lcags sgrog bsnams pa /
NK013(pa)014:1521: nyon mongs pa'i bdud kyi gdan la rol pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:1524: ma h+aa kro d+he shwa ri dz+aa li ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:1525: byang sgor reg shes 'dus byung dag pa 'joms pa chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:1526: mtshan mar ma yin pa'i yum ral gcig ma gnyis sku mdog ljang nag /
NK013(pa)014:1527: yab kyi phyag g.yas na rdo rje rgya gram gyi dbyug pa /
NK013(pa)014:1528: yum gyi g.yas gser gyi dril chen 'khrol ba /
NK013(pa)014:1529: lha yi bu'i bdud kyi gdan la rol pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:1530: kun kyang zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum bgrad cing mche ba bzhi gtsigs pa /
NK013(pa)014:1532: rnam par 'gyur ba'i khro gnyer chu rlabs ltar 'khrugs pa /
NK013(pa)014:1534: ral pa gyen du bardzesa shing /
NK013(pa)014:1535: zhing glang stag gi gos gsum /
NK013(pa)014:1537: khrag zhag sgyu 'phrul thal ba'i lugs /
NK013(pa)014:1538: thal ba'i byug pa gsum ste dur khrod kyi chas brgyad /
NK013(pa)014:1539: chu srin nyi zla mche ba gshog pa /
NK013(pa)014:1540: rdo rje'i khrab slag lcags med pa la chas brgyad de bcu drug gis brgyan pa /
NK013(pa)014:1541: yum gyi g.yon thams cad thod pa khrag gis bkang ba thogs shing /
NK013(pa)014:1542: gzhal yas gyi sgo khang thams cad khro bo'i sku
NK013(pa)014:1543: las 'phros pa'i me ri rdo rje rtse lnga'i gzugs
NK013(pa)014:1544: 'bar ba'i klong na rngams pa chen pos gar dgus
NK013(pa)014:1545: gtum zhing bdud bgegs kyi tshogs rnam par 'joms kyang
NK013(pa)014:1546: / thugs chos nyid las ma g.yos pas /
NK013(pa)014:1547: yab yum de rnams ni rdo rje mi 'gyur ba'i sku'o //
NK013(pa)014:1548: gzhal yas pho brang gi phyi rol la t+aa la'i
NK013(pa)014:1549: tshal du mkha' 'gro so gnyis lha chen po dpal
NK013(pa)014:1550: mgon bdun cu sogs dang rta babs kyi nam mkha'
NK013(pa)014:1551: rgyud sde drug gi rtsa gsum lha dang dbus mchod
NK013(pa)014:1552: rten gyi chos 'khor la rig 'dzin bla ma sprin
NK013(pa)014:1553: ltar 'khrigs pa'o // de ltar bdag gi dkyil 'khor 'di na bzhugs pa bzhin du /
NK013(pa)014:1554: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu chos kyi dbyings kyis
NK013(pa)014:1555: gar khyam pa thams cad rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor dang
NK013(pa)014:1556: / chos kyi dbyings sems nyid sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bas
NK013(pa)014:1557: khyab pa'i rten brten pa ma lus pa snang snong
NK013(pa)014:1558: zung du 'jug par gsal bar gyur /
NK013(pa)014:1559: slar yang gsal gdab cing dag pa dran pa'i phyir /
NK013(pa)014:1560: gang phyir rdo rje thugs chud pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:1561: las dang spyod pa dka' thub dang //
NK013(pa)014:1562: srid pa'i ri bos mi bskyed pa //
NK013(pa)014:1563: de ni mi bskyod mchog tu gsungs //
NK013(pa)014:1564: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba yi //
NK013(pa)014:1565: ji snyed sku gsung thugs snang ba //
NK013(pa)014:1566: mes dang thabs kyis khyad par gyis //
NK013(pa)014:1567: rnam par snang phyir snang mdzad mchog /
NK013(pa)014:1568: rgyal ba kun gyi yon tan ni //
NK013(pa)014:1569: tshogs rnams 'dus pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK013(pa)014:1570: yon tan rin chen ltar 'byung bas //
NK013(pa)014:1571: rin chen 'byung bar gsungs pa yin //
NK013(pa)014:1572: dpag tu med pa gsung gi sgo //
NK013(pa)014:1573: dbang po thabs kyi bye brag gis //
