NK013(pa)014:1574: don rtags gsung dang yi ge'i sgo //
NK013(pa)014:1575: mtha' yas snang phyir mtha' yas mchog /
NK013(pa)014:1576: dpag med thugs rje'i mdzad pa yi /
NK013(pa)014:1580: / 'gro ba skyobs pa'i don mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)014:1581: don grub ces ni rnam par bstan //
NK013(pa)014:1582: rig pa'i rgyal po 'di dag kyang //
NK013(pa)014:1583: tha mal lnga nyid gnas dag cing //
NK013(pa)014:1584: de las thabs des mngon byas pas //
NK013(pa)014:1585: der dbang bskur te nyid snang ba //
NK013(pa)014:1586: rgyal po nyid du brjod pa yin //
NK013(pa)014:1587: steng 'og gnyis la mngon grub pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:1589: gang de thabs las mngon gyur pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:1590: bde ba'i gzugs dang tshor ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:1593: rnam dag bdag med bde ba'i ros //
NK013(pa)014:1594: dbang bskur ye shes rgyal po bshang //
NK013(pa)014:1595: gang phyir snang dang sgom dang bris //
NK013(pa)014:1596: phyag rgya rtsa bcud thig le'i mdog /
NK013(pa)014:1597: dkar dang dmar dang ser ba dang //
NK013(pa)014:1598: sngo dang ljang dang rim ldan pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:1599: rgyal ba kun gyi bde bskyed cing //
NK013(pa)014:1600: spyod dang de las 'byung ba'i yum //
NK013(pa)014:1601: thams cad de las 'byung ba lnga //
NK013(pa)014:1602: tha mal zhen pa dag pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:1603: dbang bsgyur rgyal po lnga rang bzhin //
NK013(pa)014:1604: sra dang gsher dang drod dang bskyod //
NK013(pa)014:1605: nam mkha'i khams kyi gang che ba //
NK013(pa)014:1606: steng 'og thabs las mngon gyur pa //
NK013(pa)014:1607: yul dang shes pa dbyer med cing //
NK013(pa)014:1608: thugs rje shes rab 'brel pa yi /
NK013(pa)014:1611: gnyis med gzigs pa spyan gyi mchog /
NK013(pa)014:1612: zag med stong pa'i blo chen gyis //
NK013(pa)014:1613: skyes dang bsdu dang gnas pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)014:1614: mtha' dbus bral ba'i de bzhin nyid //
NK013(pa)014:1615: nam mkha'i dbyings shes gang brjod pa //
NK013(pa)014:1616: thun mong thun mong ma yin pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:1617: las dang lta ba nyon mongs pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:1618: shes bya'i dri ma mtha' yas pa //
NK013(pa)014:1619: rtog pas sbyor zhing bsreg pas na //
NK013(pa)014:1620: gos dkar ma ru brjod pa yin //
NK013(pa)014:1621: gang phyir las dang ting 'dzin dang //
NK013(pa)014:1622: ye shes thugs rje bar med chus //
NK013(pa)014:1623: gang dang 'khru dang tshim byed pas //
NK013(pa)014:1624: chu ni ma m+aa ki ru bshad //
NK013(pa)014:1625: gang phyir rtog dang thabs dag dang //
NK013(pa)014:1626: ting 'dzin thabs kyis rlung dag gis //
NK013(pa)014:1627: bgrod pa med pa'i zhing khams su //
NK013(pa)014:1628: sgrol ba sgrol ma nyid du bshad //
NK013(pa)014:1629: snying po ye shes rang byung nyid //
NK013(pa)014:1630: kun rten gnas dang khyab pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)014:1631: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin la //
NK013(pa)014:1632: sa yi snying por brjod pa yin //
NK013(pa)014:1633: rang byung snying po byang chub sems //
NK013(pa)014:1634: nam mkha' lta bur bsam brjod bral //
NK013(pa)014:1635: mtha' dbus sgro bkur gang 'das pa //
NK013(pa)014:1636: de ni nam mkha'i snying po nyid //
NK013(pa)014:1637: gang phyir thugs rje dpag med pas /
NK013(pa)014:1639: / 'gro ba chu bo brgal ba'i bar //
NK013(pa)014:1640: skye ba med cing gzigs pas na //
NK013(pa)014:1641: spyan ras gzigs dbang pad+ma'i gtso //
NK013(pa)014:1642: rtog dang dbyer med rdo rje yis //
NK013(pa)014:1643: mtha' yi bdag rtog mtshan ma dag /
NK013(pa)014:1644: 'joms pa phyag na rdo rje ste //
NK013(pa)014:1645: thun mong nyid dang khyad par gyi //
NK013(pa)014:1646: gsang ba'i rnam par shes pa bzhi //
NK013(pa)014:1647: thun mong yul dang khyad par gyis //
NK013(pa)014:1648: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba las //
NK013(pa)014:1649: mtshon dang rtog dang sgom pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:1650: lha mo bzhir ni mngon snang ba //
NK013(pa)014:1651: byang chub sems dang bde ba dang //
NK013(pa)014:1652: thabs kyi bde bas sgeg pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:1653: lha mo 'di ni sgeg mor bshad //
NK013(pa)014:1654: grol dang ma grol 'khor ba yi //
NK013(pa)014:1655: phyi nang sgra yi bye brag kun //
NK013(pa)014:1656: brag cha lta bur brjod mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)014:1657: bar chad med pas phreng ba dang //
NK013(pa)014:1658: tshims pa'i ngo bo gang bstan dang //
NK013(pa)014:1659: dri dang ldan pa'i khyad par gyis //
NK013(pa)014:1660: dbyangs nyid tshims shing yid bde bas //
NK013(pa)014:1661: de nyid rdo rje girti ma //
NK013(pa)014:1662: ro yis khyab cing gar bsgyur ldan //
NK013(pa)014:1663: bde ba chen po bzhi yi gar //
NK013(pa)014:1664: khyab dang mdzes dang tshims pa ltar //
NK013(pa)014:1665: mi gnas bkrol bar gar mkhan ma //
NK013(pa)014:1666: rgyan dang chags pa'i sgra dag dang //
NK013(pa)014:1667: yid kyi phreng ba bde ba'i gar //
NK013(pa)014:1668: lha mo bzhi yi rang bzhin no //
NK013(pa)014:1669: ma rtogs 'gro ba mtha' yas pa //
NK013(pa)014:1670: rang bzhin thugs rje mdzad pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:1671: yongs la phan thog skyob pa ni /
NK013(pa)014:1674: rtogs goms mthar phyin khyad par gyi //
NK013(pa)014:1675: las dang nyon mongs lta ba'i rim //
NK013(pa)014:1676: sel ba 'di ni sgrib sel lo //
NK013(pa)014:1677: thabs dang shes rab gnas rtog na //
NK013(pa)014:1678: gang phyir sgong len mi gnas pa //
NK013(pa)014:1679: phyi nang snod bcud ma lus pa //
NK013(pa)014:1680: dbye ba med pas kun tu bzang //
NK013(pa)014:1681: bdag dang gzhan du 'dzin pa kun //
NK013(pa)014:1682: zag pa med pa'i shes rab yin //
NK013(pa)014:1683: lta ba'i d+r+wa ba spyod pas na //
NK013(pa)014:1684: zag med shes rab 'jam dpal sku //
NK013(pa)014:1685: dbang po yi ge thig ler bcas //
NK013(pa)014:1686: gnas dang rtog dang sgom pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:1687: mngon du snang phyir brjod pa yin //
NK013(pa)014:1688: dus bzhi rim pa gnyis brgyad de //
NK013(pa)014:1689: de gnyis brod dang spro bskyed dang //
NK013(pa)014:1690: spyod yul phyir dag brjod pa ni //
NK013(pa)014:1691: dri dang phreng bas gang tshims shing //
NK013(pa)014:1692: yid rtog med pas rdo rje dri //
NK013(pa)014:1693: phyi nang khyab pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK013(pa)014:1694: me tog thig le bder bkod pas //
NK013(pa)014:1695: rdo rje me tog bla na med //
NK013(pa)014:1696: phyi nang sems la gnas bcas pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:1697: mun pa bsal phyir shes rab dang //
NK013(pa)014:1698: ye shes snang ba bla na med //
NK013(pa)014:1699: rdo rje gsal ba'i mar me ma //
NK013(pa)014:1700: phyi nang dkyil 'khor ma lus la //
NK013(pa)014:1701: rang byung ting 'dzin bde ba yis //
NK013(pa)014:1702: thams cad khyab par gnas pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)014:1703: khyab byed rdo rje dri chab ma //
NK013(pa)014:1704: de bzhin nyid la dgongs pa yin /
NK013(pa)014:1706: / 'khor ba'i chos rnams ma lus pa //
NK013(pa)014:1707: byang chub snying po tshar bcad pas //
NK013(pa)014:1708: rnam par rgyal ba zhes su brjod //
NK013(pa)014:1709: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes ni //
NK013(pa)014:1710: gnyis med rtog pa'i gnyen po ste //
NK013(pa)014:1711: rtog goms de ni 'jogs pas na //
NK013(pa)014:1712: ya man+ta kritra gshin rje ste //
NK013(pa)014:1713: gang phyir 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las //
NK013(pa)014:1714: thabs dang bcas pa'i rdzu 'phrul las /
NK013(pa)014:1716: / 'joms dang sgrol bar mdzad pas na //
NK013(pa)014:1717: rta mgrin rgyal por de bshad de /
NK013(pa)014:1719: / 'khor ba'i bdud kyi dug lnga las //
NK013(pa)014:1720: ye shes lnga ru gsal goms pas //
NK013(pa)014:1721: gnyis med rtsi ru gang 'khyil ba //
NK013(pa)014:1722: sgrib zad bdud rtsi 'khyil par bshad //
NK013(pa)014:1723: gang du lus dang bcas pa yin //
NK013(pa)014:1724: dbang po yul dang rnam shes reg /
NK013(pa)014:1725: rang rgyud bcas pa'i ye shes nyid //
NK013(pa)014:1726: sgo ba rnam pa bzhi ru gsungs //
NK013(pa)014:1727: rang rgyud rtag chad bzlog pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:1728: gzung dang lha dang bde ba dang //
NK013(pa)014:1729: thig le rig par bcas pa nyid //
NK013(pa)014:1730: gang phyir gnas dag dgug pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:1731: gang du 'gro bar mi nus dang //
NK013(pa)014:1732: de las 'da' bar dka' ba dang //
NK013(pa)014:1733: bstim nas bde ba dril bu mas //
NK013(pa)014:1734: gzung dang 'khyud dang sdom pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:1735: gnyis su med pas bde chen pa //
NK013(pa)014:1736: rang lus snang srid brtan g.yo la //
NK013(pa)014:1737: rtog dang goms pa'i tshul gyis sbyar //
NK013(pa)014:1738: de dag ma lus 'dren byed pa //
NK013(pa)014:1739: rig pa'i rgyal po kun dbyer med //
NK013(pa)014:1740: kun gzhi rdo rje mi phyed pas //
NK013(pa)014:1741: kun tu bzang por de bshad do //
NK013(pa)014:1743: ma lus zag med khyab pa'i dbyings //
NK013(pa)014:1744: rtog dang shes dang gang gyur pa //
NK013(pa)014:1745: kun tu bzang mor de bshad do //
NK013(pa)014:1746: dmyal ba yi dwags byol song dang /
NK013(pa)014:1747: mi dang lha dang lha min te //
NK013(pa)014:1748: so so'i gnas de gang yin pa /
NK013(pa)014:1751: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can //
NK013(pa)014:1757: mtha' dbus med par khyab pa yis //
NK013(pa)014:1758: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK013(pa)014:1759: ma skyes rig pa byang chub sems //
NK013(pa)014:1760: dngos med dngos po'i rang bzhin du //
NK013(pa)014:1761: rdo rje sems dpa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK013(pa)014:1762: g.yo dang ma g.yor bcas pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:1763: phyi nang snod bcud ma lus pa //
NK013(pa)014:1764: rang byung sems kyi dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK013(pa)014:1765: rang bzhin gnas dang rtogs pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:1766: bsam dang dmigs dang goms pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:1767: sku gsung thugs dang mtshan ma dang //
NK013(pa)014:1768: lha dang lha min gsang ba dang //
NK013(pa)014:1770: grul bum yi dwags klu rnams dang //
NK013(pa)014:1771: rgyu ba srog chags ma lus dang //
NK013(pa)014:1772: rtsi shing gel ba 'bras bu dang //
NK013(pa)014:1773: phun sum tshogs pa ma lus dang //
NK013(pa)014:1774: ma bcos don gyi lha nyid de //
NK013(pa)014:1775: byang chub sems su khyad par med //
NK013(pa)014:1776: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK013(pa)014:1782: rig pa'i don nyid dkyil nyid de //
NK013(pa)014:1784: gnyis pa dbang bskur ba'i phyir thugs srog bkod pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:1787: de ltar gsal ba'i lha tshogs thams cad kyi thugs
NK013(pa)014:1788: ka'i dbus rang 'dra'i ye shes sems dpa' rgyan spangs
NK013(pa)014:1789: pa re'i thugs kar rang rang gi phyag mtshan lte
NK013(pa)014:1790: bar yab thams cad la nyi ma dang /
NK013(pa)014:1791: yum thams cad la zla ba'i steng rigs lnga sems dpa' yab yum kun bzang bcas la /
NK013(pa)014:1805: thub drug krem trum srum prem k+sham ye dang /
NK013(pa)014:1806: sgo ba yab bzhir h'u h'u h'u h'u /
NK013(pa)014:1807: yum la dzahmh'u bam hamhrnamasa kyi mthar rang rang gi bzlas bya'i sngags kyis mtshan pa gsal bar gyur /
NK013(pa)014:1809: thugs ka nas 'phros pa'i 'od kyis dbang gi lha
NK013(pa)014:1810: rigs lnga 'khor bcas badz+ra sa m+aa dzah de dag
NK013(pa)014:1811: kun kyang thabs dang shes rab dbyer med pas byang
NK013(pa)014:1812: chub sems kyi 'od zer gyis bdag la dbang bskur
NK013(pa)014:1814: phung po lnga rigs lnga dang /
NK013(pa)014:1815: nyon mongs pa lnga ye shes lngar gnas 'gyur /
NK013(pa)014:1816: gtso bo bya byed yab yum /
NK013(pa)014:1817: thub drug bcas la mi bskyod pa rnam snang /
NK013(pa)014:1819: gshin rje gshed yab yum rnams la rnam snang /
NK013(pa)014:1823: stobs po che yab yum rnams la rin 'byung /
NK013(pa)014:1827: rta mgrin yab yum rnams la snang mtha' /
NK013(pa)014:1831: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba yab yum rnams la don grub
NK013(pa)014:1832: rnams zhal gcig phyag gnyis rang rtags dang de'i yu
NK013(pa)014:1833: ba byas pa'i dril bu thugs kar bsnol ba longs
NK013(pa)014:1834: sku'i cha byad can res bdag por byas pa'i rigs
NK013(pa)014:1835: lnga lngas dbu brgyan par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:1836: phyag rgya mdzub srin theb che chung bcas so sor brkyang pa spyi bo /
NK013(pa)014:1839: rgyab g.yon rnams su bzhag ste /
NK013(pa)014:1840: ma h+aa sh+ru nya da dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:1841: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:1842: ma h+aa sa ma t+wa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:1843: ma h+aa pra t+ya be k+sha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:1844: ma h+aa kri t+y+aa nush+tha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:1845: de ni mi bskyod pa gtso bo'o //
NK013(pa)014:1849: pra d+ya kri t+y+aa rnams rnam snang gtso bo /
NK013(pa)014:1851: +aa dar+sha sh+r+au nya ta pra t+ya kri t+y+aa rnams rin 'byung gtso bo /
NK013(pa)014:1852: ma h+aa pra t+y+aa +aa dar+sha sa ma t+aa sh+r+au
NK013(pa)014:1853: nya t+ya kri t+y+aa rnams snang mtha' bdag po dang
NK013(pa)014:1854: / ma h+aa kri t+y+aa +aa dar+sha sa ma t+aa
NK013(pa)014:1855: pra t+ya sh+r+au nya ta rnams don grub gtso bor
NK013(pa)014:1856: byas pa ste lnga tshan lnga'o //
NK013(pa)014:1857: rtags de dag gis don rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad chos nyid las ma g.yos pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:1858: 'gag pa med par rang snang ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:1859: ye nas dbyer med pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:1860: gdul bya'i mos pa dang mthun par 'jug pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:1861: don gnyis phun sum tshogs pa rnams mtshan pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:1862: gsum pa yin gyi brlab pa'i cho 'phrul ba'i rdo rje lngar byed pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:1863: dam ye dbyer med du byed pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:1865: rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i rgya gnas lngar gtugs te /
NK013(pa)014:1866: sarba ta th+aa ga t+aa ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:1867: sarba ta th+aa ga t+aa ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:1868: sarba ta th+aa ga t+aa ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:1869: sarba ta th+aa ga t+aa ma h+aa a nu ra ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:1870: sarba ta tha ga t+aa ma h+aa pu tsa badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:1871: lha tshogs thams cad kyi dung khang gi nang du zla ba la gnas pa'i +amo dkar po /
NK013(pa)014:1872: mgrin par ljags pad+ma la gnas pa'i +aahdamara po /
NK013(pa)014:1873: thugs kar g.yas nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i h'u mthing sngon /
NK013(pa)014:1874: lte bar rin po che zur brgyad la gnas pa s+w+aa ser po /
NK013(pa)014:1875: gsang bar chos 'byung gru gsum la gnas pa'i h+aa
NK013(pa)014:1876: ljang gu rnams las 'phros pa'i 'od zer gyis phyogs
NK013(pa)014:1877: bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung
NK013(pa)014:1878: thugs yon tan phrin las kyi rgyud bskul /
NK013(pa)014:1879: rdo rje lnga'i lha tshogs mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK013(pa)014:1881: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi go 'phang gi chos lnga dang tha mi dad par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:1882: yi ge rnams 'od du zhu ba las /
NK013(pa)014:1883: sku rdo rje dkar po'i 'khor lo dang dril bu can /
NK013(pa)014:1884: thugs kar 'khor lo +amo gyis mtshan pa /
NK013(pa)014:1885: gsung rdo rje dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu can //
NK013(pa)014:1886: thugs kar pad+ma as mtshan pa /
NK013(pa)014:1887: thugs rdo rje mthing nag rdo rje dang dril bu can /
NK013(pa)014:1888: thugs kar rdo rje h'u gis mtshan pa /
NK013(pa)014:1889: chags pa'i rdo rje ser po rin po che dang dril bu can /
NK013(pa)014:1890: thugs kar rin po che s+b+aas mtshan pa /
NK013(pa)014:1891: mchod pa'i rdo rje ljang ku /
NK013(pa)014:1892: ral gri dang dril bu can /
NK013(pa)014:1893: thugs kar ral gri has mtshan pa rnams kyi gnas lngar rgyas btab par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:1894: slar yang nga rgyal bzung ba'i phyir /
NK013(pa)014:1895: de ltar rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor bas //
NK013(pa)014:1896: dus bzhi phyogs bcu gang nas kyang //
NK013(pa)014:1897: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK013(pa)014:1898: sems nyid rtogs pas sangs rgyas te //
NK013(pa)014:1899: sangs rgyas gzhan du ma tshol cig /
NK013(pa)014:1900: dkyil 'khor kun du rab sbyar bas //
NK013(pa)014:1902: gnyis pa la snyan gsan dbab pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:1904: rig pa'i me tog gi 'jug pa /
NK013(pa)014:1905: dngos grub bskul te bstim pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:1907: thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bde bar gshegs pa thams cad /
NK013(pa)014:1908: dgongs pa chos sku las me long la gzugs brnyan shar ba ltar /
NK013(pa)014:1909: gzugs sku bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor
NK013(pa)014:1910: lo mdun gyi nam mkhar mngon sum bzhugs par gyur
NK013(pa)014:1912: dmigs med mkha' ltar khyab cing dag pa'i sku //
NK013(pa)014:1913: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK013(pa)014:1914: thugs rjes ngang nyid chos skur dag pa las //
NK013(pa)014:1915: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:1916: rdo rje gnod sbyin phyag rgya bcas /
NK013(pa)014:1917: badz+ra sa ma dza h'u dza /
NK013(pa)014:1918: gnyis pa'i lcags kyu'i rgya bcas /
NK013(pa)014:1919: hoh yod med stong pa shin tu rnal 'byor mthus //
NK013(pa)014:1920: nam mkha' bzhin las dam tshig nye bar gshegs //
NK013(pa)014:1921: ye shes rgya mtsho rnam par rol pa'i klong //
NK013(pa)014:1922: mi gnas mi dmigs nam mkha'i dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK013(pa)014:1923: tshogs chen gnyis rdzogs thugs dam dbyings kyi lha //
NK013(pa)014:1924: longs spyad rdzogs mdzad rol pa chen po'i sku //
NK013(pa)014:1925: rdo rje sems dpa' skal bzang dpal khyod bdag /
NK013(pa)014:1926: thabs kyis ma rmongs bde chen dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK013(pa)014:1927: ye shes sgyu ma rnam par rol pa'i sku /
NK013(pa)014:1929: / 'phags rje sprul pa mang po 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK013(pa)014:1930: thabs dang shes rab mchog la mnga' brnyes pas //
NK013(pa)014:1931: bder gshegs bde bar gshegs pa bzhengs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:1932: e h+ya h+ai b+ha ga w+aan /
NK013(pa)014:1933: ma h+aa ka ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK013(pa)014:1934: dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes spos dang rol mo phul /
NK013(pa)014:1935: thugs rjes lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK013(pa)014:1936: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan yang 'dren //
NK013(pa)014:1937: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nya gnas bskyod la //
NK013(pa)014:1938: bde gshegs bzhugs shing rnal grol dgyes pa bskyed //
NK013(pa)014:1939: ces bskul bas ngo bo la byon bzhud med kyang
NK013(pa)014:1940: gdul bya'i don du gshegs pa'i ye shes pa dam
NK013(pa)014:1941: tshig gi dkyil 'khor dang me ri 'dab 'brel du
NK013(pa)014:1942: bzhugs pa la / gsum pa la /
NK013(pa)014:1945: h'u badz+ra sa ma ya h'u /
NK013(pa)014:1946: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK013(pa)014:1947: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:1948: zhes gsol btab pas rang bzhin dang ting nge 'dzin
NK013(pa)014:1949: gyi dkyil 'khor sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK013(pa)014:1951: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK013(pa)014:1952: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK013(pa)014:1953: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK013(pa)014:1954: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK013(pa)014:1957: badz+ra sa ma ya hoh zhes dbyer med du byas pa de yang brtan par byas /
NK013(pa)014:1958: rin chen seng ge'i khri la yang dag nges bzhugs shing /
NK013(pa)014:1959: rang gi lha mo dag dang sras dang g.yog 'khor bcas pa rnams /
NK013(pa)014:1960: kun tu bzang po'i smon lam rjes su dgongs mdzad de /
NK013(pa)014:1961: 'jig rten lha dang bcas pa rnams la phan phyir bzhugs su gsol /
NK013(pa)014:1962: stobs kyi glang po'i khri la yang /
NK013(pa)014:1963: rang gi lha mo kun tu bzang /
NK013(pa)014:1964: 'jig rten rdzu 'phrul rta yi khri la rang gi
NK013(pa)014:1965: lha mo kun tu bzang po'i 'jig rten dbang bcu
NK013(pa)014:1966: rma bya'i khri rang gi lha mo kun tu bzang
NK013(pa)014:1967: po'i 'jig rten thog med mkha' lding khri la rang
NK013(pa)014:1968: gi kun tu bzang 'jig rten k+aa ya w+aaka tsit+ta
NK013(pa)014:1969: tish+tha badz+ra / bzhi pa mchod pa'i cho 'phrul gyi sdoms ni /
NK013(pa)014:1970: phyag dang kun bzang phyi la gsum /
NK013(pa)014:1973: sbyor sgrol sman gtor de kho na //
NK013(pa)014:1974: yon tan bstod pa bshags dam blang //
NK013(pa)014:1975: zhes pa ltar bcu gsum las /
NK013(pa)014:1977: rang gi thugs ka nas phyung ba'i spyan ma la
NK013(pa)014:1978: sogs pa'i lha mo sgo bzhir 'khod nas phyag dang
NK013(pa)014:1979: mchod pa'i las rim la 'jug par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:1980: 'og min zhing gshegs yang dag chos sku'i don //
NK013(pa)014:1981: ji bzhin gzigs kyang gdul bya mi 'dor ba'i //
NK013(pa)014:1982: thugs rje thabs kyi bye brag rnam par spro //
NK013(pa)014:1983: rab 'byams bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:1984: mi rtog rdo rje thabs kyi ye shes ni //
NK013(pa)014:1985: dmigs med shes rab yum gyi ngang du rtogs //
NK013(pa)014:1986: thugs rjes bye brag sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK013(pa)014:1987: rdo rje sems dpa' che la chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK013(pa)014:1988: gzugs sku 'ja' tshon bzhin du sor sor gsal //
NK013(pa)014:1989: thabs dang shes rab mchog la mnga' brnyes pa //
NK013(pa)014:1990: rigs lnga bde bar gshegs la mdzes pa'i sku mchog sems can sgrol la mkhas //
NK013(pa)014:1991: ngo mtshar pho brang bde bar gshegs pa'i yum //
NK013(pa)014:1992: shes rab thabs kyis gtso la mnyes mdzad ma //
NK013(pa)014:1993: rigs kyi yum rnams la yang thabs mkhas thugs rjes ye shes sprul pa'i sku //
NK013(pa)014:1994: rigs lnga rnal 'byor grub pa'i sa brnyes pa /
NK013(pa)014:1995: thugs rje chen pos 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)014:1996: sems dpa' sems ma rnams la byams dang snying rje dga' ba btang snyoms kyis //
NK013(pa)014:1997: nyon mongs log par lta ba'i dgra rnams 'joms //
NK013(pa)014:1998: gshin rje gshed po la sogs khro bo bzhi //
NK013(pa)014:1999: sgo ba yab yum rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:2000: chos rnams rnam dag ye nas lhun grub cing //
NK013(pa)014:2001: bya ba byed dang yid chos rnam par dag /
NK013(pa)014:2002: kun bzang yab yum gnyis steng 'og phyogs bzhi 'jig rten 'dul ba'i gtso //
NK013(pa)014:2003: nyon mongs drug 'joms rgyud drug dag par sbyang //
NK013(pa)014:2004: bcom ldan thub pa drug la dmigs med chos kyi
NK013(pa)014:2005: sku la longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku cir yang sprul
NK013(pa)014:2006: pa'i sku mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku mngon par byang
NK013(pa)014:2007: chub sku khams gsum zhing du sbyor a ti pu
NK013(pa)014:2008: hoh pra ti pu hoh gnyis pa /
NK013(pa)014:2009: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK013(pa)014:2010: rgyal ba rgyal mtsho ye shes kyi //
NK013(pa)014:2011: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kyi //
NK013(pa)014:2012: spyod pa rgya mtsho rmad byung kun //
NK013(pa)014:2013: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK013(pa)014:2014: na ma s+sarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa
NK013(pa)014:2015: mu khe b+h+yeh sarba t+pa t+pam ung+ga te s+pha ra
NK013(pa)014:2016: na hi mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:2017: 'byung ba kun las nam mkha' ni /
NK013(pa)014:2019: / 'byung ba chen po lnga pa ste //
NK013(pa)014:2022: / 'dod pa'i mchod pa grub gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:2023: pa na pe pe nu su ra to //
NK013(pa)014:2025: sarba t+aa tha ga ta sid+d+hi hu /
NK013(pa)014:2027: sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi hu /
NK013(pa)014:2028: sarba t+aa th+aa ga ta ga ga na pu dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:2029: gsum pa la dngos 'byor 'dod yon dang /
NK013(pa)014:2031: de bzhin nyid kyi 'dod yon no //
NK013(pa)014:2035: thos bsam mchod yon zhabs bsil sgom rlabs g.yo //
NK013(pa)014:2036: ting 'dzin bdug pa rnam grol me tog 'phro //
NK013(pa)014:2037: shes rab mar me dri chu tshul khrims mtsho //
NK013(pa)014:2038: bdud rtsi mya ngan 'das mchod rol mo'i bcud //
NK013(pa)014:2039: bla ma mchog dang mi bskyod rdo rje gtso //
NK013(pa)014:2040: dpal ldan sgyu 'phrul bde ba'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK013(pa)014:2041: gus pas 'bul na bdag gzhan sems can kun //
NK013(pa)014:2042: rnam par thar pa brgyad la mnga' brnyes shog /
NK013(pa)014:2043: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta de was+ya man+dala sa p+aa ri wa ra badz+ra ar+g+ham nas /
NK013(pa)014:2046: gnyis pa la rnam bdun dang /
NK013(pa)014:2049: yang dag don du dag mod kyang /
NK013(pa)014:2051: / 'gro ba yongs kyi don slad du //
NK013(pa)014:2052: phyag dang zhabs ni bsil slad du //
NK013(pa)014:2053: rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:2054: a ha ra a ha ra sarba bir+ya d+h+aa ra
NK013(pa)014:2055: p+au dza me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na
NK013(pa)014:2058: spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa mo //
NK013(pa)014:2060: byams pa thabs dang shes rab las //
NK013(pa)014:2062: sh+r+ai badz+ra ra ga d+h+au sh+pe h'u /
NK013(pa)014:2065: snying rje thabs dang shes rab las //
NK013(pa)014:2067: sh+r+ai badz+ra ra ga push+pe pu /
NK013(pa)014:2068: dbang gi phyag ni sgron ma bsnams //
NK013(pa)014:2070: dga' ba thabs dang shes rab las //
NK013(pa)014:2071: badz+ra lo ka'i mchod pa rol //
NK013(pa)014:2072: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa g+aa lo ke d+h+r+aih tsan+dana bdud rtsi'i char 'bebs ma //
NK013(pa)014:2074: btang snyoms thabs dang shes rab la //
NK013(pa)014:2076: sh+r+ai badz+ra ra ga gan+d+he gan //
NK013(pa)014:2077: mya ngan 'das mchog rang bzhin bas //
NK013(pa)014:2078: bcud len bro mchog zhal zas 'di //
NK013(pa)014:2079: bdag gi dad pas 'bul lags kyi //
NK013(pa)014:2080: bzhes te grub mchog stsal du gsol //
NK013(pa)014:2082: de nas gzhan yang mchod pa'i tshogs //
NK013(pa)014:2083: rol mo dbyangs snyan yid 'ong ldan //
NK013(pa)014:2084: sems can sdug bsngal sel byed pa //
NK013(pa)014:2085: sprin rnams so sor gnas gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:2086: na mo rat+na t+r+aa ya ya /
NK013(pa)014:2087: na mo b+ha ga wa te badz+ra sa ra sogs dang /
NK013(pa)014:2088: badz+ra gan+de d+harma ra ni ta /
NK013(pa)014:2091: dung mdog sgegs mo rdo rje'i spyan //
NK013(pa)014:2092: sems dpa' sngon mo'i ye shes 'bebs //
NK013(pa)014:2093: me long lta bu'i ye shes la //
NK013(pa)014:2096: yid bzhin rin chen gtsug khro ma /
NK013(pa)014:2099: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes las //
NK013(pa)014:2100: badz+ra m+aa l+ye mchod par rol //
NK013(pa)014:2102: pad+ma dbyangs mkhan rma bya'i mgrin //
NK013(pa)014:2103: spyan ras gzigs dbang dngos grub 'dzin //
NK013(pa)014:2104: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes las //
NK013(pa)014:2106: badz+ra girti h+r+aih gar mkhan 'gying bag gzi ldan ma //
NK013(pa)014:2108: bya ba nan tan ye shes las //
NK013(pa)014:2112: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:2113: dam tshig chen po dam pa grub par mdzod //
NK013(pa)014:2115: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:2116: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig grub par mdzod //
NK013(pa)014:2118: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:2119: mchod pa chen po dga' ba dag par mdzod //
NK013(pa)014:2121: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:2122: mchod pa chen po btang snyoms grub par mdzod //
NK013(pa)014:2123: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK013(pa)014:2124: sems kyi yid bzhin sprin tshogs kyis //
NK013(pa)014:2125: phyogs bcu thams cad sangs rgyas shing //
NK013(pa)014:2126: mnyen 'jam reg na bde ba yis //
NK013(pa)014:2127: sna tshogs rin po che yi gzhi //
NK013(pa)014:2128: mdzes par bres shing spras pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:2131: dbyibs legs rdzing bu bro mchog bsil //
NK013(pa)014:2133: rin chen khang pa sna tshogs dang //
NK013(pa)014:2134: rgyan dang dpag bsam ljon pa'i tshal //
NK013(pa)014:2135: h+r+aih glu dbyangs tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra //
NK013(pa)014:2137: bla bre rgyal mtshan na bza' bdugs //
NK013(pa)014:2138: do shal dpung rgyan se mo do /
NK013(pa)014:2140: / +aah bza' dang btung ba'i mchog rnams kyi //
NK013(pa)014:2141: rang la mdzes par rgyan pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:2142: lha dang lha mo'i rdul snyed kyis //
NK013(pa)014:2143: bro gar glu tshig bsam yas kyis //
NK013(pa)014:2144: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bskangs nas //
NK013(pa)014:2147: sprul pa'i 'khor lor rnam rtog spos ring ni //
NK013(pa)014:2148: gtum mos bsregs pa'i dga' ba rdo rje ma //
NK013(pa)014:2149: in+d+ra n+ai la ltar sngo bde ba'i drod //
NK013(pa)014:2150: rab 'bar sprin du 'thul bas bla ma mchod //
NK013(pa)014:2152: tshangs pa'i 'khor lor kun+da'i pad dkar ni //
NK013(pa)014:2153: rnam par 'thor ba mchog dga' rdo rje ma //
NK013(pa)014:2154: gser sbyang ltar mdzes ham ze'u 'bru //
NK013(pa)014:2155: yas 'bab sgyu ma'i sgegs pas bla ma mchod //
NK013(pa)014:2157: chos kyi 'khor lor gzung 'dzin mun pa'i gshed //
NK013(pa)014:2158: zag med snang gsal dga' bral rdo rje ma //
NK013(pa)014:2159: bye ru'i mdangs 'dzin mi shig thig le'i 'od //
NK013(pa)014:2160: lnga 'dris sku gsum rang gsal bla mar mchod //
NK013(pa)014:2161: badz+ra a lo ke gri h+na h'u //
NK013(pa)014:2162: bde skyong 'khor lor bde chen dri bzang po //
NK013(pa)014:2163: brjod bral las shar lhan skyes rdo rje ma //
NK013(pa)014:2164: ma rgad ltar ljang mas brtan byugs pa'i chab //
NK013(pa)014:2165: bde stong lang tsho'i 'gyur bas bla ma mchod //
NK013(pa)014:2167: longs spyod 'khor lor rlung sngags n+aa da'i sgra //
NK013(pa)014:2168: stong nyid ngang na sgrogs pa'i rol mo'i sprin //
NK013(pa)014:2169: rdo rje'i lus kyi zhing khams rgya mtsho na //
NK013(pa)014:2170: sangs rgyas rgyal mtsho rtag tu mnyes phyir 'bul //
NK013(pa)014:2171: d+hu ti'i dbus su gnyis 'dzin rtog pa'i ro //
NK013(pa)014:2172: gnyis med myang ba bsam mi khyab bde yis //
NK013(pa)014:2173: kun bzang ngang tshims zhal zas bkod pa bcas //
NK013(pa)014:2174: bla ma mi bskyod rdo rje mnyes phyir 'bul //
NK013(pa)014:2175: bzhi pa phyag rgya la rtogs pa lta ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:2179: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:2180: dbang po'i yul du gang gyur pa //
NK013(pa)014:2181: thabs dang shes rab ldan 'gyur zhing //
NK013(pa)014:2182: mnyam pa'i ngang nyid rtogs gsal na //
NK013(pa)014:2183: thams cad byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK013(pa)014:2185: bskyod chen 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK013(pa)014:2186: thabs dang shes rab thams cad kun //
NK013(pa)014:2188: bsgul bskyod thams cad phyag rgya yin /
NK013(pa)014:2190: / 'di ni spyi rgya chen po ste //
NK013(pa)014:2191: bla med chen pos 'di skad gsungs //
NK013(pa)014:2192: gsang ba de nyid nges pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:2194: mi bskyod nyi ma'i dkyil yi ge //
NK013(pa)014:2195: rin chen zla ba'i dkyil yi ge //
NK013(pa)014:2196: lnga gnyis zung du 'phros pa las //
NK013(pa)014:2197: sbyar bas phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK013(pa)014:2198: dang mum gnyis rtse sbyar te /
NK013(pa)014:2200: / 'bru brgyad bsnol nas rtse sprad pa //
NK013(pa)014:2201: bde ba chen po sbyin pa'i rgya //
NK013(pa)014:2203: phyag rgya bzhi'i don shes pas /
NK013(pa)014:2204: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)014:2205: h'u sgreng rtse mor rdo rje 'bar //
NK013(pa)014:2206: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing /
NK013(pa)014:2208: / 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la brten //
NK013(pa)014:2210: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK013(pa)014:2211: m+aum sgreng rtse mor dril bsil 'bar //
NK013(pa)014:2213: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta //
NK013(pa)014:2216: zla brtul 'khril ba'i +amo dzi na dzika /
NK013(pa)014:2217: 'bru bzhi l+aam sgreng rtse mor dril bsil 'bar //
NK013(pa)014:2218: nyi ma btud de 'dzum l+aam dwee sha ra ti /
NK013(pa)014:2219: 'bru bzhi s+w+aa sgreng rtse mor rin chen 'bar /
NK013(pa)014:2220: zla brtul 'khril ba'i s+w+aa rat+na d+h+r+aika /
NK013(pa)014:2221: 'bru bzhi m+aam sgreng rtse nyi ma 'bru lnga btud de m+aam mo ha ra ti /
NK013(pa)014:2223: zla brtul 'khril ba'i +amo a ro lika /
NK013(pa)014:2224: 'bru bzhi pyam sgreng nyi ma btud de pyam r+aa ga ra ti /
NK013(pa)014:2225: 'bru bzhi ha sgreng rtse mor ral gri 'bar //
NK013(pa)014:2226: zla brtul 'khril ba'i h+aa pradz+ny+aa d+h+rika /
NK013(pa)014:2227: 'bru bzhi t+aam sgreng rtse nyi ma btud de t+aam badz+ra ra ti //
NK013(pa)014:2228: rdo rje rin chen thugs kar 'dzin //
NK013(pa)014:2229: rin chen dril bsil chos la brten /
NK013(pa)014:2231: / 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta ba ni //
NK013(pa)014:2232: sa yi snying po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK013(pa)014:2234: rdo rje rin chen khu tshur bcas //
NK013(pa)014:2235: sku yi thad kar bzung ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:2236: 'dzum pa'i sge mo'i phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK013(pa)014:2237: h'u l+aa s+ye sa ma ya stam //
NK013(pa)014:2238: rdo rje ral gri'i thugs ka nas //
NK013(pa)014:2239: rin chen dril 'dzum pa'i nam mkha'i snying po'i t+r+aam a gar+b+ta ya /
NK013(pa)014:2240: rdo rje rin chen rna ltag bzhag /
NK013(pa)014:2241: rin chen phreng ba bzung ba ru /
NK013(pa)014:2243: / 'dzum pa'i mdangs phreng ba'i phyag tram ma l+ye sa ma ya ho //
NK013(pa)014:2244: rdo rje pad+ma'i thugs ka nas //
NK013(pa)014:2245: rin chen dril 'dzum pa'i spyan ras gzigs kyi phyag rgya yin //
NK013(pa)014:2246: h+r+aim ha h'u pad+ma ba da ma /
NK013(pa)014:2247: rin chen pi wam 'dzin par bya //
NK013(pa)014:2248: rdo rje len par byas nas ni /
NK013(pa)014:2250: / 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta' ba ni //
NK013(pa)014:2251: dbyangs kyi phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK013(pa)014:2252: hri girti r+aa ga ya ho //
NK013(pa)014:2253: rdo rje rdo rje'i rin chen dril bsil 'dzum pa'i
NK013(pa)014:2254: mdangs phyag na rdo rje'i dz+rim ku ru pa na
NK013(pa)014:2255: h+r+aih rin chen gar thabs bskor nas ni //
NK013(pa)014:2256: rdo rje thal mo las la 'khril /
NK013(pa)014:2258: / 'dzum pa'i gar gyi phyag rgyar dpa' bos bshad //
NK013(pa)014:2259: a nirti ra ga ya mi //
NK013(pa)014:2260: rdo rje klu shing thugs ka nas //
NK013(pa)014:2261: rin chen dril bsil 'dzum pa'i byams pa mee tri'i mee d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:2262: rin chen bdug spos thugs kar 'dzin //
NK013(pa)014:2263: rdo rje las la rab tu 'khril /
NK013(pa)014:2265: / 'dzum pa'i bdug pa'i phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK013(pa)014:2266: dzahd+h+au sh+pe pra we sha ya /
NK013(pa)014:2267: rdo rje po ti'i thugs ka nas //
NK013(pa)014:2268: rin chen dril bsil chos la brten /
NK013(pa)014:2270: / 'dzum pa'i sgrib pa rnams sel phyag rgya yin /
NK013(pa)014:2271: th+l+him ni s+sa ri pa ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:2272: rdo rje rin chen rna ltag tu //
NK013(pa)014:2273: me tog snod bcas 'dzin pa la /
NK013(pa)014:2275: / 'dzum pa'i me tog phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK013(pa)014:2276: h'u push+pe a we sha ya /
NK013(pa)014:2277: rdo rje snyems ma'i thugs ka nas //
NK013(pa)014:2278: rin chen dril 'dzum pa'i kun tu bzang po'i h'u swa r+w+aa dz+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:2279: rin chen mar me'i thugs ka nas //
NK013(pa)014:2280: rdo rje sems dpa' che la 'khril /
NK013(pa)014:2282: / 'dzum pa'i mar me'i phyag rgyar dpa' bos bshad //
NK013(pa)014:2283: bam d+ai ba su khi ni /
NK013(pa)014:2284: rdo rje ut+pala thugs ka nas //
NK013(pa)014:2285: rin chen dril 'dzum pa'i mdangs 'jam dpal gyis ni phyag rgya yin //
NK013(pa)014:2286: m+aum sh+r+ai am r+aa ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:2287: rin chen dbyug pa'i thugs ka nas //
NK013(pa)014:2288: rdo rjes nyug par byed pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:2290: / 'dzum pa'i dri yi phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK013(pa)014:2292: r+n+ri mgo gdengs pa gshed po ste //
NK013(pa)014:2293: h'u ya man+ta kri tra phata /
NK013(pa)014:2294: mdzub gnyis bkug pa lcags kyu'i rgya //
NK013(pa)014:2295: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he sho r+ai dz+wa li n+ai h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:2296: rdo rje rnon po stobs chen rgya //
NK013(pa)014:2297: h'u pra dz+ny+aan+ta kri tra h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:2298: mdzub gnyis rtse sprad zhags pa'i rgya //
NK013(pa)014:2299: a h+aa rat+na d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:2300: thod sbrul gnon pa rta mgrin rgya //
NK013(pa)014:2302: mdzub gnyis 'khyud pa lu gu rgyud //
NK013(pa)014:2303: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+aa dz+wa li ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:2304: rgya gram gnon pa 'khyil pa'i rgya //
NK013(pa)014:2307: ma h+aa karma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa ri dz+wa li ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:2308: pi wam len pa lha yi rgya /
NK013(pa)014:2310: mi ni gseg par 'dzin pa ste /
NK013(pa)014:2311: mu na h+aum trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:2312: lha mi phyag rgya go cha yin //
NK013(pa)014:2314: chos kyi 'khor lo byol song rgya //
NK013(pa)014:2316: za ma tog ni yi dwags rgya //
NK013(pa)014:2318: me chu gnyis ni dmyal ba'i rgya /
NK013(pa)014:2320: yab kyi spyi rgya kun bzang gis //
NK013(pa)014:2321: h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK013(pa)014:2322: yum gyi spyi rgya bzang mor bshad /
NK013(pa)014:2323: a a a badz+ri b+ha dra sa man+ta ah yang na kun bzang yab yum ni //
NK013(pa)014:2324: rdo rje thal mo nyid du bshad //
NK013(pa)014:2325: phyag rgya'i mchod pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK013(pa)014:2326: dkyil 'khor thugs dam bskang gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:2327: rgyal sras mchod pas mnyes gyur nas //
NK013(pa)014:2328: mthar phyin dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK013(pa)014:2330: bkra shis rdzas rtags sna bdun gos /
NK013(pa)014:2332: lha yi dbang po lha min g.yul rgyal nas //
NK013(pa)014:2333: bkra shis lha mo brgyad kyis mchod pa ltar //
NK013(pa)014:2334: rgyal ba kun dngos sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba la //
NK013(pa)014:2335: bkra shis rdzas brgyad dag gis mchod par bya //
NK013(pa)014:2336: ash+ta mang+ga la pu dza ho /
NK013(pa)014:2338: bkra shis gang zhig mchod pa'i lha rnams kyi //
NK013(pa)014:2339: phyag na gdugs dung pad+ma gser gyi nya //
NK013(pa)014:2340: dpal be'u bkra shis rgyal mtshan 'khor lo ni //
NK013(pa)014:2341: legs par thogs nas dkyil 'khor lha tshogs mchod //
NK013(pa)014:2342: mang+ga la rat+na p+au dzi te ahmh'u /
NK013(pa)014:2346: mkhas pa rnams kyis yongs bskang ste //
NK013(pa)014:2347: dngos grub 'bras bu sgrub pa'i phyir //
NK013(pa)014:2348: nyin re shes rab can gyis dbul //
NK013(pa)014:2349: tsakra rat+na pu dzi te a h'u /
NK013(pa)014:2351: nor bu btsun mo blon po glang po rta mchog dmag dpon rnams dang /
NK013(pa)014:2352: ma ni rat+na s+t+r+ai rat+na pu ru sha ha sti tu ra sga a shwa kharga rnams kyis 'bul /
NK013(pa)014:2354: srab 'jam yangs pa lha yi gos //
NK013(pa)014:2355: mi phyed rdo rje'i sku la gsol //
NK013(pa)014:2356: mi shig rdo rje'i sku la 'bul //
NK013(pa)014:2357: bdag cag rdo rje'i sku thob shog /
NK013(pa)014:2358: badz+ra was se pra tits+tsha yes+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:2359: de ltar mchod pa phul bas lha rnams mnyes te lha mo rnams rang la thim par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:2361: dkyil 'khor pa'i lha yab rnams kyi rdo rje h'u las rtse lnga pa'i lte bar sa bon dang /
NK013(pa)014:2362: yum mkha' pad+ma 'dab brgyad la sa bon dang /
NK013(pa)014:2363: bu ga phata kyis mtshan pa /
NK013(pa)014:2365: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa go ham /
NK013(pa)014:2366: a nu ra ga ya mye /
NK013(pa)014:2367: sbyor ba'i brdas phan tshun bsnol mar bskul te //
NK013(pa)014:2368: dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes snyoms par zhugs shing rgyal ba
NK013(pa)014:2369: thams cad bde ba chen po'i ye shes sems lnga'i
NK013(pa)014:2371: 'gro ba thams cad bde chen gyis tshim par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:2375: dgyes pa'i rdo rje gsor mdzad nas //
NK013(pa)014:2376: byang chub sems sprin dbab tu gsol //
NK013(pa)014:2377: rdo rje gsor ba'i dga' mchog 'di /
NK013(pa)014:2381: rdo rje 'dzin mar ldan las byung //
NK013(pa)014:2382: shes rab dbyings ma yum gyi gzhal yas su //
NK013(pa)014:2383: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus rab bkod de //
NK013(pa)014:2384: thabs dang shes rab 'brel pa'i sbyor mchod 'di //
NK013(pa)014:2385: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor tshogs la mchod par 'bul //
NK013(pa)014:2386: sarba ta th+aa ga t+aa a nu r+aa ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:2387: badz+ra pra we sha ya a la la ho /
NK013(pa)014:2389: thugs ka nas ram gyis snod 'jig rten dang //
NK013(pa)014:2393: rnam shes h'u du gyur pa rang gi zhal nas gyi mkha' la bab /
NK013(pa)014:2394: rdo rje sems dpar gyur pa'i gtsug tu kun bzang
NK013(pa)014:2395: gis mtshan pa nyi zla'i bar du bzhag nas rlung
NK013(pa)014:2397: s+pha ra na phata kyis 'og min du rnam snang gi mdzod spur thim par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:2398: de las mchod sbyin dam pa ni /
NK013(pa)014:2399: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK013(pa)014:2400: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK013(pa)014:2401: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK013(pa)014:2402: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK013(pa)014:2403: zhing gyur mchog dang mchog phran rnams //
NK013(pa)014:2404: nyi zla'i dkyil du mkhas pas bzhag /
NK013(pa)014:2405: nga rgyal lag gi 'du byed bsgom //
NK013(pa)014:2406: h'u du gyur nas rnam par dag /
NK013(pa)014:2407: dbyings su thim nas phyag rgya 'bar //
NK013(pa)014:2409: gtsug tu rnam par rgyal ba sgom //
NK013(pa)014:2410: ngo mtshar ngan 'gro thar pa'i thabs //
NK013(pa)014:2411: ye nas skye med de bzhin nyid //
NK013(pa)014:2412: sbyor srol bya ba kun byas kyang //
NK013(pa)014:2413: rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med //
NK013(pa)014:2415: hoh rang byung gdod nas dag pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:2416: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK013(pa)014:2417: rig lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK013(pa)014:2418: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK013(pa)014:2419: rgyud lnga'i sems can kun sgrol ba //
NK013(pa)014:2420: sdug bsngal sel ba'i bdud rtsi ste //
NK013(pa)014:2421: thams cad bdud rtsi'i rnal 'byor che //
NK013(pa)014:2422: byang chub sems ni rdo rje che //
NK013(pa)014:2423: pad+ma me tog yang dag ldan //
NK013(pa)014:2424: ga bur shel gyi pog phor dri //
NK013(pa)014:2425: gtsang dme med pa dri med chu //
NK013(pa)014:2426: rin chen me ltar 'bar ba'i tshogs //
NK013(pa)014:2427: ma 'dus bsdus pa'i thig le ste //
NK013(pa)014:2428: gcig tu dpa' bo'i ro rnams dang //
NK013(pa)014:2429: gnyis su med par mnyam sbyar ba /
NK013(pa)014:2431: / 'chi med bdud rtsi ra s+aa yan //
NK013(pa)014:2432: rgyal ba rgya mtsho kun gyi gsos //
NK013(pa)014:2433: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK013(pa)014:2434: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen dang //
NK013(pa)014:2435: khro bo'i rgyal po mtha' yas dang //
NK013(pa)014:2436: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs chen dang //
NK013(pa)014:2437: lha dang lha min gsang ba yi //
NK013(pa)014:2438: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskul ba'i mchog /
NK013(pa)014:2439: 'di ni sngon gyi dam tshig go //
NK013(pa)014:2440: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK013(pa)014:2441: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid 'di //
NK013(pa)014:2442: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK013(pa)014:2443: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK013(pa)014:2444: phul ba'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK013(pa)014:2446: rgyal ba thams cad dang dbyer med pa'i dpal mgon
NK013(pa)014:2447: bla ma rin po che'i zhal du +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa
NK013(pa)014:2448: a mri ta kha ram kha hi /
NK013(pa)014:2449: kun bzang rigs lnga rigs gsum d+r+aa ma lnga //
NK013(pa)014:2450: chos rgyal yab sras sa brgyad sems ma dang //
NK013(pa)014:2451: rdo rje yon tan h'u mdzad phra chen zhabs //
NK013(pa)014:2452: sangs rgyas gsang ba rnams la bdud rtsis mchod //
NK013(pa)014:2453: +aahmh'u sarba u rgyan chen po pan chen bi ma la //
NK013(pa)014:2454: rma lo kyi re zhang ban gnubs yab sras //
NK013(pa)014:2455: ye shes rgya mtsho blo gros byang chub dang //
NK013(pa)014:2456: zur ba mes dbon +aahmh'u sarba rdzogs chen pa dang 'jam dbyangs kahthoga pa //
NK013(pa)014:2457: chos rje yab sras nam mkha' rdo rje'i zhabs //
NK013(pa)014:2458: thugs rje dbang 'byor dpal 'bar rgyal mtshan gnyis /
NK013(pa)014:2459: d+h+aarma lak+sha rnams la +aahmh'u sarba ye shes rgyal mtshan nam mkha' rnam gsum dang //
NK013(pa)014:2460: chos dbang bsod nams chos 'byung sh+aakya'i mtshan //
NK013(pa)014:2461: rin chen sangs rgyas sh+aakya u rgyan mtshan //
NK013(pa)014:2462: thugs kyi rdo rje rnams la +aahmh'u sarba rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyis //
NK013(pa)014:2463: srid gsum sdug bsngal sel mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)014:2464: bde gshegs kun bzang yab yum la //
NK013(pa)014:2465: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa 'bul //
NK013(pa)014:2466: +aahmh'u sarba phung po lnga dang 'byung ba lnga /
NK013(pa)014:2467: ye shes dbyings su rnams dag pa //
NK013(pa)014:2468: rigs lnga bder gshegs yab yum la //
NK013(pa)014:2469: dam rdzas rnam shes tshogs dang spyod yul rnams //
NK013(pa)014:2470: byang chub sems su rnam dag pa //
NK013(pa)014:2471: sems dpa' lcam dral tshogs rnams la //
NK013(pa)014:2472: dam tshig thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK013(pa)014:2474: / 'gro drug dbyings su sbyor mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)014:2475: sprul sku thub pa drug rnams la //
NK013(pa)014:2476: dam tshig phyi nang bdud tshogs thams cad 'dul mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)014:2477: gnas yul ro lang rdo rje bcing sdoms 'bab //
NK013(pa)014:2478: sprul pa'i sgo skyong khro rgyal yab yum la //
NK013(pa)014:2479: rnam dag dam tshig dus rnams kun tu 'gro la brtser dgongs shing //
NK013(pa)014:2480: dug gsum dug lnga ma spangs gnas dag pa //
NK013(pa)014:2481: dus gsum bzhugs pa'i rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK013(pa)014:2482: rnam dag tshe rabs sngon nas las kyi 'phro mthud pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:2483: mched dang lcam dral karma ging la sogs //
NK013(pa)014:2484: rdo rje lcam dral ma lus 'khor bcas la //
NK013(pa)014:2485: rnam dag +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kha h+ai /
NK013(pa)014:2486: mthar rang gi gnas gsum du bdud rtsi'i thig le cig bkod de /
NK013(pa)014:2488: rdo rje lce yis dam tshig la //
NK013(pa)014:2489: rdo rje can gyi 'bru gsum bsgom //
NK013(pa)014:2490: bdud rtsi lnga dang sbyar ba'i sman //
NK013(pa)014:2491: mya ngan dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK013(pa)014:2492: sarba ta tha ga ta ka ya sid+d+hi /
NK013(pa)014:2497: bka' gsang rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK013(pa)014:2498: khams drug ldan pa rdo rje'i lha mor bcas //
NK013(pa)014:2499: bza' bca' btung ba'i mchod pa dam pa rnams /
NK013(pa)014:2500: rmad byung gtor ma chen por spungs te 'bul //
NK013(pa)014:2501: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bsgo //
NK013(pa)014:2502: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni //
NK013(pa)014:2504: chos nyid la yang chos nyid rol //
NK013(pa)014:2506: gzugs ni lag gnyis me long 'dzin //
NK013(pa)014:2507: gzugs mdzes spyod pas phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK013(pa)014:2508: shin tu sgegs pa'i gzi byin 'bar //
NK013(pa)014:2509: gzugs kyi lha mo spyan la thim //
NK013(pa)014:2511: sgra ni lag gnyis pi wam brdeg /
NK013(pa)014:2512: bde ba'i sgra snyan phyogs bcur sgrogs //
NK013(pa)014:2514: sgra yi lha mo snyan la thim //
NK013(pa)014:2516: dri ni lag gnyis spos bsnams te //
NK013(pa)014:2517: spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa mo //
NK013(pa)014:2518: kun tu tshim byed dri bsrung ldan //
NK013(pa)014:2519: dri yi lha mo shangs la thim //
NK013(pa)014:2521: ro ni lag gnyis snod bsnam ste //
NK013(pa)014:2522: bcud ldan ro mchog lnga brgyar 'phro //
NK013(pa)014:2523: shin tu sgegs pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK013(pa)014:2524: ro yi lha mo ljags la thim //
NK013(pa)014:2526: reg ni rdo rje yang 'khyud ma //
NK013(pa)014:2527: mnyen 'jam reg na bde ba yi //
NK013(pa)014:2528: gzugs mdzes sgod pa phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK013(pa)014:2529: shin tu sgegs pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK013(pa)014:2530: reg gi lha mo sku la 'khril //
NK013(pa)014:2533: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i sku //
NK013(pa)014:2534: shin tu sgegs pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK013(pa)014:2535: chos kyi lha mo thugs kar thim //
NK013(pa)014:2536: d+harma t+tu s+w+aa b+h+aa w+aa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:2537: gtor ma'i steng las 'dod yon gyi lha mo du ma spros /
NK013(pa)014:2538: rgyal ba rnams kyi spyan shang thugs ka sku lus la thim /
NK013(pa)014:2539: gtor ma'i bar bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho lha rnams kyi ljags rdo rje sbu gur gyur pas gsol /
NK013(pa)014:2540: 'og dug gsum sha khrag rus pa'i rgya mtsho sgob
NK013(pa)014:2541: chos skyong gi tshogs kyis ljags gri gug tu gyur
NK013(pa)014:2542: pas gsol nas mnyes par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:2543: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su khu dz+ny+aa na d+hartu
NK013(pa)014:2544: +aah sa p+aa ri wa ra i dam ma ma
NK013(pa)014:2545: h+aa ba lin+ta kha kha hi kha hi /
NK013(pa)014:2547: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las dang /
NK013(pa)014:2548: nyon mongs lnga yi de kho na /
NK013(pa)014:2549: don gyi mchod pa de kho na /
NK013(pa)014:2550: ye shes rol mo'i de kho na /
NK013(pa)014:2551: de ldan mchod pa'i yon tan lnga /
NK013(pa)014:2553: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyis //
NK013(pa)014:2554: dge dang sdig pa'i las byas pa //
NK013(pa)014:2555: thams cad sangs rgyas mdzad spyod de //
NK013(pa)014:2556: las kyi mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:2557: sarba ta th+aa ga t+aa karma p+au dza h'u /
NK013(pa)014:2558: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyis //
NK013(pa)014:2559: gzugs la sogs pa 'dod rnams dang //
NK013(pa)014:2560: chags las gyur pa'i bde ba ste //
NK013(pa)014:2561: sangs rgyas rnams la phul gyur nas //
NK013(pa)014:2562: rdo rje rin chen 'dra bar gyur //
NK013(pa)014:2563: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a nu r+aa ga p+au dza h'u /
NK013(pa)014:2564: nam mkha'i mtha' klas 'jig rten na //
NK013(pa)014:2565: snang zhing srid pa'i gzugs rnams kun //
NK013(pa)014:2566: phyag rgya sna tshogs dkyil 'khor la //
NK013(pa)014:2567: sku mchog phyag rgya'i mchod par bzhes //
NK013(pa)014:2568: sarba ta th+aa ga t+aa k+aa ya p+au dza h'u /
NK013(pa)014:2569: nam mkha'i mtha' klas 'jig rten na //
NK013(pa)014:2570: sgrar grags pa ni bye snyed rnams //
NK013(pa)014:2571: thams cad ma lus sngags kyi tshig /
NK013(pa)014:2572: gsung mchog chos kyi mchod pa bzhes //
NK013(pa)014:2573: sarba ta tha ga t+aa wak+ka pu dza h'u /
NK013(pa)014:2574: nam mkha'i mtha' klas 'jig rten na //
NK013(pa)014:2575: sems can rnams kyi sems rtogs rnams //
NK013(pa)014:2577: dmigs pa'i dam tshig mchod par bzhes //
NK013(pa)014:2578: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa ma ya ti p+au dza h'u /
NK013(pa)014:2580: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyis //
NK013(pa)014:2581: zhe sdang spyod pa'i las rnams kun //
NK013(pa)014:2582: rdo rje rigs kyi mdzad spyod de //
NK013(pa)014:2583: sgrol ba'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:2584: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK013(pa)014:2585: gti mug spyod pa'i las rnams kun //
NK013(pa)014:2586: bder gshegs rigs kyi mdzad spyod de //
NK013(pa)014:2587: rtog med mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:2588: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyis //
NK013(pa)014:2589: nga rgyal spyod pa'i las rnams kun //
NK013(pa)014:2590: rin chen rigs kyi mdzad spyod de //
NK013(pa)014:2591: ting 'dzin mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:2592: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi /
NK013(pa)014:2594: / 'dod chags spyod pa'i pad+ma'i rigs sbyor ba'i srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK013(pa)014:2595: phrag dog spyod pa'i las rnams kun //
NK013(pa)014:2596: las kyi rigs kyi mdzad spyod de //
NK013(pa)014:2597: dam tshig mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:2599: rang lus rnam par mi rtog par //
NK013(pa)014:2600: bshig nas stong pa nyid du bsgom //
NK013(pa)014:2601: de lta bu yi chos nyid kyis //
NK013(pa)014:2603: ri rab chen po'i gling bzhi la //
NK013(pa)014:2604: gnas pa'i sems can thams cad kun //
NK013(pa)014:2605: bdag nyid chen po rtogs pa yis //
NK013(pa)014:2606: dbyings su yang ni spa bar bya'o //
NK013(pa)014:2608: dbang po'i spyod yul rang bzhin dngos po med //
NK013(pa)014:2609: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin sdug bsngal sel //
NK013(pa)014:2610: dam rdzas dag pa lnga dang zhal zas lnga //
NK013(pa)014:2611: sku lnga chos lnga rang bzhin dbyer med bsams //
NK013(pa)014:2612: de phyir dag pas dag pa nyid mchod phyir //
NK013(pa)014:2613: chos nyid la yang chos nyid thim par 'bul //
NK013(pa)014:2614: dri med rnam dag nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK013(pa)014:2615: log rtog mtshan ma med pa'i sprin dpungs te //
NK013(pa)014:2616: ye shes nyi ma'i 'od kyis rab brgyan nas //
NK013(pa)014:2617: dag pa'i don phyir rtogs nas mchod par 'bul //
NK013(pa)014:2618: mnyam nyid blang dor med la snyoms par bzhengs //
NK013(pa)014:2619: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs pa sku yi rgyan /
NK013(pa)014:2621: / 'dod yon lnga yi lha mor byin rlabs pa //
NK013(pa)014:2622: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:2623: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK013(pa)014:2625: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:2630: glu tshigs sgra yi phyag rgya'am //
NK013(pa)014:2631: chos kyi dngos grub thor par 'gyur //
NK013(pa)014:2632: rgyan dang bgo ba'i phyag rgya yis /
NK013(pa)014:2635: bza' dang btung bar phyag rgya yis //
NK013(pa)014:2636: yid bzhin sku dang bdud rtsi 'grub //
NK013(pa)014:2637: a li ka li'i phyag rgya yis //
NK013(pa)014:2640: zhi gsang thabs zhags kyi glu rnams te //
NK013(pa)014:2641: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yis //
NK013(pa)014:2642: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le che //
NK013(pa)014:2643: bsod nams dkyil 'khor sku yi tshogs //
NK013(pa)014:2644: snang stong thig le kun tu rdzogs //
NK013(pa)014:2646: rdo rje bsod nams thig le che //
NK013(pa)014:2647: rdo rje ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK013(pa)014:2648: rdo rje sgra chen mtha' yas pa //
NK013(pa)014:2649: rdo rje rgyal po thig le che //
NK013(pa)014:2651: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK013(pa)014:2652: yon tan phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK013(pa)014:2653: ye nas lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang /
NK013(pa)014:2655: / 'dus pa'i tshogs chen thig le che //
NK013(pa)014:2657: mi dmigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK013(pa)014:2658: mtha' yas kun nas sna tshogs 'phro //
NK013(pa)014:2659: mtha' yas kun nas lhan gyis thim //
NK013(pa)014:2660: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen po //
NK013(pa)014:2662: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK013(pa)014:2663: rgyal ba'i don rnams rdul phran snyed //
NK013(pa)014:2664: sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK013(pa)014:2665: skad gcig yud la lhun gyis grub //
NK013(pa)014:2667: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK013(pa)014:2668: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK013(pa)014:2669: sku gsung thugs kyis kun tu khyab //
NK013(pa)014:2670: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che //
NK013(pa)014:2673: rgyal ba gang bzhugs 'khor dang bcas //
NK013(pa)014:2674: bla med lha dang lha mo yi //
NK013(pa)014:2675: grub pa'i byin brlab bsam mi khyab /
NK013(pa)014:2677: // sems dpa' bcu drug rigs kyi gtso //
NK013(pa)014:2678: sems ma bcu drug rigs kyi yum //
NK013(pa)014:2679: mthu chen khro bo khro mo dang //
NK013(pa)014:2680: pho nya 'jig rten skyongs bar ldan /
NK013(pa)014:2682: // sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni /
NK013(pa)014:2684: / 'jig rten thams cad ma lus kun //
NK013(pa)014:2685: rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyor bas na //
NK013(pa)014:2686: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK013(pa)014:2687: dpa' bo chen po mthu ldan rnams //
NK013(pa)014:2688: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK013(pa)014:2689: bdag gis lhag pa'i bsam pa rnams //
NK013(pa)014:2690: grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK013(pa)014:2692: // khams gsum zhing du sbyor la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:2693: dmigs med chos kyi sku longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku
NK013(pa)014:2694: la cir yang sprul pa'i sku bcu gnyis pa bshags
NK013(pa)014:2695: smon ni / hoh ye nas spros pa med pa'i dbyings //
NK013(pa)014:2696: rang bzhin rnam par dag pa na //
NK013(pa)014:2697: dus gsum gshegs shing bzhugs pa yis //
NK013(pa)014:2698: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das //
NK013(pa)014:2699: rnam pa thams cad kun mkhyen pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:2700: ye shes bye brag kun ldan pa /
NK013(pa)014:2703: bcom ldan rdo rje sems sogs te //
NK013(pa)014:2704: rigs lnga bde bar gshegs pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:2705: rigs mchog gzungs kyi yum dang bcas //
NK013(pa)014:2706: rgyal sras 'khor du sems dpa'i tshogs //
NK013(pa)014:2707: sems ma'i dkyil 'khor la sogs pa //
NK013(pa)014:2708: ye shes chen po'i dbang phyug che //
NK013(pa)014:2709: thabs la mkhas pa'i bdag nyid can //
NK013(pa)014:2711: ngo bo nyid sku ma lus shing //
NK013(pa)014:2712: rgyal ba rgya mtsho 'khor bcas pa //
NK013(pa)014:2713: khyed rnams gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:2717: dang po gsang sgor khas 'ches te //
NK013(pa)014:2718: dam tshig gnyen po mngon par mnos //
NK013(pa)014:2719: chag nyams zhig ral gyur pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:2720: rtsa ba yan lag dam mnos nas //
NK013(pa)014:2721: bka' bzhin bsrung bar rngo ma thogs //
NK013(pa)014:2722: bsrung ba'i dam tshig mnos pa las //
NK013(pa)014:2723: gti mug ma tshor dbang gis ni //
NK013(pa)014:2724: bde dang sdug bsngal rkyen ma bzod //
NK013(pa)014:2725: sgo gsum nyes skyon me shor bas //
NK013(pa)014:2726: bdag dang gzhan gyi rgyud bsregs pas //
NK013(pa)014:2727: skyon bral mtshan mar ma phyin te //
NK013(pa)014:2728: bsrung ba'i dam tshig nyams pa bshags //
NK013(pa)014:2730: tshor ba dang ni ma tshor ba'i //
NK013(pa)014:2731: nyams pa thams cad byang gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:2732: tshor dang ma tshor nyams pa rnams //
NK013(pa)014:2733: phyin chad mi byed par gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:2734: gnas thogs pa dang rgyud byang las //
NK013(pa)014:2735: slan chad phyir la mi ldogs pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:2736: sems dang 'bral bar ma gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:2737: shes rab rno zhing dbang po gsal //
NK013(pa)014:2738: ye shes can gyur sems can don //
NK013(pa)014:2739: ma lus byed pa'i mthu thob nas //
NK013(pa)014:2740: skyes pa'i tshe rabs thams cad du //
NK013(pa)014:2741: slob dpon bka' drin lan sdon cing //
NK013(pa)014:2742: pha ma'i drin lan rjes su sgrub //
NK013(pa)014:2743: man ngag snod dang ldan gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:2744: tshe 'di dang ni tshe rabs gzhan //
NK013(pa)014:2745: skyon brjod thams cad dang bral nas //
NK013(pa)014:2746: dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad du //
NK013(pa)014:2747: yon tan tshad bzhin thob gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:2749: dge ba'i rtsa ba bsgrub pa la //
NK013(pa)014:2750: bar chad byed pa'i sdang dgra dang //
NK013(pa)014:2751: sbyor ba rku dang gnod bgegs gsum //
NK013(pa)014:2752: zhi dang dbang dang mngon spyod kyis //
NK013(pa)014:2753: mnan dang bzlog dang spor zhing spar /
NK013(pa)014:2755: / 'dul skal phrin las mtshams pa bzhin //
NK013(pa)014:2756: tshar bcad grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK013(pa)014:2758: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgya snying gar bkod de /
NK013(pa)014:2760: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed de //
NK013(pa)014:2761: ye shes thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK013(pa)014:2762: gnyis med don gyi dngos grub mchog gi gnas //
NK013(pa)014:2763: bdag la stsal zhing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:2764: k+aa ya w+aa k+aa tsit+ta b+ho d+hi tsit+ta sa ma y+aa h'u /
NK013(pa)014:2766: gsum pa gsungs bzlas pa'i rnal 'byor la gnyis /
NK013(pa)014:2770: lha rtog gi bsnyen pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:2772: dang po la gtso brgyud 'khor brgyud gnyis kyi //
NK013(pa)014:2773: dang po gtso 'khor gyi sku lus go 'pho ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:2774: phyi ma shes pa go 'pho zhing bsgoms pa ste /
NK013(pa)014:2776: rtog tshogs de dag lha de dang der gyur nas
NK013(pa)014:2777: dbu'i gtsug tor dang gdan khri nas lus sku yongs
NK013(pa)014:2781: rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK013(pa)014:2782: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa //
NK013(pa)014:2783: mi bskyod yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK013(pa)014:2784: ting 'dzin thugs su dbang bskur nas //
NK013(pa)014:2785: dngos grub las rnams 'grub byed shog /
NK013(pa)014:2789: de nas rang kun bzang du gsal ba rigs 'gres la /
NK013(pa)014:2790: yid ni rang rig ma skyes pa //
NK013(pa)014:2791: kun tu bzang mo'i rang bzhin las //
NK013(pa)014:2792: ting 'dzin byed par dbang bsgyur nas //
NK013(pa)014:2793: ma lus kun gyi byed por shog /
NK013(pa)014:2794: chos ni de bzhin ma skyes pa //
NK013(pa)014:2795: kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin las //
NK013(pa)014:2796: ting 'dzin bya bar dbang bsgyur nas //
NK013(pa)014:2797: ma lus kun gyi bya bar shog /
NK013(pa)014:2798: h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK013(pa)014:2799: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta ah gzugs phung sa yi ngo bo nyid //
NK013(pa)014:2800: sems phyir snang mdzad yab yum ting 'dzin sku ru dngos grub las rnams grub byed shog /
NK013(pa)014:2803: tshor ba chu yi rang bzhin las //
NK013(pa)014:2804: sems phyir 'byung ldan ting 'dzin yon tan dngos grub s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rika /
NK013(pa)014:2806: 'du shes me yi sems mtha' yas ting 'dzin gsungs
NK013(pa)014:2807: gi dngos grub a ro lika pyam ra ga ra
NK013(pa)014:2808: ti / 'du byed rlung gi sems don grub ting 'dzin phrin las dngos grub h+aa p+r+aadz+ny+aa d+h+rika /
NK013(pa)014:2810: mig gzugs sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK013(pa)014:2811: sa snying yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK013(pa)014:2812: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bsgyur bas //
NK013(pa)014:2813: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK013(pa)014:2815: h'u l+aa s+ye sa ma stam /
NK013(pa)014:2816: sna dri sems nam snying ting 'dzin spyod yul tram a gar+b+ha ya /
NK013(pa)014:2817: t+r+aam ma l+ye sa ma ya ho /
NK013(pa)014:2818: lce ro spyan gzigs ting 'dzin spyod yul h+r+ai ha h'u pad+ma ba da ma /
NK013(pa)014:2819: hri girti r+aa ga ya ho /
NK013(pa)014:2820: rna sgra phyag rdor ting 'dzin spyod yul dz+rim ku
NK013(pa)014:2821: ru pa na h+r+aih a nirti r+aa ga ya mi
NK013(pa)014:2822: / mig dbang 'das dus ma skyes pa /
NK013(pa)014:2823: byams pa yab yum ting 'dzin spyod yul me d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:2824: dza d+h+au sh+pe pra we sha ya /
NK013(pa)014:2825: rna dbang da ltar sgrib sel ting 'dzin spyod yul th+l+him ni s+sa ram pa ya /
NK013(pa)014:2826: h'u push+pe a wa sha ya /
NK013(pa)014:2827: sna dbang ma 'ongs kun bzang ting 'dzin spyod yul h'u s+w+aa r+aa dz+aa ya /
NK013(pa)014:2828: p+aam di pa su khi n+ai /
NK013(pa)014:2829: lce dbang ma nges ma skyes sems /
NK013(pa)014:2831: / 'jam dpal ting 'dzin spyod yul m+aum sh+r+ai am r+aa g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:2833: reg shes rtag pa gshin rje ting 'dzin 'joms par dbang gdul bya ma lus mthar byed shog /
NK013(pa)014:2835: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa li n+aa h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:2836: reg yul chad pa stobs chen /
NK013(pa)014:2837: ting 'dzin gdul bya h'u pra dz+ny+aan+ta kri tra h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:2838: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa li n+aa h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:2839: reg dbang bdag 'dzin rta mgrin yab yum ting 'dzin gdul bya h'u pad+m+aan+ta kri tra phata /
NK013(pa)014:2840: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa li n+aa h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:2841: reg pa mtshan 'dzin ma skyes pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:2842: bdud rtsi ting 'dzin gdul bya ma lus h'u big+h+nan+ta kri tra phata /
NK013(pa)014:2843: ma h+aa karma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa li ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:2844: nga rgyal sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK013(pa)014:2845: brgya byin dbang po'i rang bzhin las //
NK013(pa)014:2846: ting 'dzin thub par dbang bsgyur nas /
NK013(pa)014:2850: phrag dog thag bzang ris kyi ting 'dzin 'gro ba lha min mu ne srum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:2851: 'dod chags sh+aakya ting 'dzin 'gro ba mi rnams mu ne h'u trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:2852: gti mug seng ge dam brten ting 'dzin 'gro ba byol song mu ne bram s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:2853: ser sna kha 'bar thub pa'i ting 'dzin 'gro ba yi dwags mu ne k+sham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:2854: zhe sdang gshin bu rje yi ting 'dzin 'gro ba dmyal ba mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)014:2856: thun re re rigs lnga kun bzang dang bcas la brgya rtsa res mtshon na /
NK013(pa)014:2857: sems dpa' la de'i phyed thub pa sgo ba nyer gcig re bzla bar gsungs so //
NK013(pa)014:2858: gnyis pa mnyam rdzogs la'ang mnyam rdzogs tsam dang /
NK013(pa)014:2861: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he phata dz+wahmh'u +amo s+w+aa +aam
NK013(pa)014:2862: h+aa phata dzah dam tshig gis dkyil 'khor las ye
NK013(pa)014:2863: shes kyi dkyil 'khor rten dang brten par bcas pa
NK013(pa)014:2865: mdun gyi nam mkha' la me ri 'dab 'byar gyi tshul du bzhugs par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:2866: rang rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi sems dpa'
NK013(pa)014:2867: sum brtsegs sngags phreng dang bcas pa'i sngags 'khor shang
NK013(pa)014:2868: bug g.yas nas yum gyi g.yon du thugs kar 'khor
NK013(pa)014:2869: / yang yum gyi g.yas nas rang gi g.yon brgyud 'khor /
NK013(pa)014:2870: dam tshig pa'i lha 'khor rnams dang /
NK013(pa)014:2871: ye shes pa gtso 'khor bcas pa'i thugs ka'i sngags phreng shang bug brgyud /
NK013(pa)014:2872: rang gi thugs kar 'khor bas byin bsdus /
NK013(pa)014:2873: rang gi thugs ka'i sngags phreng shang bug nas thon /
NK013(pa)014:2874: mchod pa'i tshul du lha de dag gi thugs kar 'khor bas dgyes pa bskyed /
NK013(pa)014:2875: 'od zer gyis sems can thams cad kyi sgrib pa bsal nas //
NK013(pa)014:2876: gsung rdo rje'i go 'phang la bkod /
NK013(pa)014:2877: slar 'dus te rang gi thugs kar thim par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:2878: gtso 'khor sngags tshang ma gong bzhin nam /
NK013(pa)014:2879: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+ha rtu ah zhes spyi dril bsnyen /
NK013(pa)014:2880: gnyis pa mnyam rdzogs chen pa /
NK013(pa)014:2881: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor lha yab rnams bdag mi bskyod pa la thim /
NK013(pa)014:2882: yum rnams gtso mo la thim ste 'od gsal du zhugs /
NK013(pa)014:2883: rang gi thugs ka'i sngags phreng gi 'od zer sngags kyi rnam pa shang g.yas nas thon /
NK013(pa)014:2884: mdun gyi ye shes sems dpa' la mchod pa'i tshul shangs bug g.yon nas brgyud /
NK013(pa)014:2885: thugs kar 'khor nas g.yas nas phyir thon /
NK013(pa)014:2886: rang gi g.yon nas thugs kar thim /
NK013(pa)014:2887: 'od gsal du zhugs pa'i lha rnams sku lus las phyir thon /
NK013(pa)014:2888: rang rang gi gdan steng du 'khod par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:2890: yab yum gtso bsnyen kho na bzlas pas kyang rung ngo //
NK013(pa)014:2891: mthar bzlas pa'i lta ba gsal gdab pa'i phyir /
NK013(pa)014:2892: yang dag don gyi snying po ni //
NK013(pa)014:2893: ji snyed brjod pa'i kha brgyud kyang /
NK013(pa)014:2894: gang nas brtsal kyang mi rnyed pas //
NK013(pa)014:2895: rang rig dri med dag pa yin //
NK013(pa)014:2896: de la rtag tu mos pa ni //
NK013(pa)014:2897: bsnyen pa'i dam pa mchog yin na //
NK013(pa)014:2898: sems nyid theg par rab nges te //
NK013(pa)014:2900: d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor mngon rdzogs pa //
NK013(pa)014:2901: da lta nyid du mngon gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:2904: dam ye 'phro 'du stegs la gsum gsal theb par dgos so //
NK013(pa)014:2905: bsnyen tshul 'di dag gang yang rung ba re'am /
NK013(pa)014:2906: mthar chags su bgyis kyang chog cig /
NK013(pa)014:2907: ci nus bzla ba mos sgom gyi dbang dang /
NK013(pa)014:2908: lam nges rdzogs la rtags dang dus dang /
NK013(pa)014:2909: grangs kyi dbye ba rgya cher gsungs pa rgyud dang man ngag las shes par bya'o //
NK013(pa)014:2910: gnyis pa mjug tu dngos grub gsol ba la'ang mchod bstod dang /
NK013(pa)014:2914: mdun gyi ye shes pa la kun bzang la zhabs bsil /
NK013(pa)014:2916: rol mo rnams sngags tsam gyis mchod /
NK013(pa)014:2918: bde ba las 'khrungs rdo rje 'chang ba'o //
NK013(pa)014:2919: dngos po dngos med 'byung gnas chen por mkhyen //
NK013(pa)014:2920: gang du dang por mi bskyod rdo rje ni //
NK013(pa)014:2921: dri med blo yis yi ge h'u du sprul //
NK013(pa)014:2922: gzugs med tshul gyis phreng bas bskor ba ni //
NK013(pa)014:2923: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:2924: gsung snyan yi ges kun la khyab pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:2925: spros med gsung du 'jig rten dbang phyug bzhugs //
NK013(pa)014:2926: mi gsung lha mo dam bcas 'dul mdzad pa //
NK013(pa)014:2927: sgyu 'phrul tshul mang ldan pa 'ga' ma mchis //
NK013(pa)014:2928: gang du bde chen rang bzhin rjes chags pa'i //
NK013(pa)014:2929: na chung dag dang lhan cig bzhad mdzad de //
NK013(pa)014:2930: g.yas kyi phyag gis rdo rje bsod nas kyang //
NK013(pa)014:2931: g.yon pa yis ni dril bu'i sgra snyan 'khrol //
NK013(pa)014:2932: lha mo mtha' dag btsun mor gyur pa yis //
NK013(pa)014:2933: dam tshig rnams kyi bya ba byed par 'gyur //
NK013(pa)014:2934: mnyam nyid mi g.yo mnyam nyid mchog gi rang bzhin can //
NK013(pa)014:2935: thugs rje'i bdag nyid 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sel bar mdzad //
NK013(pa)014:2936: yon tan mtha' yas dngos grub thams cad smin par mdzad //
NK013(pa)014:2937: dri med mi g.yo mnyam nyid dam pa'i mchog chos can //
NK013(pa)014:2938: yon tan shin tu phra ba'i cha la tshad med de //
NK013(pa)014:2939: dpe ni nam mkha' dang yang dkrun du yod ma yin //
NK013(pa)014:2940: dngos grub mtha' yas mnyam med dpe dang bral ba rnams //
NK013(pa)014:2941: sems can khams la dngos grub mchog rnams nges par stsol //
NK013(pa)014:2942: rtag tu dri ma med pa'i thugs rje shugs las byung //
NK013(pa)014:2943: smon lam 'grub pa 'gags pa med pa'i chos nyid can /
NK013(pa)014:2945: / 'gro ba'i don grub rab tu brtson pa mtha' yas pa //
NK013(pa)014:2946: thugs rje chen po'i bdag nyid rtag tu rnam par snang //
NK013(pa)014:2947: tshad med tshad dang bral ba shin tu rdzogs pa yis //
NK013(pa)014:2948: bde bar gshegs pa'i go 'phang dam pa brnyes gyur pa //
NK013(pa)014:2949: khams gsum kun la dngos grub mchog stsol mdzad pa yis //
NK013(pa)014:2950: thugs rje'i spyod pa mi g.yo 'gag par yongs mi 'gyur //
NK013(pa)014:2951: e ma ho shin tu bzang po'i chos nyid mchog dang ldan //
NK013(pa)014:2952: mchog sbyin rnams kyi nang nas go 'phang mchog brnyes pa //
NK013(pa)014:2953: khams gsum kun la rtag tu dngos grub mchog stsol mdzod //
NK013(pa)014:2954: mgon po dus gsum sgrib pa med par rab mkhyen pa //
NK013(pa)014:2955: dam tshig mchog gsum dngos grub dam pa bdag la stsol //
NK013(pa)014:2957: ye nas gnyis med chos skur dag pa las //
NK013(pa)014:2958: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang bskur btab ste //
NK013(pa)014:2959: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK013(pa)014:2960: de ldog don phyin rgyal ba'i dam mnos te //
NK013(pa)014:2961: bdag cag ma rig lus dang dag sems kyi //
NK013(pa)014:2962: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur pas //
NK013(pa)014:2963: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK013(pa)014:2964: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol /
NK013(pa)014:2965: dbyangs gsal rten snying yi ge brgya pas lhag chad kha bskang bar bya'o //
NK013(pa)014:2967: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i rgya bcas /
NK013(pa)014:2969: bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK013(pa)014:2970: sogs kyi mthar gnas gsum du rgya gtugs la /
NK013(pa)014:2971: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta k+aa ya sa ma ya /
NK013(pa)014:2972: b+hi d+hi tsit+ta w+aa ka sa ma ya +aah b+hi d+hi tsit+ta sa ma ya h'u /
NK013(pa)014:2973: zhes brjod pas mdun gyi ye shes pa'i dpral mgrin
NK013(pa)014:2974: snying ga nas sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i lha tshogs
NK013(pa)014:2975: byung / rang gi gnas gsum du thim /
NK013(pa)014:2978: rdo rje gsum mngon du byas /
NK013(pa)014:2979: slar yang bdag dang ye shes pa dbyer med du brtan pa'i phyir /
NK013(pa)014:2980: badz+ra sa ma ya +amo sogs nas /
NK013(pa)014:2982: zhes pa'i bar gong bzhin du brjod pas /
NK013(pa)014:2984: slar yi ge brgya pa'i sngags kyis brten pa mngon
NK013(pa)014:2985: du gyur pa chu la chu bzhag ltar bsam mo
NK013(pa)014:2986: // bzhi pa ting 'dzin phra mo'i 'jug ldang thugs kyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK013(pa)014:2987: ma h+aa'i a nu dang rjes su 'brel ba ste /
NK013(pa)014:2988: lus dkyil gsal dang lus dag dran /
NK013(pa)014:2991: spyi gtsug bde chen dkyil 'khor nas //
NK013(pa)014:2992: rnam par snang mdzad yab yum la //
NK013(pa)014:2993: sgo ba yab yum brgyad kyis bskor /
NK013(pa)014:2996: rtsa dang thig le sngags dang rlung //
NK013(pa)014:2997: dbu yi gtsug tor rtse mo ni //
NK013(pa)014:2998: rigs bdag kun bzang yab yum la //
NK013(pa)014:2999: thub drug sprul pa'i 'khor gyis bskor /
NK013(pa)014:3002: mgrin pa longs spyod dkyil 'khor la //
NK013(pa)014:3003: snang ba mtha' yas yab yum ni //
NK013(pa)014:3004: spyan ras gzigs dang glu ma dang //
NK013(pa)014:3005: kun bzang mar me ma yis bskor /
NK013(pa)014:3008: gnas rten grub pas g.yo bar grub //
NK013(pa)014:3009: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo la //
NK013(pa)014:3010: mi bskyod yab dang yum du bcas //
NK013(pa)014:3011: sa yi snying po sgeg mo dang //
NK013(pa)014:3012: byams pa bdug spos ma yis bskor /
NK013(pa)014:3014: / 'khor lo thig le sngags dang rlung /
NK013(pa)014:3017: lte ba sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK013(pa)014:3018: dkon mchog dpal ni yab yum la //
NK013(pa)014:3019: nam mkha'i snying po phreng ba ma //
NK013(pa)014:3020: sgrib sel me tog ma dang bcas /
NK013(pa)014:3024: / 'khor lo khams bcud sngags dang rlung //
NK013(pa)014:3025: gsang ba me rlung dkyil 'khor la //
NK013(pa)014:3026: grub pa gdon mi za ba ni //
NK013(pa)014:3027: phyag na rdo rje gar ma dang /
NK013(pa)014:3029: / 'jam dpal dri chab ma yi bskor /
NK013(pa)014:3031: / 'khor lo bdud rtsi yi ge g.yos /
NK013(pa)014:3034: gnyis pa lus ngag dran pa'i phyir /
NK013(pa)014:3035: rang gi lus nyid 'dom gang la //
NK013(pa)014:3036: thams cad tshang bas gnas pa ni //
NK013(pa)014:3037: kun gzhi de steng nyon yid med //
NK013(pa)014:3038: yab ni rgyu nyid ar gnas so //
NK013(pa)014:3039: rkang mthil rlung la sum mdo me //
NK013(pa)014:3040: lte ba chu la snying ga sa //
NK013(pa)014:3041: sgal tshig ri rab skra ni me //
NK013(pa)014:3042: mi mnyam med pa'i gru bzhi lus //
NK013(pa)014:3043: snying ga'i rtsa yi sgo bzhi la //
NK013(pa)014:3044: rkang brgyad ka ba rnam pa brgyad //
NK013(pa)014:3045: mig gnyis pany+tsa ra ga la //
NK013(pa)014:3046: sna ni rin chen pha gu nyid //
NK013(pa)014:3047: so ni d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed la //
NK013(pa)014:3049: rna ba rta ba nyid du gnas //
NK013(pa)014:3050: snying ni ma 'jig seng ge'i gdan //
NK013(pa)014:3051: mkhal ma stobs bcu glang po che //
NK013(pa)014:3052: mtsher ba rdzu 'phrul rta yi khri //
NK013(pa)014:3053: mchin pa dbang bcu rma bya nyid //
NK013(pa)014:3054: glo ba thogs med nam mkha' lding //
NK013(pa)014:3055: pho ba rin chen khri rkang la //
NK013(pa)014:3056: mchin khri dkar nag nyi zla'i gdan //
NK013(pa)014:3057: rgyu long chags med pad+ma yin //
NK013(pa)014:3058: khyab byed gzugs phung rnam snang mdzad //
NK013(pa)014:3059: srog 'dzin rnam shes mi bskyod pa //
NK013(pa)014:3060: mi mnyam tshor ba rin chen 'byung //
NK013(pa)014:3061: gyen rgyu 'du shes snang mtha' yas //
NK013(pa)014:3062: thur sel 'du byed don yod grub //
NK013(pa)014:3063: sra ba sa ni sangs rgyas spyan //
NK013(pa)014:3064: nam mkha' dbyings phyug ma nyid la //
NK013(pa)014:3065: gnyen pa'i chu dbyings ma m+aa ki //
NK013(pa)014:3066: dro ba med dbyings gos dkar mo //
NK013(pa)014:3067: bskyod pa rlung ni dam tshig sgrol //
NK013(pa)014:3068: bcud ni yab la snod ni yum //
NK013(pa)014:3069: spyad byar gyur pa'i btsun mo ni //
NK013(pa)014:3070: rgyu bas snying me rlung mig /
NK013(pa)014:3071: gzugs ni sgeg mor gnas pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:3072: shin tu rgyu ba nam mkha' nyid //
NK013(pa)014:3073: nam snying sna la gnas pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:3074: dri ni lha mo phreng ba mo //
NK013(pa)014:3075: mngon par rgyu ba spyan ras gzigs //
NK013(pa)014:3076: rdo rje myong mar byed pa ste //
NK013(pa)014:3077: ro ni lha mo glu len ma //
NK013(pa)014:3078: rab tu rgyu ba phyag rdor nyid //
NK013(pa)014:3079: rna ba la gnas thos pa la //
NK013(pa)014:3080: sgra ni las kyi gar byed ma //
NK013(pa)014:3081: rnam shes dbang po byang chub sems //
NK013(pa)014:3082: yul la snang ba mched pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:3083: thob par byed pa snang ba gsum //
NK013(pa)014:3084: byams pa me yi rlung du bshad //
NK013(pa)014:3085: dpyid ni 'das dus spos me ma //
NK013(pa)014:3086: sgrib sel sna yi rlung yin te //
NK013(pa)014:3087: da ltar dbyar ni me tog la //
NK013(pa)014:3088: kun bzang ma ni mngon par rgyu /
NK013(pa)014:3090: / 'byung dus ston te mar me ma /
NK013(pa)014:3092: / 'jam dpal rlung nyid gnas pa yang //
NK013(pa)014:3093: ma nges dgun de dri chab ma //
NK013(pa)014:3094: dbang por snang ba'i lha nyid kun //
NK013(pa)014:3095: rang la ye nas dus spyod yul /
NK013(pa)014:3097: / 'di ni snying rje thabs mchog yab //
NK013(pa)014:3098: chos ni stong pa shes rab yum //
NK013(pa)014:3099: zhe sdang dmyal bar snang ba yang //
NK013(pa)014:3100: thub pas zhe sdang me yang gsod //
NK013(pa)014:3101: ser snas yi dwags snang ba yang //
NK013(pa)014:3102: nga rgyal ri bsnyil thub pa yin //
NK013(pa)014:3103: gti mug byol song skyes pa la //
NK013(pa)014:3104: thub pas gti mug mun pa sel /
NK013(pa)014:3106: / 'dod chags mi yi skye gnas nyid /
NK013(pa)014:3109: khong khros lha ma yin du skye //
NK013(pa)014:3110: bdag gzhan dran pas lha min thub //
NK013(pa)014:3111: phrag dog lha yi gnas snang bas //
NK013(pa)014:3112: phrag dog lcags 'grol lha yi thub //
NK013(pa)014:3113: lus kyi 'dus te reg pa ni //
NK013(pa)014:3114: rdo rje reg pa gshin rje'i gshed //
NK013(pa)014:3115: reg pa sra ba sa yin te //
NK013(pa)014:3116: rtag par ma yin lcags kyu ma //
NK013(pa)014:3117: lus kyi dbang po reg byed nyid //
NK013(pa)014:3118: yab kyi rdo rje stobs po che //
NK013(pa)014:3119: gsher ba 'byung ba chu nyid de //
NK013(pa)014:3120: chad par ma yin zhags pa ma //
NK013(pa)014:3121: lus kyi yul ni reg bya nyid //
NK013(pa)014:3122: yum gyi pad+ma rta mgrin dpal //
NK013(pa)014:3123: tsha zhing dro ba me yin te //
NK013(pa)014:3124: bdag tu ma yin lcags sgrog ma //
NK013(pa)014:3125: lus kyi rnam par shes pa ni //
NK013(pa)014:3126: dam rdzas dkar dmar bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK013(pa)014:3127: g.yo rlung stong bde'i nam mkha' ni //
NK013(pa)014:3128: mtshan mar ma yin dril bu ma //
NK013(pa)014:3129: srid gsum khams gsum sems can la //
NK013(pa)014:3130: ye nas rang la lhun gyis grub //
NK013(pa)014:3131: rang gnas chen po rtogs gyur nas //
NK013(pa)014:3132: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor bskyed par bya //
NK013(pa)014:3134: lha de dag gi thugs kar mi shigs pa'i thig le dwangs ma lnga 'dus /
NK013(pa)014:3135: 'od lnga'i rang bzhin 'tsher ba re re bsgoms te /
NK013(pa)014:3136: de yi dbus su dkyil 'khor yongs rdzogs re gsal btab pa la sems bzung zhing /
NK013(pa)014:3137: rdo rje'i bzlas pa 'bru gsum spro bsdu dang sbyar
NK013(pa)014:3138: ba'i 'od gsal gyi rnal 'byor zab mos phyi snod
NK013(pa)014:3139: nang bcud thams cad stong pa'i ngang la mnyam par
NK013(pa)014:3140: 'jog pa dang / de gsal gdab pa'i phyir /
NK013(pa)014:3145: gsang ba'i thig le dkyil 'khor dbyings /
NK013(pa)014:3147: / 'byung ba shes rab rigs kyi yum //
NK013(pa)014:3148: chen po'i rigs kyi de bzhin nyid //
NK013(pa)014:3149: byang chub sems ni rdo rje'i tshogs //
NK013(pa)014:3150: dbang po yul dus rig pa rnams //
NK013(pa)014:3151: kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK013(pa)014:3152: bdag nyid chen po ltag pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:3153: thugs kyi ye shes lngas bltar zhing //
NK013(pa)014:3154: snying po thig le mnyam sbyor bas //
NK013(pa)014:3155: bde ba'i ye shes rol mo yis //
NK013(pa)014:3156: ye shes dgyes la mchod par 'bul //
NK013(pa)014:3157: zag pa med pa'i bsod nams kyis //
NK013(pa)014:3158: ye shes sgyu mar rang snang ba //
NK013(pa)014:3159: rol mo'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas mchog /
NK013(pa)014:3160: gsang ba'i thig le nyid kyi dbyings //
NK013(pa)014:3161: de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK013(pa)014:3162: ces nges pa'i shes pa bskyed do //
NK013(pa)014:3163: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa la /
NK013(pa)014:3166: dang po la tshogs kyi mchod pa /
NK013(pa)014:3171: sngon du bya dang gsol ba gdab /
NK013(pa)014:3172: mtshams bcad byin rlabs byin dbab dang /
NK013(pa)014:3173: mchod cing tshims par bya ba'o //
NK013(pa)014:3175: tshogs kyi man+dala dza gad pany+tsa dang sbyar ba nub /
NK013(pa)014:3182: dar dmar mthing gi zhal kheb dang /
NK013(pa)014:3183: phyi nang gi mchod pa sbyar /
NK013(pa)014:3184: 'byung po phyogs skyong la gtor ma bsngo /
NK013(pa)014:3185: gnyis pa las rdor gyis 'khor lo'i gtso bo la phyag gsum 'tshal nas /
NK013(pa)014:3187: rdo rje slob dpon dpal dang ldan //
NK013(pa)014:3188: srid pa'i sdug bsngal bcad pa dang //
NK013(pa)014:3189: byis pa'i lam nas brgal ba'i phyir //
NK013(pa)014:3190: spyod pa'i khyad par mdzad du gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3191: phyogs bcu dus bzhi bsam yas kyis //
NK013(pa)014:3192: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad dang //
NK013(pa)014:3193: sras kyi tshogs 'dus ji snyed pa //
NK013(pa)014:3194: spyod pa'i khyad par 'di las byung //
NK013(pa)014:3195: bde bas bde ba chen po yi //
NK013(pa)014:3196: ngo mtshar yang dag bstan du gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3197: byang chub snying po mchog gi bar //
NK013(pa)014:3198: bde mchog spyod pa yang dag blang //
NK013(pa)014:3199: zhes lan gsum gsol ba gdab bo //
NK013(pa)014:3201: sum+b+ha ni sogs brjod cing bgegs gtor dor /
NK013(pa)014:3203: sa yi phyogs 'dir gsang spyod lta ba la mi dbang ba thams cad rgyang ring du byer cig /
NK013(pa)014:3209: rang gi thugs ka nas ram yam kham gsum spros /
NK013(pa)014:3210: tshogs kyi zhal zas thams cad bsreg gtor sbyang ste stong par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:3211: kro d+hi shwa r+ai h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:3213: stong pa nyid kyi ngang las tshogs gzhong b+han+d+ha rin po che'i gzhal med khang yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK013(pa)014:3219: 'og dus gsum sha khrag rus pa'i mchod pa tshogs rdzas kun bzang nam mkha'i mdzod du gyur /
NK013(pa)014:3222: stong pa'i ngang las rang gi thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum chad /
NK013(pa)014:3223: mu tig dri ma med pa dkar po lta bu'i sogs sman byin rlabs yongs rdzogs nas /
NK013(pa)014:3224: h'u h+r+ai th+aah lnga pa spyan 'dren dang /
NK013(pa)014:3227: badz+ra sa ma ya h'u dzah rdo rje sems dpa' sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK013(pa)014:3228: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa'i bshes gnyen te //
NK013(pa)014:3229: sprul pa zhi khro mang po'i 'byung gnas gtso /
