NK013(pa)014:3231: / 'gro ba'i don phyir mchod cing gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3232: thugs rje chen po ye shes sgrol 'bar ba //
NK013(pa)014:3233: nyi zla lta bur sgrib pa sel mdzad cing //
NK013(pa)014:3234: yon tan mchog gis brgyan cing bsgrub pa'i mgon //
NK013(pa)014:3235: mchod gnas dpal zhing dam par gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3236: rin chen dbyig ltar shin tu mdzes pa'i sku //
NK013(pa)014:3237: mnyam nyid ye shes nam mkha'i dbyings ltar dag /
NK013(pa)014:3238: 'gro ba ma lus bsgral bar dam bcas la //
NK013(pa)014:3239: bka' drin dran phyir mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3240: chags rab don phyir ma lus dbang du bsdud //
NK013(pa)014:3241: rtog pa'i ye shes thar lam 'dren pa'i dpal //
NK013(pa)014:3242: chu skyes kha 'bus 'gro ba'i yid bsgyur ba //
NK013(pa)014:3243: dag pa'i don phyir mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3244: ye shes mtshon chen dug gsum rtsad nas gcod //
NK013(pa)014:3245: nan tan ye shes sprul pa phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NK013(pa)014:3246: phrin las rnam bzhi 'gro drug bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK013(pa)014:3247: mnyam pa'i don phyir mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3248: shes rab dbyings ma'i rigs kyi yum lnga'i ngang //
NK013(pa)014:3249: chos dbyings ye shes nam mkhar gsal ba dang //
NK013(pa)014:3250: gsang chen bde ba'i longs spyod rdzogs pa'i ngang //
NK013(pa)014:3251: thabs kyi phyag rgyar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3252: rtogs pa'i ye shes rigs kyi phyag rgyar snang //
NK013(pa)014:3253: thabs kyi ma rmongs phrin las mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK013(pa)014:3254: thugs rje'i spyod pas yon tan mthar phyin pa //
NK013(pa)014:3255: sems dpa' chen po mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3256: phyi nang gnyis kyi lha mo dam tshig ma //
NK013(pa)014:3257: phyag rgya bzhi yi ye shes gsal ba las //
NK013(pa)014:3258: gar dang phyag rgyas rol cing dgyes mdzad de //
NK013(pa)014:3259: gtso mchog thugs dam bskangs phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3260: tikra ta khro bo gdug pa 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK013(pa)014:3261: thugs rje thabs kyis phyogs skyong zhabs kyis gnon //
NK013(pa)014:3262: h'u dang phata kyi 'brug sgra ldir ba las //
NK013(pa)014:3263: brjid pa'i thabs kyis 'gying zhing gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3264: gzhal yas phyogs bzhi'i ye shes bzhi yi ngang //
NK013(pa)014:3265: byams dang snying rje dga' ba btang snyoms tshul //
NK013(pa)014:3266: thar pa'i lam ston yang dag dbyings la bkod //
NK013(pa)014:3267: sgo skyongs spyan 'dren mchod kyi gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3268: sku gsung thugs las sprul pa'i pho nya mo //
NK013(pa)014:3269: phrin las rnam bzhi rdzogs par mdzad 'tshal gyis //
NK013(pa)014:3270: ye shes skar ltar 'khrugs pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK013(pa)014:3271: dam tshig rjes dgongs mchod cing gshegs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3272: e h+ya hi sogs kyis spyan drangs rgya bcas /
NK013(pa)014:3273: sh+r+ai badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah sh+r+ai badz+ra p+aa sha h'u /
NK013(pa)014:3275: sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+de hoh gnyis pa ni /
NK013(pa)014:3276: 'byung ba chen po nam mkha' ni /
NK013(pa)014:3277: sogs sngags dang bcas pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:3278: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das /
NK013(pa)014:3279: sogs gong kun bzang mchod pa'i skabs 'byung ba sngags dang bcas pas mchod /
NK013(pa)014:3280: kun bzang phyi nang gsang ba de kho na nyid tshigs bcad du bsdeb pa /
NK013(pa)014:3281: ting nge 'dzin gyi sbir gyis legs bris pa /
NK013(pa)014:3283: / 'jig rten snang ba rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor na //
NK013(pa)014:3284: rgya mtsho'i yon chab lho sprin bdug spos 'thul //
NK013(pa)014:3285: rtsi shing me tog nyi zla'i mar me gsal //
NK013(pa)014:3286: chu bo'i byug pa ri bo zhal zas dang //
NK013(pa)014:3287: sgrar grags thams cad rol mo snang grags phyi //
NK013(pa)014:3288: gang shar tshogs drug stong nyid sprul pa'i gshis //
NK013(pa)014:3289: bden med spros bral sgyu ma'i bkod pa nang //
NK013(pa)014:3290: snang ba sku dang sgrar grags gsung rdo rje //
NK013(pa)014:3291: dran rtog mi shig blo 'das gsang ba'i dbyings //
NK013(pa)014:3292: skye med ngang nas gnas lugs 'gag med gdangs //
NK013(pa)014:3293: sna tshogs shar ba de nyid ngang nas mchod //
NK013(pa)014:3294: drug pa la tshogs mchod dang /
NK013(pa)014:3295: tshogs bshags kyis lha tshim par bya ba /
NK013(pa)014:3296: dam tshig gi rdzas kyis rnal 'byor pa tshim par bya ba /
NK013(pa)014:3297: lhag ma'i zas kyis lhag sdud tshim par bya ba /
NK013(pa)014:3298: de dag gi smon lam mo //
NK013(pa)014:3302: gtor ma'i steng gi 'dod yon lha mos tshogs zhing rnams dgyes par bskyed /
NK013(pa)014:3303: bar bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho las /
NK013(pa)014:3304: ljags rdo rje sbu gus bcud drang ste gsol /
NK013(pa)014:3305: 'og sha khrag rus pa khro rgyal sgo ba chos skyongs rnams kyis gsol bas mnyes par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:3307: gzugs ni lag gnyis me long 'dzin //
NK013(pa)014:3308: sogs nas gong gtor mchod skabs ltar khams drug gi lha mo rdzogs pa /
NK013(pa)014:3311: spro na sgegs mo brgyad mchod mthar /
NK013(pa)014:3314: ga na tsakra p+au dza ba kha kha kha h+ai
NK013(pa)014:3315: sogs zhi ba zhe gnyis sngags tshang ma'i mthar btags
NK013(pa)014:3318: yang dag pa'i dgongs pa mngon du gyur pa dpal
NK013(pa)014:3319: kun tu bzang po nas drin chen bla ma dam
NK013(pa)014:3320: pa'i bar du byon pa rtsa brgyud kyi bla ma
NK013(pa)014:3321: / yi dam zhi khro phur gsum la sogs te rgyud sde chen po drug gi lha /
NK013(pa)014:3323: he ru ka yi gnas bcu /
NK013(pa)014:3324: dur khrod chen po brgyad la sogs pa na gnas pa'i dpa' bo mkha' 'gro /
NK013(pa)014:3325: chos skyongs ba'i srung ma nag po gnod sbyin lcam
NK013(pa)014:3326: gsum la sogs pa'i zhal du tshogs kyi mchod pa
NK013(pa)014:3328: rnal 'byor pa bdag cag gi rtsa ba yan lag
NK013(pa)014:3329: chag nyams 'gal 'khrul du gyur pa thams cad mthol
NK013(pa)014:3330: lo bshags so // byang zhing dag par mdzad du gsol /
NK013(pa)014:3331: h'u lta ba 'phang dmas chos nyid don ma rtogs //
NK013(pa)014:3332: sgom pa yun thung yi dam lha ma gsal //
NK013(pa)014:3333: spyod pa rlab chung yi dam lha ma mnyes //
NK013(pa)014:3334: brtse gdung chung bas slob dpon sku ma mnyes //
NK013(pa)014:3335: bkra ba'i lha tshogs rnams la bshags par bgyi //
NK013(pa)014:3336: yi ge brgya pa brjod la chag nyams rang bzhin
NK013(pa)014:3337: med par shes pa rtog pa lta bas bskangs bar
NK013(pa)014:3338: bya'o // gnyis pa zhu ba dang lan gyis tshogs kyi don ngo sprad pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:3339: bdud rtsi'i mchod pas tshogs kyi rnam rtog sel ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:3340: tshogs la rol ba dngos so //
NK013(pa)014:3342: dang po zhu ba'i phyir las rdor gyis dbang phyug la phyag gsum 'tshal te /
NK013(pa)014:3343: dza gad kyi zhal bu thogs la /
NK013(pa)014:3346: gzigs shig mdzes ldan dam pa'i chos /
NK013(pa)014:3348: / 'di la rnam rtog byar mi rung //
NK013(pa)014:3349: khyi dang bram ze gdol pa gsum //
NK013(pa)014:3350: rang bzhin gcig pa nyid du rol //
NK013(pa)014:3352: rdo rje 'dzin sogs dgongs su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3353: bdag gi tshogs kyi mchod pa 'di //
NK013(pa)014:3354: mnyes pa'i don du bstab lags na //
NK013(pa)014:3355: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3357: slob dpon gyis ye shes chen po las byung ba'i /
NK013(pa)014:3358: tshogs chen 'bar bas nyon mongs bsregs /
NK013(pa)014:3361: kun gyis a ho su kha brjod //
NK013(pa)014:3363: a ho ma ha su kha ho /
NK013(pa)014:3365: gsum pa che ba la tshogs kyi rang bzhin ngo sprad pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:3366: de yi rgyu yo byad lam du bya ba'o //
NK013(pa)014:3368: byang chub sems su ngo sprod pa ste /
NK013(pa)014:3369: stong la 'byor ba'i rtags su dam pa 'byung //
NK013(pa)014:3370: bde mchog bde mdzad bde bar mdzad pa ste //
NK013(pa)014:3371: rig pa'i skyes bu rdo rje sems dpa' yin //
NK013(pa)014:3372: de ni byang chub sems su rig pas rig /
NK013(pa)014:3373: byang chub sems ni dngos grub mchog /
NK013(pa)014:3374: de rig yang dag nyid ces bya /
NK013(pa)014:3376: / 'od dang mngon shes lnga la sogs //
NK013(pa)014:3377: ldan yang gnod sbyin mos mi shes //
NK013(pa)014:3384: na bza' dang ni zhal zas rnams //
NK013(pa)014:3385: grub pa'i rdzas su dbang bskur te //
NK013(pa)014:3386: gsol nas dngos grub mchog thob 'gyur //
NK013(pa)014:3389: glu dang tshig gi sgra rnams ni //
NK013(pa)014:3390: gsung gi ngo bor byin rlabs nas //
NK013(pa)014:3391: bsgrags nas dngos grub mchog thob 'gyur //
NK013(pa)014:3394: bro dang gar gyis mchod byas te /
NK013(pa)014:3397: dngos grub mchog kyang thob par 'gyur //
NK013(pa)014:3398: las kyi rdo rjes 'dus pa thams cad la gnas gsum du dri yi thig le 'bul /
NK013(pa)014:3399: gnyis pa bdud rtsi'i mchod pa la /
NK013(pa)014:3403: las kyi rdo rje phyag gsum btsal nas /
NK013(pa)014:3404: h'u mdzad h'u gis thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK013(pa)014:3405: lcang lor bcas pa'i pad+ma b+hany+tsa ru //
NK013(pa)014:3406: tshe 'dzin mchog gi dmar chen dam pas bkang //
NK013(pa)014:3407: pad+ma zil tig dri dang rak+ta kh+aa //
NK013(pa)014:3408: rdo rje las kyi chu dang bdud rtsi lnga //
NK013(pa)014:3409: sha chen mkha' lding shel sgong gzugs tshogs sogs //
NK013(pa)014:3410: sman chen lnga dang cho dang byi la se //
NK013(pa)014:3411: sbyor dang sgrol ba'i bdud rtsi mchog nyid kyis //
NK013(pa)014:3412: h'u mdzad h'u gis thugs dam bskong bar mdzod //
NK013(pa)014:3416: rang byung gdod nas dag pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:3419: zhes dngos grub blangs ba rdzogs par brjod nas /
NK013(pa)014:3420: mtheb srin nyi zla'i skyogs kyis 'bul /
NK013(pa)014:3421: slob dpon gyi mdun du phyi mchod bkod pa las
NK013(pa)014:3422: rdor gyis tshogs la 'grim pa'am btegs te slar yang
NK013(pa)014:3424: gsum pa la phyag tshang bas tshogs 'gyed phul nas /
NK013(pa)014:3426: tshogs kyi mchod pa rgyan du rol //
NK013(pa)014:3432: rang nyid bcom ldan mi bskyod rdo rje yi //
NK013(pa)014:3433: snying gar zab yangs rgyud sde'i dkyil 'khor lha //
NK013(pa)014:3434: spyi bor bla ma mgrin par mkha' 'gro dang //
NK013(pa)014:3435: lte bar chos skyongs rtsa khams dpa' bo dang //
NK013(pa)014:3436: rnal 'byor ma lus rdo rje rtse gsum ljags //
NK013(pa)014:3437: bza' dang btung ba khams drug 'dod yon gyi //
NK013(pa)014:3438: sprul pa'i rig ma rang byung rtsi'i bcud //
NK013(pa)014:3439: rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i ngang du mchod //
NK013(pa)014:3440: zhes bza' btung longs spyod bzhin /
NK013(pa)014:3443: mi gtsang ba'i rtog pa ste mi bya ba gsum /
NK013(pa)014:3445: rdo rje'i spun la tha mal bla dwags kyi ming dang /
NK013(pa)014:3446: dam rdzas la tha mal gyi ming nas mi 'bod pa gsum /
NK013(pa)014:3449: sems chos nyid de mi 'dral ba gsum /
NK013(pa)014:3452: ji ltar bya tshul gsang ba ste gsang ba gsum /
NK013(pa)014:3453: tshogs gral du ma bsdad pa la mi sbyin /
NK013(pa)014:3454: rang gis byin rlab rdzas gzhan la mi sbyin /
NK013(pa)014:3455: lhag ma khyi bya la sogs pa'i don du mi sbyin pa gsum /
NK013(pa)014:3456: tshogs gral du ku co rtsod pa bag med pa rnams spangs ba'i tshul la 'bad do //
NK013(pa)014:3457: gsum pa zos lhag phyogs gcig bsdus pa /
NK013(pa)014:3458: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor shar lho dri yi man+dala dang zhing lpags steng /
NK013(pa)014:3459: gtor stegs la bsog 'jog med par snod du bkod /
NK013(pa)014:3460: de'i steng ngos gtor khrir tshogs mchod kyi lhag mar dpal 'bar btsugs te sman raka sbreng /
NK013(pa)014:3461: las rdor gyis phyag byas te /
NK013(pa)014:3462: lhag ma la byin rlabs zhu 'tshal /
NK013(pa)014:3464: lhag ma'i dam rdzas steng 'dod yon gyi lha mo /
NK013(pa)014:3466: 'og dug gsum sha khrag rus pa'i tshogs su gyur /
NK013(pa)014:3467: lus kyis mdzes pa'i phyag rgya dang /
NK013(pa)014:3469: e +aa ra li hoh dzahmh'u bam hmoh badz+ra sa ma ya phem phem /
NK013(pa)014:3470: thugs kar lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas /
NK013(pa)014:3489: dak+ki ni hri da ya h'u phata /
NK013(pa)014:3490: ces brjod pas rang gi thugs ka nas 'dod pa'i rgyal po byung nas /
NK013(pa)014:3491: lhag mgron thams cad kyi thugs ka nas bzung ste dkyil 'khor gyi mu ran la bkug par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:3492: lhag ma gnyis kyi gtsang lhag dang dme lhag so sor sman raka sbreng /
NK013(pa)014:3493: sarba bud+d+ha badz+ra rat+na pad ma karma d+aak+ki ni e mam ba lin+ta h'u t+r+aam h+r+aihh+aa phata /
NK013(pa)014:3495: dme lhag dang gcig tu bsres /
NK013(pa)014:3496: mkha' 'gro ma sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK013(pa)014:3497: dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK013(pa)014:3498: dam can bcu gnyis dregs pa'i tshogs dang bcas pa /
NK013(pa)014:3503: rdo rje pho nya mo drug cu rtsa bzhi la sogs pa /
NK013(pa)014:3504: dpal chen po'i spyan sngar khas blangs shing dam bcas
NK013(pa)014:3505: pa la sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rin po che
NK013(pa)014:3506: srung bar zhal gyis bzhes pa /
NK013(pa)014:3508: tshogs lhag la dbang ba rnams kyi zhal du kha kha kha hi /
NK013(pa)014:3511: chos sbyong zab mo la bar du gcod pa'i rkyen bzlog cig /
NK013(pa)014:3512: ces brjod la lhag ma skyong ngo //
NK013(pa)014:3514: lhag mgron rnams rang gnas su gshegs par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:3516: zag med bde ba'i dpal las legs sprul pa //
NK013(pa)014:3517: gdan gsum tshang ba'i dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho la //
NK013(pa)014:3518: dgyes ldan lha yi mchod pa'i sprin dpung tshogas //
NK013(pa)014:3519: legs par phul bas tshogs gnyis rdzogs par shog /
NK013(pa)014:3520: rdo rje'i lus kyis sgyu ma'i thab khung du //
NK013(pa)014:3521: rang rig gdod nas grub pa'i rtsa gsum la //
NK013(pa)014:3522: kun rtog bza' ba'i bsreg blugs phul ba'i mthus /
NK013(pa)014:3524: / 'khor 'das dag mnyam chen por rgyas theb shog /
NK013(pa)014:3525: rdo rje theg pa'i gsang ba 'dir 'dus pa //
NK013(pa)014:3526: skal ldan mi yisa 'byor ldan yo byad tshogs //
NK013(pa)014:3527: dam tshig rdzas la legs pa spyod pa'i mthus //
NK013(pa)014:3528: nyams rtog gong nas gong du 'phel bar shog /
NK013(pa)014:3529: sngon tshe dpal chen spyan sngar dam mnos pa //
NK013(pa)014:3530: lhag sdud rnams kyis rnam mang 'dod yon la //
NK013(pa)014:3531: bde bar rol pas bde chen rdo rje sems //
NK013(pa)014:3532: bsgrub la rtag tu bar chad srung bar shog /
NK013(pa)014:3533: dngos kun ye shes sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba yis //
NK013(pa)014:3534: chos nyid rdzogs pa chen por tshim byed pa //
NK013(pa)014:3535: lhan skyes gnyug ma'i tshogs kyi 'khor lo ni //
NK013(pa)014:3536: snying dbus pad+mara rtag tu sim gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:3537: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK013(pa)014:3538: bsgom bzlas mchod bstod tshogs 'khor phul ba yis //
NK013(pa)014:3539: dge ba 'di yis bdag gzhan sems can rnams //
NK013(pa)014:3540: skyon bral yon tan ma lus rab rdzogs te //
NK013(pa)014:3541: mthar thug sangs rgyas sku lnga thob par shog /
NK013(pa)014:3542: gnyis pa lhag chen gyis cho ga ni /
NK013(pa)014:3543: srung ma'i gtor chog ste tshogs mchod med kyang bsnyen pa'i mjug tu bya bar gsungs pas /
NK013(pa)014:3544: mdun stegs la thod snod du gtor ma snying gi dbyibs can so drug gam /
NK013(pa)014:3545: lnga dam rdzas kyis brgyan pa bkod /
NK013(pa)014:3546: gtor gzhong gi mdun du phyi mchod bshams /
NK013(pa)014:3548: gtor ma'i steng 'dod yon gyi lha mo sogs tshogs lhag byin rlabs ltar dang /
NK013(pa)014:3549: bdag gi thugs ka nas khro bo 'dod pa'i rgyal
NK013(pa)014:3550: po dmar po lcags kyu dang zhags pa thogs pa
NK013(pa)014:3551: spros / mkha' 'gro ma so gnyis dang /
NK013(pa)014:3552: dpa' bo bzhi rang dbang med par spyan drangs te /
NK013(pa)014:3553: bcom ldan 'das rigs lnga'i 'khor gyi phyir gzhal med
NK013(pa)014:3554: khang gi phyi rol ta la'i tshal du phyogs rer
NK013(pa)014:3555: brgyad brgyad dang / zur bzhir bzhi gnas pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:3557: sogs gong ltar dang spyug glus bskul /
NK013(pa)014:3558: de thams cad kyang zhing tshal ba'i gdan la gar gyis 'gying ba /
NK013(pa)014:3559: gcer bu lag na gri gug dang /
NK013(pa)014:3561: rus pa'i rgyan dang g.yer kha'i phreng bas klub pa /
NK013(pa)014:3567: slob dpon gyis gtor ma la kha phru btab la /
NK013(pa)014:3568: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i ljags kyi rtse mo las /
NK013(pa)014:3570: mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis zhal du thim /
NK013(pa)014:3571: de ni kha chu'i dgongs pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:3572: gtor ma bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho /
NK013(pa)014:3574: de ni bdud rtsi'i dgongs pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:3575: dug gsum sha khrag rus par gyur yang mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis gsol bar gyur /
NK013(pa)014:3576: de ni dug gsum gyi dgongs pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:3578: h'u badz+ra d+h+aa ka d+aak+ki ni /
NK013(pa)014:3579: pra tits+tsha e mam ba lim ta h'u phata kha hi /
NK013(pa)014:3580: sarba bud+d+ha d+h+aa ka d+aak+ki ni /
NK013(pa)014:3581: pra tits+tsha i mam ba lim ta +amo phata kha hi /
NK013(pa)014:3583: t+r+aam sarba rat+na d+h+aa ka d+h+aa ki ni /
NK013(pa)014:3584: pra tits+tsha i mam ba lim ta t+r+aam phata kha hi /
NK013(pa)014:3586: h+r+aihsarba pad+ma d+aa ka d+aak+ki ni /
NK013(pa)014:3587: pra tits+tsha i mam ba lim ta /
NK013(pa)014:3590: h+aahsarba karma d+aa ka d+aak+ki ni /
NK013(pa)014:3591: pra tits+tsha i mam ba lim ta h+aa phata kha hi /
NK013(pa)014:3594: / 'di rnams so so'i grangs tshad dam gsum re bazla'o //
NK013(pa)014:3595: de nas mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis rna ba cag ger nyan par gyur pa la /
NK013(pa)014:3596: rdo rje dril bu'i 'gyur ba bcas /
NK013(pa)014:3598: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' la //
NK013(pa)014:3599: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK013(pa)014:3600: mngon par dga' ba'i 'jig rten nas //
NK013(pa)014:3601: rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ma rnams //
NK013(pa)014:3602: yi dwags stan la yang dag bzhugs //
NK013(pa)014:3604: skal dang rang gi lag char ldan //
NK013(pa)014:3605: gdug pa'i sems kyis bsdig byed cing //
NK013(pa)014:3606: sha khrag dang ni rgyu ma dang //
NK013(pa)014:3607: rkang dang tshil bu za spyod rnams //
NK013(pa)014:3608: za bar byed cing 'dren par byed //
NK013(pa)014:3609: gsod par byed cing phrog par byed //
NK013(pa)014:3610: kun kyang rang gi dam tshig ldan //
NK013(pa)014:3611: shar gyi phyogs nas gshegs su gsol /
NK013(pa)014:3613: / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK013(pa)014:3615: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar sgrubs //
NK013(pa)014:3616: las bcol phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3617: dpal dang ldan pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK013(pa)014:3618: rdo rje nam mkhar gzi byed che dang 'bar byed me /
NK013(pa)014:3620: / 'joms byed ma dang bong bu'i mgo //
NK013(pa)014:3621: kun kyang rang gi dam tshig ldan //
NK013(pa)014:3622: lho yi phyogs 'dir gshegs bka' yi bdag gi las bcol bde ba can gyi 'jig rten nas //
NK013(pa)014:3623: rdo rje nam chags chen ma dang chags bral ma /
NK013(pa)014:3626: kun kyang rang gi lag char ldan //
NK013(pa)014:3627: nub kyi 'di gshegs bka' yi bdag gi las bcol rnam par dag pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK013(pa)014:3628: rdo rje nam sna tshogs lus dang srung ba mo //
NK013(pa)014:3629: gnod sbyin ma dang yang dag 'phrog /
NK013(pa)014:3630: kun kyang byang gi phyogs 'dir gshegs bka' yi bdag gi sha chen spungs pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK013(pa)014:3631: bya rog gdong ni mig 'phrul can /
NK013(pa)014:3634: shar lho'i lag par gri dang khrag gzhung thogs //
NK013(pa)014:3635: mchog tu sha dang khrag la dgyes //
NK013(pa)014:3636: kun kyang shar lho mtshams 'dir gshegs bka' yi bdag
NK013(pa)014:3637: gi las bcol keng rus spungs pa'i 'jig rten nas
NK013(pa)014:3638: // bzhad dang 'ug pa'i gdong ring ma //
NK013(pa)014:3639: khros pa khyi dang phag gi gdong //
NK013(pa)014:3640: lho nub nam lto 'phyang po la bum pa 'dzin //
NK013(pa)014:3641: kun kyang lho nub mtshams 'dir gshegs bka' yi bdag gi las bcol rak+ta khrag gi rba klong nas //
NK013(pa)014:3643: khros pa ra dang byi la'i gdong //
NK013(pa)014:3644: nub byang nam mkhar 'gro rgyu ma'i mgo nas za bar byed //
NK013(pa)014:3645: kun kyang nub byang mtshams 'dir gshegs bka' yi bdag
NK013(pa)014:3646: gi las bcol thal chen spungs pa'i 'jig rten nas
NK013(pa)014:3647: // keng rus dkar po 'dzin pa ste //
NK013(pa)014:3648: khros pas rus pa'i phreng ba klub //
NK013(pa)014:3649: byang shar nam phan tshun 'thab cing rtsod par byed /
NK013(pa)014:3651: / 'jigs byed drag po'i mche ba can //
NK013(pa)014:3652: lce spyang gi ni 'khor gyis bskor //
NK013(pa)014:3653: kun kyang 'dir gshegs bka' yi bdag gi las bcol dpal ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yi //
NK013(pa)014:3654: dkyil 'khor de yi gra bzhi nas /
NK013(pa)014:3657: shar gyi phyogs nas byung ba ni //
NK013(pa)014:3658: rdo rje mkha' 'gro chen mo ste //
NK013(pa)014:3659: srin mo bum sna gshegs su gsol /
NK013(pa)014:3662: kun kyang 'dir gshegs bka' yi bdag gi las bcol
NK013(pa)014:3663: lho yi phyogs rin chen mkha' 'gro rdo rje dus
NK013(pa)014:3664: mtshan 'jigs byed 'bum phrag lnga dang bcas //
NK013(pa)014:3665: kun kyang 'dir gshegs bka' yi bdag gi las bcol
NK013(pa)014:3666: nub kyi phyogs nas pad+ma mkha' 'gro rdo rje dus
NK013(pa)014:3670: kun kyang 'dir gshegs bka' yi bdag gi las bcol byang gi phyogs rdo rje lang+ka mgrin bcu yang //
NK013(pa)014:3671: gnod sbyin bye ba 'bum dang bcas //
NK013(pa)014:3672: kun kyang 'dir gshegs bka' yi bdag gi las bcol mkha' 'gro pho mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK013(pa)014:3673: sngon tshe bcom ldan rigs lnga yis //
NK013(pa)014:3674: pho rnams btul te gdan du bting //
NK013(pa)014:3675: mo rnams btul te mdza' mor byas //
NK013(pa)014:3676: so so'i dam tshig bgos pa bzhin //
NK013(pa)014:3677: bdag kyang rgyal ba'i bstan srung na //
NK013(pa)014:3678: las bcol phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3679: bar du gcod pa'i dgra bgegs rnams //
NK013(pa)014:3680: myur du sgrol la med par mdzad //
NK013(pa)014:3681: bdud 'dul mthu dang skal ldan tshe //
NK013(pa)014:3682: mdzod ldan nor dang 'khor rnams kyis //
NK013(pa)014:3683: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3685: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha hi /
NK013(pa)014:3687: mchod pa'i tshogs gtor gzhong du gshegs la /
NK013(pa)014:3694: zhes yi ge brgya pa bzla bzhin rol mo'i sgra bcas gtor ma gshegs /
NK013(pa)014:3697: dam tshig 'khor lo'i gnas su gshegs //
NK013(pa)014:3701: dang po gtor ma nam mkha' mthong sar khyer sman rag bran /
NK013(pa)014:3703: rgya gar yul gyi tshu rol du //
NK013(pa)014:3704: bal po'i yul gyi pha rol na //
NK013(pa)014:3705: a su ra yi brag phug tu //
NK013(pa)014:3706: pad+ma dbang gis dam stsal ba //
NK013(pa)014:3707: mi sdug nag mo'i bu mo bdud mo bzhi //
NK013(pa)014:3708: dmar mo khro gnyer bu mo gnod sbyin bzhi //
NK013(pa)014:3709: dkar sham bzhin bzang bu mo sman btsun bzhi /
NK013(pa)014:3711: / 'dir gshegs dam dgongs mchod sbyin bsnam du gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3717: ma ma sring 'gro ma h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK013(pa)014:3722: ya hi gats+tsha sa rang gnas su gshegs /
NK013(pa)014:3724: gtor ma rtsa ba gcig pa rtse mo gsum pa la /
NK013(pa)014:3726: gtor ma t+r+aam las rin chen mchod sdong ni /
NK013(pa)014:3727: rtse gsum 'bru gsum rtsa ba t+r+aam mtshan pa //
NK013(pa)014:3728: bde bar gshegs pa dam can srung ma dang /
NK013(pa)014:3730: / 'gro drug sems can kun la mchod sbyin 'bul //
NK013(pa)014:3731: lha tshogs thams cad zhal phyir gzigs par bsgoms la rol mo dang /
NK013(pa)014:3733: bye brag srung 'khor gyi skabs kyi dz+wa li badz+ra'i sngags brjod /
NK013(pa)014:3734: rang gi gnas lnga nas mtshon cha sna lnga spros //
NK013(pa)014:3735: rdo rje'i rwa gur la phog /
NK013(pa)014:3736: de las mtshon cha spros bdud bgegs thams cad bskrad /
NK013(pa)014:3737: tshur 'dus srung ba'i gur khang brtan par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:3738: badz+ra b+h+r+aum rak+sha rak+shah rten snying dang /
NK013(pa)014:3739: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sgrub pa la //
NK013(pa)014:3740: sogs sman lam byas te lha tshogs zhal nang du gzigs par bsam /
NK013(pa)014:3742: gtong rag gi mchod bshags dang /
NK013(pa)014:3746: rnam bdun 'dod yon sman rag gtor ma sngags tsam gyis mchod de /
NK013(pa)014:3747: sha dang rus pa khrag kyang med //
NK013(pa)014:3748: nam mkha' la ni 'ja' tshon ltar //
NK013(pa)014:3749: khyod kyi sku ni ston par mdzad //
NK013(pa)014:3750: khong stong khyod kyi sku la bstod //
NK013(pa)014:3751: khyod ni glang po'i rna ba can //
NK013(pa)014:3752: khyod ni seng ge'i stang stabs can //
NK013(pa)014:3753: khyod ni pha ltar skyobs pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:3754: khyod ni ma ltar byams pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:3755: khyod ni sa ltar 'degs pa ste //
NK013(pa)014:3756: khyod ni chu ltar sdud pa'o //
NK013(pa)014:3757: khyod ni gzugs sdug yid kyis brgyan //
NK013(pa)014:3758: khyod ni rlung ltar gtor ba'o //
NK013(pa)014:3759: khyod ni sprin ltar lding ba'o //
NK013(pa)014:3761: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi bdag /
NK013(pa)014:3762: ye shes rgyu mtsho rab zab thugs //
NK013(pa)014:3764: rdo rje yid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK013(pa)014:3765: rang nyid gtso bo phyag gnyis pa'i rnam pas shar sgor 'khod par gyur //
NK013(pa)014:3769: bdag ni rang rig ye shes blo dang mi ldan pas /
NK013(pa)014:3770: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK013(pa)014:3771: bka' rgyud bla ma'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK013(pa)014:3772: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK013(pa)014:3773: bdag ni bag med rdo rje sems sogs thugs thugs
NK013(pa)014:3774: rje che mnga' bdag ni bag med ma mo mkha'
NK013(pa)014:3775: 'gro'i thugs rje yig brgya lan gsum dang dbyangs gsal
NK013(pa)014:3777: gnyis pa la dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing lha ru sdang /
NK013(pa)014:3778: go bgo lus bsrung smon bkra shis /
NK013(pa)014:3782: zhes brjod pas rang gi snying ga'i 'od kyis phog
NK013(pa)014:3783: pas khams gsum brtan g.yo rnam par dag pa 'od
NK013(pa)014:3784: du zhu ba srung 'khor la thim /
NK013(pa)014:3787: dngos po rnams yum la thim /
NK013(pa)014:3793: thub drug bya byed la thim /
NK013(pa)014:3794: de thams cad kyang nyi ma dang zer bzhin yab rnams rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK013(pa)014:3795: yum rnams dbyings phyug ma la thim /
NK013(pa)014:3800: de gyen rdzogs na da'i bar du thim nas /
NK013(pa)014:3801: spros bral rnam par dag pa rang byung gi ye shes nam mkha' lta bu mngon sum du gyur /
NK013(pa)014:3802: stong nyid la ci gnas su mnyam par 'jog /
NK013(pa)014:3804: de'i ngang las sdang ba ni /
NK013(pa)014:3806: rang nyid rdo rje sems dpa' zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i sku rgyur /
NK013(pa)014:3810: spyi bo dang lus kyi gnas lnga lngar rigs lnga dang rdo rje lngas mtshan par gyur /
NK013(pa)014:3811: rdo rje'i phyag rgya gtug ste /
NK013(pa)014:3812: h'u +amo s+w+aa +aamhh+aah +amo +aam h'u s+w+aa h+aah sems dpa' sum brtsegs gsal /
NK013(pa)014:3813: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha ham /
NK013(pa)014:3814: lus rdo rje'i go khrab kyis zhu lugs su g.yogs /
NK013(pa)014:3815: h'u h'u zhes pa'ang rkang pa'i mthe bong nas rdo rje'i rgyun thag zung re byung /
NK013(pa)014:3818: dpyi mig gnas mdun rgyab tu /
NK013(pa)014:3823: dpral ba'i skra mtshams drug tu rdo rje rgya gram gyi mdud pa re bcings bar gyur /
NK013(pa)014:3825: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK013(pa)014:3826: sku gsung thugs kyis kun la khyab //
NK013(pa)014:3827: mdzub mo g.yas na h'u nag po //
NK013(pa)014:3828: g.yon a dmar po gnyis khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin nag po rdo rje dang /
NK013(pa)014:3829: phag rgod kyi mche ba 'dzin pa /
NK013(pa)014:3830: bdud rtsi thab sbyor dmar po ral gri dang zhags
NK013(pa)014:3831: pa thogs pas mdo drug tu zhabs bsnol te srung
NK013(pa)014:3832: bar gyur / h'u a zhes gnas drug tu bsgom
NK013(pa)014:3833: +aar+ya lam+bo d+ha ra a b+hi shany+tsa h+r+aihh+r+aih rgyun thag
NK013(pa)014:3834: rtse smin mtshams na yod pa las dar mthing dmar
NK013(pa)014:3836: badz+ra rat+na pad+ma m+aa l+ye a b+hi shany+tsa t+r+aam t+r+aam /
NK013(pa)014:3837: zhes rin po che dang me tog gi phreng ba bcings /
NK013(pa)014:3838: yi ge brgya pa bzla bas gsal zhing brtan par bya'o //
NK013(pa)014:3840: sangs rgyas 'byung dang skal mnyam zhing //
NK013(pa)014:3841: theg pa dman par yang mi skye //
NK013(pa)014:3842: ngan song dag tu mi ltung bar //
NK013(pa)014:3843: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK013(pa)014:3844: lus byad bzang zhing yan lag rdzogs //
NK013(pa)014:3845: snying rje che zhing shes rab ldan //
NK013(pa)014:3846: bdag dang gzhan don rdzogs spyod shog /
NK013(pa)014:3847: bla med byang chub thor tshugs can //
NK013(pa)014:3848: shin tu brtan pa'i ri bor gnas //
NK013(pa)014:3849: mu stegs rlung gis tshugs mi 'gyur //
NK013(pa)014:3850: theg mchog rdo rje de lta bu //
NK013(pa)014:3852: rdo rje nor bu rin po che //
NK013(pa)014:3853: byi dor byas shing shin tu gsal //
NK013(pa)014:3854: bskal pa grangs med gnas gyur kyang //
NK013(pa)014:3855: sku ni shin tu gzhon pa'i tshul //
NK013(pa)014:3856: skye shi med pa'i rdo rje yis //
NK013(pa)014:3857: thams cad 'byung ba'i gter yin te //
NK013(pa)014:3858: yon tan phun sum tshogs dang ldan //
NK013(pa)014:3859: bla med byang chub grub gyur nas //
NK013(pa)014:3860: ye shes rdo rje grub par shog /
NK013(pa)014:3861: tshogs chen gnyis kyang rdzogs rgyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:3862: thams cad kun gyis ston pa po //
NK013(pa)014:3863: thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang brnyes //
NK013(pa)014:3864: sangs rgyas nyid la dbang byed shog /
NK013(pa)014:3865: de rtogs kun kyang rdo rje'i rigs //
NK013(pa)014:3866: sku gsung thugs su 'grub par shog /
NK013(pa)014:3867: sems can 'dam gyis mi gos shing //
NK013(pa)014:3868: bla na med pa'i byang chub lam //
NK013(pa)014:3869: sna tshogs sdug bsngal zhi mdzad cing //
NK013(pa)014:3870: sems can skom pa ngom mdzad shog /
NK013(pa)014:3871: thugs dam nyams pa kun bskang ste //
NK013(pa)014:3872: ye shes bla ma'i sa gnon nas //
NK013(pa)014:3873: sku gsung thugs ni mi zad pa //
NK013(pa)014:3874: rgyan gyi 'khor lo thob par shog /
NK013(pa)014:3875: 'di las bdag gi dge ba gang thob pa /
NK013(pa)014:3877: / 'gro ba blo zhan rnams kyis chos kun ni //
NK013(pa)014:3878: stong nyid sgyu ma lta bur rab rtogs nas //
NK013(pa)014:3879: ye shes gnyis med sku gsum thob par shog /
NK013(pa)014:3880: de lta'i dge rtsas lam gnas rnal 'byor kun //
NK013(pa)014:3881: bskyed rims mthar phyin yang dag zhen grol nas //
NK013(pa)014:3882: kun gyi mthar lam mngon gyur don rdzogs te //
NK013(pa)014:3883: mtha' yas 'gro don tshul bzhin byed par shog /
NK013(pa)014:3885: zhal nas gsungs pa'i bkra shis dang /
NK013(pa)014:3886: bkra shis gang zhig ka dag ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK013(pa)014:3887: lhun grub 'od gsal rtag pa dam pa'i rol mo can //
NK013(pa)014:3888: thugs rje kun khyab kun bzang brgyud gsum bla ma yis //
NK013(pa)014:3889: bden pa des kyang dag mnyam la gnas bkra shis shog /
NK013(pa)014:3890: bkra shis gang zhig shin tu zhi ba'i chos dbyings las //
NK013(pa)014:3891: mi bskyod rdo rje kha sbyor rgyal po mdzes pa'i sku //
NK013(pa)014:3892: zung 'jug ye shes sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i 'khor lo'i bdag /
NK013(pa)014:3893: bden pa bye brag zer klong in+t+ra n+ai la'i lhun po la //
NK013(pa)014:3894: mkha' dbyings dbang po'i gzhu yis 'khyud 'dra zhal gsum mnga' /
NK013(pa)014:3896: / drug ldan phyag na sna tshogs rang rtags legs 'dzin pa //
NK013(pa)014:3897: bden pa me long la sogs ye shes bzhi las grub pa'i sku //
NK013(pa)014:3898: rnam snang la sogs rtsibs bzhi'i 'khor lo la gnas pa //
NK013(pa)014:3899: spyan ma la sogs mnyam sbyor longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK013(pa)014:3900: bden pa mig sogs dbang shes yul bcas dag pa rgyal ba'i sras //
NK013(pa)014:3901: sa snying la sogs glo 'bur gru chad la gnas pa //
NK013(pa)014:3902: sgeg mo la sogs bcu drug mnyam sbyor mngon byang sku //
NK013(pa)014:3903: bden pa phung sogs 'byung ba'i 'khor 'das bden gnyis rnam dag pa //
NK013(pa)014:3904: de bzhin gshegs sogs dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i spro ba'i gzhi //
NK013(pa)014:3905: rigs sogs kun bdag khyams la bya byed chos kyi sku //
NK013(pa)014:3906: bden pa ser sna la sogs rtog pa drug dag thub pa ni //
NK013(pa)014:3907: lha la sogs pa'i 'gro ba drug po 'dren mdzad cing //
NK013(pa)014:3908: sbyin sogs phar phyin drug bdag 'khyams gnas sprul pa'i sku //
NK013(pa)014:3909: bden pa byams pa la sogs tshad med bzhi dngos reg sogs dag /
NK013(pa)014:3910: gshin rje la sogs mthar byed yab yum rdo rje'i sku //
NK013(pa)014:3911: phung po la sogs bdud bzhi'i ro la dpa' zhing brjid //
NK013(pa)014:3912: bden pa bkra shis gang zhig 'og min stug po bkod pa'i zhing //
NK013(pa)014:3913: thar pa chen po'i gzhal med 'od lnga'i sprin phung 'phro //
NK013(pa)014:3914: zla ba rlung bskyod gser dang dril bu'i d+r+wa bas brgyan //
NK013(pa)014:3915: bden pa byang phyogs so bdun bkod pa ngo mtshar sgyu ma'i phul //
NK013(pa)014:3916: yid phrog t+aa la dpag bsam shing tshal rta babs brgyan //
NK013(pa)014:3917: pad+ma ri dwags gdugs dang chos 'khor rgyal mtshan 'phyang //
NK013(pa)014:3918: bden pa sna tshogs rdo rje'i srung ba'i skur khang bdud las rgyal //
NK013(pa)014:3919: log 'dren bgegs 'joms sna lnga 'bar ba'i me ri 'khyil //
NK013(pa)014:3920: skyon bral pad+ma nam mkha'i mtha' mnyam pho brang gi
NK013(pa)014:3921: bden pa des kyang dag mnyam la gnas bkra shis
NK013(pa)014:3922: shog / bkra shis gang zhig rdo rje 'chang gis gsungs pa'i rgyud //
NK013(pa)014:3923: bye ba dung phyur dpag med kun gyi rtse mo mchog /
NK013(pa)014:3924: gsang ba snying po phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba'i thugs kyi mdzod //
NK013(pa)014:3925: bden pa des kyang dag mnyam la gnas bkra shis shog /
NK013(pa)014:3926: ces shis par brjod pas dge legs su bya'o //
NK013(pa)014:3927: gnyis pa las kyi rjes la /
NK013(pa)014:3928: spyod lam rgyun gyi rnal 'byor ston te /
NK013(pa)014:3929: tha mal pa'i mtshan mar 'dzin pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:3931: gnas khang dag pa'i zhing dang gzhal med khang /
NK013(pa)014:3932: grogs su dang 'grogs kyang yi dam gyi lha dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i nga rgyal gyis /
NK013(pa)014:3933: byed spyod thams cad rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i ye shes dang /
NK013(pa)014:3935: bgo brgyan sogs yo byad kyi rnal 'byor zab mos
NK013(pa)014:3936: dge sdig btang snyoms tha mal ba ma yin par
NK013(pa)014:3937: rdo rje theg pa'i thabs mkhas kyis zag med tshogs
NK013(pa)014:3938: gnyis rdzogs pa'i dge bar bsgyur ba la mkhas par
NK013(pa)014:3939: bya'o // de ltar rjes la thob pa'i dus kun
NK013(pa)014:3940: du tha mal du mig yeng ba gal che zhing
NK013(pa)014:3941: bya'o // / rnal 'byor gyis skyon sems can 'di
NK013(pa)014:3942: dag thams cad bdag gis sangs rgyas su bya'o snyam
NK013(pa)014:3943: pa'i sems bskyed rin po che'i rtsi dang ma bral
NK013(pa)014:3944: bya'o // / ba dgos te / me long lta bu'i sgrub thabs las /
NK013(pa)014:3945: yang na rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK013(pa)014:3946: byin rlabs kyis ni rnam par sbyangs //
NK013(pa)014:3947: sems can thams cad mthong ba na //
NK013(pa)014:3948: snying rje byams pa'i sems bskyed de //
NK013(pa)014:3949: sangs rgyas nyid du bya'o zhes //
NK013(pa)014:3950: smon pa'i sems ni khyad par can //
NK013(pa)014:3951: blo can gyis ni rtag tu bya //
NK013(pa)014:3952: de ltar dus bzhi'i nyin mtshan du //
NK013(pa)014:3953: rnal 'byor tshul la gnas pa yin //
NK013(pa)014:3954: zhes gsungs pa dang gzhan yang gnyid 'od gsal du
NK013(pa)014:3955: sba ba sogs chu bo rgyun gyi rnal 'byor 'khor
NK013(pa)014:3956: yug tu byas te gnyis 'dzin gyi 'ching ba grol
NK013(pa)014:3957: nas ting nge 'dzin la blo brtan pa ni dngos
NK013(pa)014:3958: grub kyi rgyu'o // de skad du'ang rgyud las /
NK013(pa)014:3959: gang gis glang chen myos 'dra'i sems //
NK013(pa)014:3960: mnyam par bzhag pas btul nas ni //
NK013(pa)014:3961: sngags dang phyag rgya rab brtan na //
NK013(pa)014:3962: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por 'gyur //
NK013(pa)014:3964: gnyis pa grub pa 'bras bu la gnas skabs dang /
NK013(pa)014:3966: dang po la'ang zhar las byung ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:3968: dang po ji skad bshad pa'i bskyed rim byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:3970: rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor gsum dang ldan pas lcags la
NK013(pa)014:3971: gser 'gyur gyi rtsi bzhin tha mal phyi snang zhen
NK013(pa)014:3972: sbyong ste / rgyas thebs par byas nas /
NK013(pa)014:3973: rdo rje gsum gyi rnal 'byor goms pas /
NK013(pa)014:3974: ro lang gser du bsgyur ba dang /
NK013(pa)014:3975: bum pa bzang po'i gter sogs dngos grub brgyad dang /
NK013(pa)014:3978: gdon bgegs gtor ma sogs dang /
NK013(pa)014:3979: chu mer bsgyur ba sogs rdzu 'phrul rab 'byams la
NK013(pa)014:3980: mnga' dbang 'byor na zhi rgyas dbang drug gi las
NK013(pa)014:3981: phran tshegs smos ci dgos te 'jig rten pa'i 'og
NK013(pa)014:3982: min gyi bar gyi mthun pa'i las dang dngos grub
NK013(pa)014:3983: thams cad 'grub pa'i thabs lta ba /
NK013(pa)014:3984: rdzogs rim gyis rgyas thebs pa'i bskyed rim gyi rnal 'byor goms pa mngon gyur pa gtso che zhing /
NK013(pa)014:3986: phra mo'i rnal 'byor gyi mthar son pas yid ting nge 'dzin brtan pa dang /
NK013(pa)014:3987: de'i rgyu rdzogs pa zhig dgos so //
NK013(pa)014:3989: de ltar bskyed rim gyis gzhi bzung ste /
NK013(pa)014:3990: gang la gnad du bsnun pa rdo rje'i lus dang /
NK013(pa)014:3991: de la ji ltar bsnun pa'i tshul mkhas pas mtshan bcas kyi rdzogs rim /
NK013(pa)014:3992: rtsa gsum 'khor lo drug ldan gyi lus la /
NK013(pa)014:3993: steng sgo dang 'og sgo 'ju 'dul rang lus dang /
NK013(pa)014:3994: phyag rgya gang yang rung ba la brten pa'i yas 'bab dang /
NK013(pa)014:3995: mas brtan gyi dga' bzhi'i ye shes ngos bzung zhing /
NK013(pa)014:3996: de la brten nas bde chen 'dren pa'i goms pa mthar son pas /
NK013(pa)014:3997: ril po dang rjes gzhig gis mtshan ma med pa'i
NK013(pa)014:3998: rdzogs rim la 'jug pa ni rlung dbu ma skur
NK013(pa)014:3999: zhugs pa'i rtags kyis drangs pa'i 'od gsal 'char ba
NK013(pa)014:4000: de ting stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK013(pa)014:4001: de yi ngang las sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lha sku
NK013(pa)014:4002: grib ma lta bur ldang ba kun snang snying rje
NK013(pa)014:4004: de yang bde stong zung 'jug gi rnam rol chu
NK013(pa)014:4005: la gzugs brnyan phos pa lta bu'i gsang chen rigs
NK013(pa)014:4006: gcig phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK013(pa)014:4007: de'ang gang snang thams cad zhu bade'am lhan skyes kyi
NK013(pa)014:4008: lha skur rtsal sbyong ba phyag rgya spros bcas te
NK013(pa)014:4009: skye shi bar do gsum dang chos mthun de sbyong
NK013(pa)014:4010: byed / 'bras dus sku gsum dang mthun pa'i rnam pa lam byed yin cing /
NK013(pa)014:4011: de ltar rdzogs rim la goms pa'i gang zag gis //
NK013(pa)014:4012: rtogs pa de brtan pa'i slad du brtul zhugs kyi
NK013(pa)014:4013: spyod pa tshom bu tshogs sgrub la 'jug par 'gyur
NK013(pa)014:4014: zhing / de'i 'bras bu mthong lam la sbyor bas /
NK013(pa)014:4015: dbang po rno na 'od gsal las zung 'jug gi
NK013(pa)014:4016: lha skur dngos la ldang nus pa tshe dbang dang
NK013(pa)014:4017: / mi nus kyang don gyi 'od gsal grub pa rnam smin rig 'dzin gang rung gi mthar /
NK013(pa)014:4018: ye shes sgyu ma'i sku can sgom lam phyag chen rig 'dzin dang /
NK013(pa)014:4019: de nas kha sbyor yan lag bdun ldan gyi go
NK013(pa)014:4020: 'phang 'grub ma rag pa'i mthar lam lhun grub rig
NK013(pa)014:4022: brtson pa dang ldan na bar ma chad par nyi
NK013(pa)014:4023: zla'i bgrod pa las kyang myur bar 'gro ba yin
NK013(pa)014:4025: gang zhig 'di la mos gyur pa //
NK013(pa)014:4026: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis //
NK013(pa)014:4027: phyogs dus kun nas thams cad du //
NK013(pa)014:4028: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yi //
NK013(pa)014:4029: nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur //
NK013(pa)014:4031: bde gshegs nyid kyi yul bzhugs pa /
NK013(pa)014:4033: / 'jigs med kun tu bzang por sbyar //
NK013(pa)014:4036: de ltar rdo rje theg pa sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i
NK013(pa)014:4037: sgor zhugs nas dad brtson dam tshig ma nyams pa'i
NK013(pa)014:4038: gang zag gis lam tshul bzhin bsgom na /
NK013(pa)014:4039: sngags bla med kyi 'phags pa'i 'bras bu mthong ba'i chos la mngon du 'gyur nus zhing /
NK013(pa)014:4040: de nus na sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang la dka' ba med par myur du bgrod pa yin te /
NK013(pa)014:4041: sbyang gzhi rgyu rgyud la brten pa'i sbyang bya glo
NK013(pa)014:4042: bur gyi dri ma dag pa rab kyi mthar thug
NK013(pa)014:4043: pa ni phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i longs spyod chen po'i
NK013(pa)014:4044: dbyings / rang snang rnam dag stug po bkod pa
NK013(pa)014:4045: nang g.yo ba med par bzhugs pa'i chos sku'i rang
NK013(pa)014:4046: dbyings / mdangs / dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i sprin chen po bskod de /
NK013(pa)014:4047: sprul sku nam mkha' dang mnyam par spro bas 'khor
NK013(pa)014:4048: ba ma stong gi bar la gdul bya'i don lhun
NK013(pa)014:4050: ngo bo la 'gyur ba med pa rdo rje'i skur bzhugs pa ni /
NK013(pa)014:4051: rgyud kyi rgyal po la brtson pas thob pa'i 'bras bu lags na /
NK013(pa)014:4052: skal ba dang ldan pa dag gis g.yar dam mi lhod par bya'o //
NK013(pa)014:4053: de ltar dpal ldan sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i sgrub thabs 'adi'ang /
NK013(pa)014:4054: rtsa ba dang bshad pa'i rgyud sde rnams dang /
NK013(pa)014:4055: rgya bod kyi man ngag tshad ma'i 'grel ba rnams dang /
NK013(pa)014:4056: d+r+wa chen d+r+wa chung me long lta bu la sogs pa'i sgrub thabs rnams dang /
NK013(pa)014:4057: rig 'dzin dam pa gzhan gyi'ang yig cha rnams dang /
NK013(pa)014:4058: khyad par slob dpon pad+ma las snyan du brgyud pa'i man ngag khyad par du 'phags pa'i bdag po /
NK013(pa)014:4059: lam 'di las zung 'jug la gshegs pa mang po'i
NK013(pa)014:4060: 'byung gnas chos rje kahthoga pa'i snyan brgyud dri ma
NK013(pa)014:4061: med pa rnams la yang yang dpyad de legs par
NK013(pa)014:4063: sangs rgyas gsang dang pad+ma bi ma la'i /
NK013(pa)014:4064: zhal lung som nyi'i gnas min brgyud pa ni /
NK013(pa)014:4065: rmad byung rin chen gser phreng las 'ongs pa //
NK013(pa)014:4066: gsang chen 'di 'dra 'jig rten gsum na dkon //
NK013(pa)014:4067: mkhas 'dod dug chus ma spags lhag bsam gyis //
NK013(pa)014:4068: shin tu gsang ba rmad byung snying po'i rgyud //
NK013(pa)014:4069: dpang por bkod nas grub thob 'bum phrag lam //
NK013(pa)014:4070: nyams med bdud rtsi'i zil mngar bdag gis 'thor //
NK013(pa)014:4071: zab yang rgyud sde'i rgya mtsho gting mtha' bral //
NK013(pa)014:4072: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i gsang ba'i yul yin na //
NK013(pa)014:4073: blo chung bdag 'dras dpyad pa'i nyes mchis na //
NK013(pa)014:4074: bla ma rnams dang gsang ba'i bdag la 'chags //
NK013(pa)014:4075: bsod nams gzi brjid rab 'bar 'gro ba mtha' yas kyis //
NK013(pa)014:4076: snying gi mun sel bde chen lhan gcig skyes pa ni //
NK013(pa)014:4077: nyi ma ltar gsal rdo rje sems dpa'i sgyu 'phrul bde //
NK013(pa)014:4078: mkha' mtha' zad pa de srid rtag tu snang gyur cig /
NK013(pa)014:4079: ces pa'ang ring mo nas bya bar 'dod pa la /
NK013(pa)014:4080: nye char don gnyer can rnams kyis bskul ba bzhin /
NK013(pa)014:4081: bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka' drin gyis 'tsho
NK013(pa)014:4082: ba'i gsang ba sgyu 'phrul pa sh+aakya'i dge slong rdo
NK013(pa)014:4083: rje 'dzin pa chos kyi rgya mtshos gangs can gyi
NK013(pa)014:4084: khrod na mngon par mtho ba'i sgrub gnas chen po
NK013(pa)014:4085: shar kahthoga rdo rje'i gdan du /
NK013(pa)014:4087: 'bum 'gyur zla ba'i tshes dang po nas brtsams te /
NK013(pa)014:4088: dmar phyogs kyi tshes bcu la rdzogs par gyur pa'i
NK013(pa)014:4089: dge bas lus can kun gyis dpal rdo rje sems
NK013(pa)014:4090: dpa'i go 'phang mngon du byed par gyur cig /
